\id MRK - KadiwГ©u NT -Brazil 1999 (DBL -2013)
\h MARCOS
\toc1 NotaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axi Ane IdГӯ Marcos
\toc2 Marcos
\toc3 Mc
\mt1 NOTAЗӨANAЗӨAXI ANE IDГҚ MARCOS
\ip Marcos judeu codaa onalee lioneeЙЎМ¶a, niЙЎМ¶ijo Jesus maleeЙЎМ¶igotedeloco digoina iiЙЎМ¶o. Marcos lixigaЙЎМ¶awa BarnabГ© ane nexodi ijaa Paulo niЙЎМ¶ijo odoejegi niwiajeЙЎМ¶egi modigotece eletidi iiЙЎМ¶otedi moyeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece nibodicetedi anele. Odaa niЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi ja yaxawa Paulo niЙЎМ¶ijo me idei niwiloЙЎМ¶onaЙЎМ¶axi. Pedro jiЙЎМ¶ijaa yaxawa Marcos me nakato ЗӨoniotagodi, codaa Pedro jiЙЎМ¶ijaa yeloЙЎМ¶odita Marcos ane leeditibige me iditini. (Awiniteloco miditaЙЎМ¶a Atos 12.12,25; 13.5,13; 15.37; Colossenses 4.10; 2 TimГіteo 4.11; 1 Pedro 5.13).
\ip Marcos eetece naЙЎМ¶atetigi Jesus me icilatidi eelotaginadi, codaa meote Г©maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a me newiЙЎМ¶atace. Eledi yalaЙЎМ¶ata Jesus mida notoetiigitedeloco inoatawece niwicidi abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a, codaa me ЙЎМ¶odaxakawa SatanГЎs. Eledi yalaЙЎМ¶ata Jesus mida naЙЎМ¶atetigitedeloco niwocotaЙЎМ¶a inaa ebekadi nelecoli. Codaa Marcos yalaЙЎМ¶ata Jesus mida naЙЎМ¶atetigi me ixomaЙЎМ¶ateetedice codaa me napitaЙЎМ¶adi ЙЎМ¶obeyaceЙЎМ¶eco. Marcos aЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a yalaЙЎМ¶ata lanokegi Jesus, pida boЙЎМ¶odaa yalaЙЎМ¶ata niЙЎМ¶idaa dinanatedigi Jesus meote ane iiЙЎМ¶ete AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji meote, meotedibige me ЙЎМ¶odewiЙЎМ¶atace.
\c 1
\s1 Natematigigi JoГЈo Batista
\r (Mateus 3.1-12; Lucas 3.1-18; JoГЈo 1.19-28)
\p 
\v 1 Nibodicetedi anele aneetece Jesus Cristo, Lionigi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.
\p 
\v 2 JiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee maleekoka dinojogotedini nibodicetedi anele. IsaГӯas ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo eledi anoyeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece lowooko AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji niЙЎМ¶ijo jotigide, oyalaЙЎМ¶atalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lotaЙЎМ¶a, niЙЎМ¶ijo modi,
\q1 вҖңDigawini! Jimonyaticogi ЙЎМ¶adodoe niЙЎМ¶ijo aneetece niЙЎМ¶inoa yotaЙЎМ¶a me ilakidetece ЙЎМ¶anaigi.
\q1 
\v 3 Dapaawetibece miditaЙЎМ¶a nipodigi ane yadilo ane diЙЎМ¶ica niЙЎМ¶eladimigipi,
\q1 mee me dotaЙЎМ¶a,
\q1 вҖҳAlakidenitema naigi ЗӨoniotagodi me ixomaЙЎМ¶atedijo!
\q1 Awii naicoli me dixoketema!вҖҷвҖқ
\p 
\v 4 JoГЈo Batista niЙЎМ¶ijo ane niiЙЎМ¶e AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji idiaaЙЎМ¶i miditaЙЎМ¶a nipodigi ane yadilo ane diЙЎМ¶ica niЙЎМ¶eladimigipi, odaa nilegetiniwace oko. Yatematitibece latematigo, yalaЙЎМ¶ata niЙЎМ¶ina oko me leeditibige modinilaatece libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco, odaa ja dinilege me ikee modinilaatece libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco, odaa ja ixomaЙЎМ¶ateetedice AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco.
\v 5 Ijotawece niЙЎМ¶ijo niЙЎМ¶eladimigipitigi nipodigi JudГ©ia, aniaa nigotaЙЎМ¶a JerusalГ©m igotibeci midataЙЎМ¶a JoГЈo me nilegetiniwace midi akiidi JordГЈo. NiЙЎМ¶ijo noЙЎМ¶odi lodoe eliodi oko me inoa libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco codaa moyemaa moika libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco, odaa ja nilegetiniwace.
\p 
\v 6 JoГЈo lowoodi, gameelo lamodi anonibila, codaa nigoenaЙЎМ¶adi ewacogo. Codaa yeligo ЙЎМ¶onipidi inaa napigo.
\v 7 Inoatawece nokododi yalakatiditiogi niЙЎМ¶ica noiigi, meetiogi, вҖңNigidiaaЙЎМ¶idi enagi eledi oko ane daЙЎМ¶axa me ЙЎМ¶oneЙЎМ¶egi caticedi ee, oteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a jakadi me idakagitini lodoe me jowilece liwelatedi.
\v 8 Jibake ninyoЙЎМ¶odi me ЙЎМ¶adilegenitiwaji me jikee niЙЎМ¶ikani mawiite niЙЎМ¶inoa ЙЎМ¶abeyaceЙЎМ¶eco, pida baЙЎМ¶a ibake Liwigo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me iigi anodaaЙЎМ¶eni me ЙЎМ¶adewiki.вҖқ
\s1 JoГЈo ilege Jesus
\r (Mateus 3.13-17; Lucas 3.21-22)
\p 
\v 9 NiЙЎМ¶ijoa nokododi me dilegenaЙЎМ¶a JoГЈo, Jesus noditedice nigotaЙЎМ¶a NazarГ©, nipodigi GalilГ©ia. Odaa jiЙЎМ¶igo aneitice JoГЈo me dilegenaЙЎМ¶a. Odaa JoГЈo ja ilege Jesus miditaЙЎМ¶a akiidi JordГЈo.
\v 10 NiЙЎМ¶ijo Jesus naЙЎМ¶a doletibige me daxoditedita ninyoЙЎМ¶odi, aЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a leegi, ja nadi ditibigimedi me domoke. Odaa Liwigo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ja dinikatelogo dinanatigi yotibi.
\v 11 Odaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ja dotaЙЎМ¶a digoida ditibigimedi, meete, вҖңAkaami Ionigi ane daЙЎМ¶axa me jemaa. Eliodi me idinitibeci akaami leeЙЎМ¶odi.вҖқ \fig |src="CN01656b.TIF" size="span" copy="В© 1978 David C. Cook Publishing Co." ref="Marcos 1.9-11"\fig*
\s1 SatanГЎs dineetalo Jesus me domeЙЎМ¶eo meote ane beyagi
\r (Mateus 4.1-11; Lucas 4.1-13)
\p 
\v 12 Odaa aЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a leegi Liwigo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ja yadeegitedicogi Jesus miditaЙЎМ¶a nipodigi ane yadilo ane diЙЎМ¶icata niЙЎМ¶eladimigipi.
\v 13 Odaa Jesus jiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶itedice cwareenta nokododi. Odaa ЗӨodaxakawa jiЙЎМ¶icaaniЙЎМ¶igotalo Jesus me dineetalo, domeЙЎМ¶eotibige deЙЎМ¶eote loenatagi ane beyagi. Codaa niЙЎМ¶idi nipodigi inoa eijedi ane doide, pida aanjotedi odoweditelogo Jesus.
\s1 Jesus jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶eyatedigi libakedi miditaЙЎМ¶a nipodigi GalilГ©ia
\r (Mateus 4.12-22; Lucas 4.14-15; 5.1-11)
\p 
\v 14 NiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi noЙЎМ¶oixotiwece JoГЈo manitaЙЎМ¶a niwiloЙЎМ¶onaЙЎМ¶axi, Jesus jiЙЎМ¶igo nipodigi GalilГ©ia yatematitedibece nibodicetedi anele aneetece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me icota me iiЙЎМ¶e laaleЙЎМ¶enali oko.
\v 15 Odaa mee, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ica noko AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane nibikota jiЙЎМ¶icota. Ja nipegi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji nige iiЙЎМ¶e laaleЙЎМ¶enali oko. Adinilaanitecetiwaji ЙЎМ¶abeyaceЙЎМ¶eco, codaa iwaЙЎМ¶ati nibodicetedi anele.вҖқ
\p 
\v 16 NiЙЎМ¶ijo Jesus me noxiwigi liniogotibece niweiigi GalilГ©ia, odaa ja nadi SimГЈo ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo nioxoa ane liboonaЙЎМ¶adi AndrГ©. Oyokoletedinigi leelatiidi miditaЙЎМ¶a weiigi leeЙЎМ¶odi mina libakedi me nomiigomigipi.
\v 17 Odaa Jesus meetediogi, вҖңAnagi, aniwitibici! ЗӨadiiЙЎМ¶axini anodaaЙЎМ¶emiita oko madeegitalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, digo anemii madeegi noЙЎМ¶ojegi oko.вҖқ
\v 18 AЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a leegi odaa joЙЎМ¶oikatedice leelatiidi, odaa joЙЎМ¶odiotibece Jesus.
\p 
\v 19 Odaa niЙЎМ¶igoawaanigi odoe, Jesus ja nadi Tiago ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo nioxoa ane liboonaЙЎМ¶adi JoГЈo, lionigipi Zebedeu. Ideiticoace catinedi liwatece, oyoetibigo leelatiidi.
\v 20 AЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a leegi Jesus jaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a eniditediogi modiotibece. Odaa jiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶oyaladi niЙЎМ¶ijo eniodi maditaЙЎМ¶a liwatece ijaaЙЎМ¶ijoa liimetedipi, odaa joЙЎМ¶odiotibece Jesus.
\s1 Jesus icilatidi ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa ane dakatiogi niwigo abeyaceЙЎМ¶egi
\r (Lucas 4.31-37)
\p 
\v 21 Jesus ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece joЙЎМ¶otota nigotaЙЎМ¶a Cafarnaum. Odaa aЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a leegi, naЙЎМ¶a saabado, Jesus jiЙЎМ¶igo diiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶a manitaЙЎМ¶a liiakanaЙЎМ¶axi judeutedi.
\v 22 NiЙЎМ¶idi noiigi ane yatecoЙЎМ¶o eliodi moyopo leeЙЎМ¶odi anodaaЙЎМ¶eeteda me diiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶a. LeeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a diiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶a, ibake epaa naЙЎМ¶atetigi, aliciagi niЙЎМ¶ijoa niiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anadi anodiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atece lajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco MoisГ©s, leeЙЎМ¶odi boЙЎМ¶oibake naЙЎМ¶atetigi niЙЎМ¶inoa eletidi niiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anadi niЙЎМ¶ina modiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atece najoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco.
\p 
\v 23 ManitaЙЎМ¶a niiakanaЙЎМ¶axi onini ica ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa ane dakatiogi niwigo abeyaceЙЎМ¶egi aneo meote loenataka ane napioi. Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo Jesus me diiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶a, niЙЎМ¶ijo niwigo abeyaceЙЎМ¶egi eo niЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa me dacaage, odaa mee,
\v 24 вҖңAЙЎМ¶ica anejinaЙЎМ¶ataЙЎМ¶agi, Jesus anicoЙЎМ¶iticogi nigotaЙЎМ¶a NazarГ©! Domige naЙЎМ¶anagi me ЙЎМ¶odaaЙЎМ¶ateЙЎМ¶egi? JowooЙЎМ¶odi anakaami. Akaami NiЙЎМ¶ijoa ane iolatedice AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, codaa nimonya miniokiniwateda me dibatema.вҖқ
\p 
\v 25 Odaa Jesus ja yapeteЙЎМ¶e niЙЎМ¶ijo niwigo abeyaceЙЎМ¶egi, meete, вҖңAnotokiti, codaa anotitice niЙЎМ¶idoda ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa!вҖқ
\v 26 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo niwigo abeyaceЙЎМ¶egi eliodi meo me dinaxilaketibece niЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa. NaЙЎМ¶a dinigetaЙЎМ¶atee me dacaage, odaa ja ika niЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa.
\v 27 Ijotawece niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi nawelatibigiwaji, odaa ja dinigetiwage, modi, вҖңAmiida ica niciagi? Domige niiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶egi gela? IgaataЙЎМ¶a ida notoetiigi me iticoitedice niwicidi abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a, codaa oyiwaЙЎМ¶adi!вҖқ
\v 28 Odaa aЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a leegi, nibodigitigi niЙЎМ¶ida aneote Jesus jiЙЎМ¶ilaagiteloco iditawece nipodigi GalilГ©ia.
\s1 Jesus nicilatiditediniwace eliodi oko
\r (Mateus 8.14-17; Lucas 4.38-41)
\p 
\v 29 NiЙЎМ¶ijo Jesus naЙЎМ¶a noditedice liiakanaЙЎМ¶axi judeutedi, odaa dowicetedicogi liЙЎМ¶eladi SimГЈo ijaa AndrГ©. Ijo maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a lixigaЙЎМ¶awepodi Tiago ijaa JoГЈo.
\v 30 Aca SimГЈo loxiiЙЎМ¶ate noЙЎМ¶otota one deelotika. Iwoteloco lipe, eliodi me dapicoЙЎМ¶o-lolaadi. NaЙЎМ¶a dakatedio Jesus ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece, odaa joЙЎМ¶oyatematitalo me deelotika SimГЈo loxiiЙЎМ¶ate.
\v 31 Odaa Jesus ja dakatediwece aneitice naЙЎМ¶ajo iwaalo, naЙЎМ¶a dibatedigi libaaЙЎМ¶adi, odaa ja yaxawa me nicotini. Odaa ja ma me dapicoЙЎМ¶o-lolaadi, odaa jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶eyatigi me yoe liweenigi Jesus ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece.
\p 
\v 32 NiЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶ocidi, naЙЎМ¶a dalimeti aligeЙЎМ¶e, ica noiigi oyadeegitalo Jesus icoatawece niЙЎМ¶icoa neelotaginadi codaa me niЙЎМ¶ica anodakatiogi niwicidi abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a.
\v 33 Ijotawece niЙЎМ¶ijo niЙЎМ¶eladimigipitigi nigotaЙЎМ¶a dinatecoЙЎМ¶otee lodoe SimГЈo liЙЎМ¶eladi.
\v 34 Odaa Jesus icilatidi eliodi oko, codaa inoatawece ane latopaco neelotika, codaa iticoitedice owidi niwicidi abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a. NiЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a iticoitedice, odaa Jesus aika niЙЎМ¶ijoa niwicidi abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a doЙЎМ¶oyalaЙЎМ¶atalo leeЙЎМ¶odi oyowooЙЎМ¶odi Jesus me AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji Lionigi.
\s1 Jesus dinoЙЎМ¶atedice mokiniwatece me yotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶e AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji
\r (Lucas 4.42-44)
\p 
\v 35 NiЙЎМ¶ijo maleedaЙЎМ¶a dinici okoЙЎМ¶okoodi, Jesus jiЙЎМ¶itedibige, odaa jiЙЎМ¶igo miditaЙЎМ¶a nipodigi ane diЙЎМ¶icata oko. Odaa jiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶itedice me yotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶e AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.
\v 36 SimГЈo ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo niЙЎМ¶ijo eledi anodiotibece joЙЎМ¶odoletibige Jesus idiaanaЙЎМ¶adii.
\v 37 NiЙЎМ¶ijo noЙЎМ¶oyakadi Jesus, odaa joЙЎМ¶oditalo, вҖңInatawece noiigi oyapitibigaЙЎМ¶aji.вҖқ
\p 
\v 38 Pida Jesus meetediogi, вҖңIniЙЎМ¶a midiwataЙЎМ¶a eletidi nigotadawaanaЙЎМ¶a ane ipegitege niЙЎМ¶ina anejonaЙЎМ¶a amaleeЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a idiaa yatematikanaЙЎМ¶adi. IgaataЙЎМ¶a jiЙЎМ¶idaa ibakedi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane niiЙЎМ¶etediwa.вҖқ
\v 39 Odaa Jesus jiЙЎМ¶igotedeloco iditawece nipodigi GalilГ©ia, yatematitedibece latematiko midiwataЙЎМ¶a liiakanaЙЎМ¶axiidi judeutedi, codaa iticoitedicoace niwicidi abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a.
\s1 Jesus icilatidi ica dawace-lolaadi
\r (Mateus 8.1-4; Lucas 5.12-16)
\p 
\v 40 Ica noko ica ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa dawace-lolaadi igo midoataЙЎМ¶a Jesus, odaa yamaЙЎМ¶atedi lokotidi lodoe, odaa meetalo, вҖңNigemaani madicilatiti, jowooЙЎМ¶odi mida ЙЎМ¶animaweneЙЎМ¶egi madicilatiti.вҖқ
\p 
\v 41 Jesus eliodi me iwikode, odaa ipeketedeloco libaaЙЎМ¶atedi, odaa ja niniЙЎМ¶odi, meeteta niЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa, вҖңJemaa me ЙЎМ¶adicilatiti! Natigide, ja ЙЎМ¶adicili!вҖқ
\v 42 Odaa aЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a leegi, ja ma niЙЎМ¶ijo leelotagi, jeЙЎМ¶ele lolaadi niЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa.
\v 43-44 Odaa aЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a leegi, Jesus ja iiЙЎМ¶e mopi. Codaa yajoi niЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa, meeteta, вҖңDigawini! JiniЙЎМ¶ica anatematiita me ЙЎМ¶adicilatiti. Pida emii midiwataЙЎМ¶a sacerdotitedi, odaa ikeeni naЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶adicili. Odaa aboonitalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji niЙЎМ¶ijo jotigide MoisГ©s ane iiЙЎМ¶e moibootalo mikeenita niЙЎМ¶ina eledi oko AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji naЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶adicilatiti.вҖқ
\p 
\v 45 Pida niЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa naЙЎМ¶a noditice, odaa jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶eyatigi me yatematitiogi niЙЎМ¶ina eledi oko, odaa jiЙЎМ¶ilaagitice nibodigi. JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi Jesus me daЙЎМ¶a domaЙЎМ¶alee yakadi me dakatediwece nigotadi niЙЎМ¶ina me yemaa. Pida jiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶itedice midiwataЙЎМ¶a nipodaЙЎМ¶a ane diЙЎМ¶icata niЙЎМ¶eladimigipi, wetice nigotadi. Odaa niЙЎМ¶ina oko jiЙЎМ¶igotibeci miniwataЙЎМ¶a, oicoЙЎМ¶oticogi inoatawece nigotadi.
\c 2
\s1 Jesus icilatidi ica ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa alejaado ane daЙЎМ¶adiaa ditineЙЎМ¶e
\r (Mateus 9.1-8; Lucas 5.17-26)
\p 
\v 1 NaЙЎМ¶a ixomaЙЎМ¶atedijo icoa nokododi, Jesus joЙЎМ¶opitacedicogi nigotaЙЎМ¶a Cafarnaum. Odaa jiЙЎМ¶ilaagitice nibodigi niЙЎМ¶iniwa liЙЎМ¶eladi.
\v 2 Odaa aЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a leegi eliodi oko dinatecoЙЎМ¶otee, codaa aЙЎМ¶aleeЙЎМ¶ica nimedi anipegitege lapoagi liЙЎМ¶eladi. Odaa Jesus yatematitediogi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lotaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶idi noiigi-nelegi.
\v 3 EЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee me datematika Jesus, odaa icoa cwaatolo ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi oyadeegi ica alejaado ane daЙЎМ¶adiaa ditineЙЎМ¶e, odaa joЙЎМ¶oyoyaЙЎМ¶adi waxoditinigi lipe.
\v 4 Pida aЙЎМ¶oyakadi doЙЎМ¶odipegitalo Jesus leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi-nelegi. Odaa joЙЎМ¶odalaЙЎМ¶atetibigimece diimigi lelГЎЙЎМ¶a, odaa joЙЎМ¶owo lawimaЙЎМ¶ajegi niЙЎМ¶ijo diimigi lelГЎЙЎМ¶a, ditibigimedi niЙЎМ¶ijo aneitedice Jesus. NiЙЎМ¶ijo noЙЎМ¶owo lawimaЙЎМ¶ajegi nelegi, odaa joЙЎМ¶onikatini niЙЎМ¶ijo alejaado.
\v 5 NiЙЎМ¶ijo Jesus naЙЎМ¶a nadi niЙЎМ¶ijoa cwaatolo ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi moyiwaЙЎМ¶adi mida nimaweneЙЎМ¶egi me icilatidi niЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa alejaado, odaa jeЙЎМ¶eete niЙЎМ¶ijo alejaado, вҖңIonigi, AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ja napitaЙЎМ¶adi ЙЎМ¶abeyaceЙЎМ¶eco!вҖқ \fig |src="CN01687B.TIF" size="span" copy="В© 1978 David C. Cook Publishing Co." ref="Marcos 2.1-5"\fig*
\p 
\v 6 Icoa niiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anadi anodiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atece lajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco MoisГ©s idiaaЙЎМ¶i nicotiniwace. Odaa ja nowookonaЙЎМ¶a, codaa epaa dinige, modi,
\v 7 вҖңIgame leeЙЎМ¶odi idoa ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa meote ida ligegi? DotaЙЎМ¶atedibige AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. IgaataЙЎМ¶a aЙЎМ¶ica eledi ane yakadi me napitaЙЎМ¶adi libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco niЙЎМ¶ina oko. Iniokiniwateda AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji baЙЎМ¶a yakadi me napitaЙЎМ¶adi nibeyaceЙЎМ¶eco.вҖқ
\p 
\v 8 Odaa aЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a leegi Jesus ja yowooЙЎМ¶odi ane lowoogo, odaa jeЙЎМ¶eetediogi, вҖңIgame leeЙЎМ¶odi midaЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶adowoogo catiwedi ЙЎМ¶adaaleЙЎМ¶enali?
\v 9 Amigida ica ane daЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶alaЙЎМ¶a mejita niЙЎМ¶idi ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa alejaado? DomigetaЙЎМ¶a eneЙЎМ¶egi dakake mejita, вҖҳAneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ja napitaЙЎМ¶adi ЙЎМ¶abeyaceЙЎМ¶ecoвҖҷ, oЙЎМ¶oa, domigetaЙЎМ¶a eneЙЎМ¶egi dakake mejita, вҖҳAdabititini, abaata ЙЎМ¶adipe, odaaЙЎМ¶awaligi!вҖҷ?
\v 10 Pida jikeetaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji, Ee, ЗӨoneleegiwa ane jicoЙЎМ¶otibigimece ditibigimedi, mida inimaweneЙЎМ¶egi digoina iiЙЎМ¶o me inapitaЙЎМ¶adi libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco oko.вҖқ Odaa Jesus jeЙЎМ¶eete niЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa alejaado,
\v 11 вҖңЗӨadiiЙЎМ¶eni, adabititini, abaata ЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶elate, odaa opiliticogi ЙЎМ¶adiЙЎМ¶eladi!вҖқ
\p 
\v 12 Odaa aЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a leegi niЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa ja dabiditini, dibata naЙЎМ¶ajo liЙЎМ¶elate, odaa joЙЎМ¶opi, yakagiditeloco lodoe niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi-nelegi. Odaa ijotawece eliodi moyopo, codaa odoЙЎМ¶etetalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, odaa modi, вҖңAniЙЎМ¶ica me jinataЙЎМ¶a liciagi niЙЎМ¶ida niciagi!вҖқ
\s1 Jesus eniditeta Levi me diotibece
\r (Mateus 9.9-13; Lucas 5.27-32)
\p 
\v 13 Jesus niЙЎМ¶igotace liniogotibece weiigi. Odaa ica noiigi-nelegi jiЙЎМ¶igo midoataЙЎМ¶a, odaa jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶eyatedigi me niiЙЎМ¶axitediniwace.
\v 14 MaleeЙЎМ¶idiaa neЙЎМ¶ewaligite, odaa ja nadi Levi, niЙЎМ¶ijo lionigi Alfeu. Levi idiaaЙЎМ¶i nicoteloco nibaanco aneitice me dibatibigege ninyeelo ninionigi-eliodi romaanotedi. Odaa Jesus jeЙЎМ¶eeteta, вҖңAnagi, aniwitibici!вҖқ Odaa Levi ja dabiditini, odaa ja diotece Jesus.
\p 
\v 15 Jesus igo Levi liЙЎМ¶eladi. Odaa ja nicotedini me ligiiwepodi niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece. AaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a ligiiwepodi eliodi niЙЎМ¶ijo anodibatibigege ninyeelo ninionigi-eliodi romaanotedi, codaa meliodi oko ane daЙЎМ¶axa me abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a, igaataЙЎМ¶a eliodi niЙЎМ¶ijo oko anodiotece Jesus.
\v 16 NiЙЎМ¶ijoa niiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anadi anodiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atece lajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco MoisГ©s, niЙЎМ¶ijo anida aneetege niЙЎМ¶ijo lapo fariseutedi, onadi Jesus me ligiiwepodi niЙЎМ¶ijo anodibatibigege ninyeelo ninionigi-eliodi romaanotedi, codaa me niЙЎМ¶ijoa eletidi oko aneliodi me abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a. NiЙЎМ¶ijo noЙЎМ¶onadi, odaa joЙЎМ¶onigetiniwace niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece Jesus, moditiogi, вҖңIgame leeЙЎМ¶odi ЗӨaniotagodi me ligiiwepodi codaa me lacipaЙЎМ¶awepodi niЙЎМ¶ina anodibatibigege ninyeelo ninionigi-eliodi romaanotedi, codaa me niЙЎМ¶idi oko aninoa libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco?вҖқ
\p 
\v 17 Jesus ja wajipate niЙЎМ¶ijo noЙЎМ¶onigetiniwace niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece. NiЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a wajipatediogi, odaa jeЙЎМ¶eetediogi, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ina oko icileЙЎМ¶egi ayopotibige dotowegi, inokina niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane deelotika baЙЎМ¶a yopotibige dotowegi. Odaa Ee iciagi niЙЎМ¶ina dotowegi. IgaataЙЎМ¶a ajanagi niЙЎМ¶ina iiЙЎМ¶o daЙЎМ¶a jiniditiogi niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶atibigiwaji, pida janagi me jiniditiogi niЙЎМ¶ina oko abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a, ane liciagi niЙЎМ¶ina oko eelotaginadipi, amaleeЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a odinilaatece libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco.вҖқ
\s1 Oige Jesus oigetece niЙЎМ¶ica anodaaЙЎМ¶ee me daЙЎМ¶a jiniodaЙЎМ¶a meneЙЎМ¶egi jotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji
\r (Mateus 9.14-17; Lucas 5.33-39)
\p 
\v 18 Ica noko niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibeci JoГЈo Batista ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibeci fariseutedi odinatita nigigi mepaanoЙЎМ¶oyotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶e AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Ica oko enagitibeci midoataЙЎМ¶a Jesus, odaa joЙЎМ¶oige, moditalo, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibeci JoГЈo Batista ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibeci fariseutedi odinatita nigigi mepaanoЙЎМ¶oyotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶e AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Igame leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶idi anodiotibigaЙЎМ¶adici me doЙЎМ¶odinatita nigigi mepaanoЙЎМ¶oyotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶e AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji?вҖқ
\p 
\v 19 Odaa Jesus ja niniЙЎМ¶oditediogi, meetediogi, вҖңIna oko nodenigipi midi lalokegi nadoneЙЎМ¶egi, domigodinatita nigigi ina nigini niЙЎМ¶ijo ane wado miditaЙЎМ¶a? OteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶oyakadi modinatita nigigi!
\v 20 Pida icota niЙЎМ¶ica noko niЙЎМ¶ini ane wado modibata, odaa onoЙЎМ¶aticogi liwigotigi niЙЎМ¶idi oko. Odaa niЙЎМ¶ica noko niЙЎМ¶idi oko nodenigipi joЙЎМ¶odinatita nigigi.
\p 
\v 21 AЙЎМ¶ica ane napade niЙЎМ¶ina nowoodaЙЎМ¶agi oxiiЙЎМ¶odi daЙЎМ¶a dapadenaЙЎМ¶ata niЙЎМ¶ina lipegeteЙЎМ¶e liwai gela, igaataЙЎМ¶a nige dinabake, odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo lapadenaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶adi gela dinixigitiwage, odaa ja yaaЙЎМ¶adi niЙЎМ¶idi nowoodaЙЎМ¶agi oxiiЙЎМ¶odi anonapade, odaa jeЙЎМ¶epaanaЙЎМ¶a eliodi laakajegi.
\v 22 AЙЎМ¶ica ane iatinigi viinyo gela naЙЎМ¶ana laЙЎМ¶aaЙЎМ¶axi ewacogo opake. IgaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina viinyo gela beyagi nigoiatinigi naЙЎМ¶ana laЙЎМ¶aaЙЎМ¶axi opake, odaa niЙЎМ¶ica viinyo mina aniadi, codaa naЙЎМ¶ada laЙЎМ¶aaЙЎМ¶axi icota me beyagi. Pida leeditibige moiatinigi viinyo gela naЙЎМ¶ana laЙЎМ¶aaЙЎМ¶axi gela.вҖқ
\s1 Jesus diiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atetece ica anodaaЙЎМ¶ee modeemitetigi saabado
\r (Mateus 12.1-8; Lucas 6.1-5)
\p 
\v 23 Ica noko me saabado Jesus ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece oyakagiditeloco ica nixoЙЎМ¶otagi leyeema. NoЙЎМ¶oyakagiditeloco, odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece joЙЎМ¶onotegi ligecidi leyeema, onolagilatedi oyeligo.
\v 24 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijoa fariseutedi moditalo Jesus, вҖңDigawini! Igame leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶idi anodiotibigaЙЎМ¶adici mowo ane yolitoЙЎМ¶odomi ЙЎМ¶onajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶egi me daЙЎМ¶a jaoЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina me saabado?вҖқ
\p 
\v 25-26 Pida Jesus meetediogi, вҖңAjawienataka me naЙЎМ¶alomeЙЎМ¶enitelocotiwaji niЙЎМ¶ijo Davi aneo niЙЎМ¶ijo jotigide, Abiatar me lacilo-sacerdotitedi. NiЙЎМ¶ijo Davi ijaaЙЎМ¶ijoa lokaaЙЎМ¶etedipi naЙЎМ¶a nigodi nigigi, odaa Davi dakatio minitaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liЙЎМ¶eladi, odaa ja yeligo nipaon niЙЎМ¶ijoa sacerdotitedi anoibootalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. ЗӨonajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶egi ЙЎМ¶odoxoЙЎМ¶o me diЙЎМ¶ica eledi ane yakadi me yeligo niЙЎМ¶ijo paon. Inokinoa sacerdotitedi boЙЎМ¶oyakadi moyeligo niЙЎМ¶ijo paon. Pida Davi baanaЙЎМ¶a yeligo, codaa yajigotiogi niЙЎМ¶ijoa lokaaЙЎМ¶etedipi maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a oyeligo.вҖқ
\p 
\v 27 Odaa Jesus meetediogi, вҖңAneotedoЙЎМ¶oji eote niЙЎМ¶ina saabado me yaxawa niЙЎМ¶ina oko. AЙЎМ¶eote niЙЎМ¶ina oko midokida modowediteloco niiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶egi ane iiЙЎМ¶e modowediteloco saabado.
\v 28 Ee, ЗӨoneleegiwa ane jicoЙЎМ¶otibigimece ditibigimedi, ida inaЙЎМ¶atetigi mejitece ane yakadi me jaoЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina me saabado.вҖқ
\c 3
\s1 Jesus icilatidi ica ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa beyagi libaaЙЎМ¶adi me saabado
\r (Mateus 12.9-14; Lucas 6.6-11)
\p 
\v 1 Jesus dakatacediwece manitaЙЎМ¶a liiakanaЙЎМ¶axi judeutedi. IdiaaЙЎМ¶itice ica ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa beyagi libaaЙЎМ¶adi.
\v 2 Onidi ica oko anoiwitalo Jesus odoletibige monadi mige icilatidi niЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa ane beyagi libaaЙЎМ¶adi me saabado, igaataЙЎМ¶a domoЙЎМ¶oyemaa me nilaagedi Jesus niЙЎМ¶ina meote niЙЎМ¶icoa ane yolitoЙЎМ¶odomi lajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco MoisГ©s me jaoЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina me saabado.
\v 3 Odaa Jesus meeteta niЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa, вҖңAnagi digoina lodoe niЙЎМ¶ina oko!вҖқ
\v 4 Odaa Jesus jeЙЎМ¶eetediogi niЙЎМ¶ijo oko lakapetedipi, вҖңAmiinoa icoa lajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco MoisГ©s ane ЙЎМ¶odiiЙЎМ¶e me jaoЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina me saabado? Domige jakataЙЎМ¶a me jaoЙЎМ¶a anele, oЙЎМ¶oa domige me jaoЙЎМ¶a ane beyagi? Domige jakataЙЎМ¶a me jaxawanaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina oko me jaoЙЎМ¶a lewiЙЎМ¶a, oЙЎМ¶oa jikanaЙЎМ¶a me yeleo?вҖқ
\p Odaa aЙЎМ¶ica anoyatigi ligegi doЙЎМ¶oigidi.
\v 5 Odaa Jesus naЙЎМ¶a iwitediogi, odaa ja yelatetema niЙЎМ¶ijo oko, codaa agecaЙЎМ¶alo leeЙЎМ¶odi laaleЙЎМ¶enali me daЙЎМ¶axa me dakake. Odaa jeЙЎМ¶eeteta niЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa ane beyagi libaaЙЎМ¶adi, вҖңIxokeni ЙЎМ¶abaaЙЎМ¶adi!вҖқ NiЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a ixoketice libaaЙЎМ¶adi, odaa ja icГӯ, ja liciagi niЙЎМ¶ijo eledi libaaЙЎМ¶adi.
\v 6 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijoa fariseutedi ja noditicoaci, jiЙЎМ¶igotibeci oyotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶e niЙЎМ¶ijo lapo anodiotibeci inionigi-eliodi Herodes. Odoletibige niЙЎМ¶ica nimaweneЙЎМ¶egi moyeloadi Jesus.
\s1 Ica noiigi-nelegi odiotece Jesus
\p 
\v 7 Odaa Jesus naЙЎМ¶a noditedicogi aneitedice, jiЙЎМ¶igo lixigaЙЎМ¶awepodi niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece, igotibeci liniogotibece niweiigi GalilГ©ia. Odaa niЙЎМ¶ica noiigi-nelegi anodiotece. NiЙЎМ¶ica oko oicoЙЎМ¶oticogi nipodigi GalilГ©ia, codaa me JudГ©ia.
\v 8 Ica eledi oko boЙЎМ¶oicoЙЎМ¶oticogi nigotaЙЎМ¶a JerusalГ©m, codaa me nipodigi IdumГ©ia, codaa ica eledi oko oicoЙЎМ¶oticogi daato akiidi JordГЈo. Ica eledi oko oicoЙЎМ¶oticogi nigotadi Tiro aniaa Sidom. NiЙЎМ¶idi noiigi-nelegi enagitibeci midoataЙЎМ¶a Jesus niЙЎМ¶ijo noЙЎМ¶odibodicetibige ane loenataka.
\v 9 Jesus ja iiЙЎМ¶e niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece moilakideti aca niwatece, meetediogi, вҖңAlakideni naЙЎМ¶adi niwatece ayenikamaЙЎМ¶a deЙЎМ¶ejigo jaxoditinigi.вҖқ LeeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi-nelegi eneЙЎМ¶egi oiligice.
\v 10 Codaa eliodi oko ane icilatidi, odaa joaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ijo oko eelotaginadi me diniligice, odoletibige moyakadi modibatelogo maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a icilatidi.
\v 11 NiЙЎМ¶ijo oko anodakatiogi niwicidi abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a noЙЎМ¶onadi Jesus, odaa niwicidi abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a owo menitiniwace lodoe, codaa nacaagaЙЎМ¶a, modi, вҖңJaЙЎМ¶akamaЙЎМ¶akaami Lionigi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji!вҖқ
\p 
\v 12 Odaa Jesus ja noxoЙЎМ¶otediniwace, codaa najoitediniwace me doЙЎМ¶oyatemati niЙЎМ¶ica anijoa.
\s1 Jesus iolatedice icoa dooze ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi me liiЙЎМ¶exedi
\r (Mateus 10.1-4; Lucas 6.12-16)
\p 
\v 13 Jesus dalaЙЎМ¶atetedibigimece aca wetiЙЎМ¶a, odaa jeЙЎМ¶eniditediogi niЙЎМ¶ijoa ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi ane yemaa me iolatedicoace, odaa joЙЎМ¶odiitalo.
\v 14 Odaa Jesus ja iolatedicoace icoa dooze ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi aneyatedigi me вҖңIiЙЎМ¶exedipiвҖқ. Iolatedicoace midiaaЙЎМ¶i mijoataЙЎМ¶a, codaa me iiЙЎМ¶e moyatematitedibece latematiko.
\v 15 Odaa ja yajigotediogi notoetiigi moicilatidi eelotaginadi, codaa moiticoiticoace niwicidi abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a.
\p 
\v 16-17 Digawini liboonaЙЎМ¶atedi niЙЎМ¶ijoa ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi Jesus ane iolatedicoace: SimГЈo anidokeyatedigi me Pedro, Tiago ijaa JoГЈo ane lionigipi Zebedeu anidokoyatigi me Boanerges, amina anejinaЙЎМ¶ata, вҖңLionigipi niximaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶aвҖқ.
\v 18-19 Codaa aaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a iolatedicoace AndrГ©, Filipe, Bartolomeu, Mateus, TomГ©, Tiago ane lionigi Alfeu, Tadeu, SimГЈo ane domaЙЎМ¶a yemaa me nideleЙЎМ¶etiniwace romaanotedi, ijaa Judas Iscariotes ane yajigo Jesus niЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi mijoataЙЎМ¶a neloЙЎМ¶ododipi.
\s1 Modi Belzebu, ane diaabo, me yajigotalo notoetiigi Jesus
\r (Mateus 12.22-32; Lucas 11.14-23; 12.10)
\p 
\v 20 NiЙЎМ¶ijo Jesus niЙЎМ¶igo liЙЎМ¶eladi, odaa niЙЎМ¶ica noiigi-nelegi ja dinatecoЙЎМ¶oteetace. Odaa Jesus ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece aЙЎМ¶aleeЙЎМ¶oyakadi oteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a me niodaЙЎМ¶a.
\v 21 Odaa litacepodi Jesus joЙЎМ¶odibodice niЙЎМ¶ica Jesus aneote, odaa ja noditicoaci liЙЎМ¶eladi me lowoogo modigotalo Jesus, domoЙЎМ¶oyadeegitedicogi liЙЎМ¶eladi, leeЙЎМ¶odi ica oko anodi Jesus me yetole.
\p 
\v 22 Onidiwa icoa niiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anadi anodiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atece lajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco MoisГ©s anoicoЙЎМ¶oticogi nigotaЙЎМ¶a JerusalГ©m. NiЙЎМ¶idi modi, вҖңBelzebu, ane lacilo niwicidi abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a, yajacaЙЎМ¶adi, codaa yajigotalo notoetiigi me iticoitedicoace niwicidi abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a.вҖқ
\p 
\v 23 Odaa Jesus jeЙЎМ¶eniditediogi niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi me igotibeci odipegitalo, odaa ibake natematiko anida ane iciaceeketetege me niiЙЎМ¶axitediniwace. Odaa meetediogi, вҖңIgamodaaЙЎМ¶ee SatanГЎs me yakadi mepaa diniticoitice minitaЙЎМ¶a oko? Ayakadi!
\v 24 Nigidi inionigi-eliodi loiigi ane dawalacetiwage, odaa nigidiaa dinideletiwage, odaa loiigi icota me ma.
\v 25 Nigidi dinoiigiwepodi, ane dawalacetiwage, codaa midiaa dakapetiwage, niЙЎМ¶idi noiigi icota me ma.
\v 26 Codaa niwicidi abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a ane iiЙЎМ¶e SatanГЎs nige dawalacetiwage, odaa idiaa dakapetiwage, icota me ma notoetiigi SatanГЎs, odaa aЙЎМ¶alee diiЙЎМ¶enataka.
\p 
\v 27 Pida aЙЎМ¶ica ane yakadi me dakatiwece liЙЎМ¶eladi niЙЎМ¶ini ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa loniciweЙЎМ¶enigi me doliceta niЙЎМ¶inoa ane nepilidi. Idoka yakadi modolicetalo ane nepilidi niЙЎМ¶ini ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa nigodoejegi moigoetini. Odaa nigaleekoka oyakadi moyadeegi niЙЎМ¶inoa ane nepilidi niЙЎМ¶ini ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa.
\v 28 EjitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji niЙЎМ¶ina anewi. AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji yakadi me ixomaЙЎМ¶ateetedice inoatawece ane latopaco libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco niЙЎМ¶ina oko anowote, codaa lotaЙЎМ¶a ane beyagi modakapetege.
\v 29 Pida AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji baadaЙЎМ¶a ixomaЙЎМ¶ateetedice niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane beyagi modotaЙЎМ¶atibige Liwigo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Idioka limedi me laagedi niЙЎМ¶ini oko.вҖқ
\v 30 Odaa jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee Jesus me igidi leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶idi oko modi me dakatiogilo niwigo abeyaceЙЎМ¶egi.
\s1 JoЙЎМ¶ototalo Jesus nioxoadipi ajaaЙЎМ¶ajo eliodo
\r (Mateus 12.46-50; Lucas 8.19-21)
\p 
\v 31 NiЙЎМ¶icotiobeci Jesus nioxoadipi ajaaЙЎМ¶ajo eliodo. Odaa ideiticoace we niЙЎМ¶ijo diimigi, odaa joЙЎМ¶odienaЙЎМ¶atalo Jesus.
\v 32 Eliodi oko oyawiile Jesus, odaa moditalo, вҖңЗӨadiodo idiaa ЙЎМ¶anioxoadipi etidi wetice, onienaЙЎМ¶ataЙЎМ¶awa.вҖқ
\p 
\v 33 Odaa Jesus ja igiditediogi, meetediogi, вҖңAmaajo aca eiodo? Codaa amiijo ica inioxoadipi?вҖқ
\v 34 NaЙЎМ¶a niipetediogi Jesus niЙЎМ¶ijo ane nicotiniwace anoyawiile, odaa jeЙЎМ¶ee, вҖңDigawini! NiЙЎМ¶idi jiЙЎМ¶idiaa inioxoadipi codaa me eiodo.
\v 35 IgaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina aneo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane yemaa, niЙЎМ¶ini jiЙЎМ¶iniaa inioxoa, iniwaalo, codaa me eiodo.вҖқ
\c 4
\s1 Natematigigi ica enanaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶a
\r (Mateus 13.1-9; Lucas 8.4-8)
\p 
\v 1 Jesus naЙЎМ¶a niiЙЎМ¶axitacediniwace noiigi liniogotibece niweiigi GalilГ©ia. Odaa eliodi oko odilapodetelogo. JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi me waxoditedinigi naЙЎМ¶ajo niwatece nicotedinigi le, odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi-nelegi idiaaЙЎМ¶i miditaЙЎМ¶a dotiwadi liniogotibece weiigi.
\v 2 NiЙЎМ¶ijo Jesus me niiЙЎМ¶axitediniwace niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi, yatemati owidi natematiko anida ane iciaceeketetege.
\p Odaa meetediogi,
\v 3 вҖңDiganajipaatiwa! Ica ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa one yadeegi nolacidi meyateloco miditaЙЎМ¶a lixoЙЎМ¶otagi.
\v 4 NiЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a ilaagaЙЎМ¶aditedibece niЙЎМ¶ijoa nolacidi inoatawece liwailidi, odaa onicoa icoa lolacidi aneniteloco naigi liniogotibece. Odaa ilaaЙЎМ¶axodi jeЙЎМ¶enagitibeci, joЙЎМ¶oyelio niЙЎМ¶ijoa lolacidi.
\v 5 Icoa eletidi lolacidi onenite midiwataЙЎМ¶a wetiadi ane deЙЎМ¶ewi ina mica iiЙЎМ¶o. Odaa aЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a leegi niЙЎМ¶ijoa lolacidi ja nokoloЙЎМ¶o leeЙЎМ¶odi me deЙЎМ¶ewi ina mica iiЙЎМ¶o.
\v 6 Pida naЙЎМ¶a dapicoЙЎМ¶o aligeЙЎМ¶e, odaa ja yalegi ijoatawece niЙЎМ¶ijoa nawodigijedi, odaa ja yadilo, leeЙЎМ¶odi onateciЙЎМ¶ijoa litotitedi.
\v 7 Icoa eletidi lolacidi enitedini miditaЙЎМ¶a ipelakijadi. Odaa ipelaЙЎМ¶a naЙЎМ¶a ili, odaa ja iЙЎМ¶owalaЙЎМ¶adi lawodigijedi niЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa aneyatedini, odaa aika daЙЎМ¶a etaye.
\v 8 Pida icoa eletidi beЙЎМ¶eniteloco miditaЙЎМ¶a ica iiЙЎМ¶o anele. NaЙЎМ¶a nokoloЙЎМ¶o, odaa beЙЎМ¶ele me ili, codaa etaye. Onidateci ligegi yajigo triinta, seseenta, codaa me onaniteci taalia lolacidi leyeema.вҖқ
\v 9 Odaa meetediogi Jesus, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ina oko ane wajipatalo yotaЙЎМ¶a, leeditibige me watacotece.вҖқ
\s1 Jesus yatemati ane diitigi niЙЎМ¶ijo natematigigi niЙЎМ¶ijo enanaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶a
\r (Mateus 13.10-23; Lucas 8.9-15)
\p 
\v 10 NiЙЎМ¶ijo noЙЎМ¶opitibeci niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi-nelegi, odaa onaniЙЎМ¶iniwatece Jesus ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo dooze anodiotibece ijaaЙЎМ¶ijoa eletidi lokaaЙЎМ¶etedipi anidiaaЙЎМ¶itice oigetece anodaa diitigi niЙЎМ¶ijo latematigo ane yatemati.
\v 11 Odaa Jesus jeЙЎМ¶eetediogi, вҖңAneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ЙЎМ¶adiolaatedicetiwaji me ikeetedaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji anodaaЙЎМ¶ee me iiЙЎМ¶e laaleЙЎМ¶enali niЙЎМ¶ina oko. Pida jatematitiogi natematiko anida ane jiciaceeketege niЙЎМ¶ina ane doЙЎМ¶oyemaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me iiЙЎМ¶e laaleЙЎМ¶enali.
\q1 
\v 12 вҖҳJiЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi mideЙЎМ¶ejigotiogi amaleeЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a onadi,
\q1 pida aЙЎМ¶oyowooЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ica ane jao,
\q1 codaa owajipata,
\q1 pida aЙЎМ¶oyowooЙЎМ¶odi iiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco.
\q1 Odaa jiЙЎМ¶idaa me doЙЎМ¶oyakadi modinilaatece libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco,
\q1 odaa ayakadi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me yapitaЙЎМ¶adi laaleЙЎМ¶enali.вҖҷвҖқ
\p 
\v 13 Odaa Jesus ja nigetediniwace, meetediogi, вҖңNige doЙЎМ¶owooЙЎМ¶oti ane diitigitiwaji niЙЎМ¶ijo yatematigo ane jatemati, igame ЙЎМ¶animaweneЙЎМ¶egi mowooЙЎМ¶oti inoa eletidi yatematiko?
\v 14 NiЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa ane ilaagaЙЎМ¶aditedibece lolacidi liciagi niЙЎМ¶ina ane yatematitedibece nibodicetedi anele ane icoЙЎМ¶otedicogi miniwataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.
\v 15 Initibece oko ane wajipatalo niЙЎМ¶inoa nibodicetedi anele liciagi naigi liniogotibece. NiЙЎМ¶ina naЙЎМ¶a wajipata, odaa aЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a leegi SatanГЎs ja noЙЎМ¶a natematiko ane ideite catiwedi laaleЙЎМ¶enali.
\v 16 Odaa ina eledi oko liciagi niЙЎМ¶ina iiЙЎМ¶o aninoa wetiadi. NiЙЎМ¶ina noЙЎМ¶owajipatalo nibodicetedi anele, odibatege niЙЎМ¶ijoa natematiko, codaa me ninitibigiwaji.
\v 17 Pida niЙЎМ¶ijo oko aЙЎМ¶eliodi eliwaЙЎМ¶atakaneЙЎМ¶egi liciaco niЙЎМ¶ijoa nawodigijedi anokateciЙЎМ¶idiwa litodi, odaa aЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a leegi midiaaЙЎМ¶i. NiЙЎМ¶ina niЙЎМ¶inoa ane dakaketema, codaa ina moyalomeЙЎМ¶e niЙЎМ¶ina eledi oko leeЙЎМ¶odi monakato AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, odaa niЙЎМ¶idi oko joЙЎМ¶oika monakato AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.
\v 18 Ina eledi oko liciagi niЙЎМ¶ina iiЙЎМ¶o aninaa ipelaЙЎМ¶a. Owajipatalo nibodicetedi anele.
\v 19 Pida oigecaЙЎМ¶aleЙЎМ¶e niЙЎМ¶inoa aninoatigi digoina iiЙЎМ¶o, odaa daЙЎМ¶axa moyemaa dinyeelo, codaa oyemaa niЙЎМ¶inoa anicinoa mepoka oyakadi. Odaa jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee, liciagi niЙЎМ¶inoa nawodigijedi ane yapoЙЎМ¶oditini ipelaЙЎМ¶a, odaa inoatawece niЙЎМ¶inoa anoyemaa mowote aika me ili AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lotaЙЎМ¶a catiwedi laaleЙЎМ¶enali, odaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lotaЙЎМ¶a aiigi ane lakataЙЎМ¶a.
\v 20 Pida ina eledi oko baЙЎМ¶a liciagi niЙЎМ¶ijo iiЙЎМ¶o anele. NiЙЎМ¶idi oko odibatege nibodicetedi anele, odaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lotaЙЎМ¶a iigi lakataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶idi oko, odaa liciagi metaye niЙЎМ¶ijoa lolacidi anoyajigo ligegi anidiwa triinta, seseenta codaa me onaniteci taalia lolacidi.вҖқ
\s1 Jesus diiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atetece nilokokena AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji
\r (Lucas 8.16-18)
\p 
\v 21 Jesus eЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee me dotaЙЎМ¶a, meetediogi, вҖңDomigica ane yalegi noledaЙЎМ¶axi odaa yapoЙЎМ¶oditeloco baalida, oЙЎМ¶oa domigetaЙЎМ¶a ixotiwece nipe le? AЙЎМ¶ica! Pida oyalegi naЙЎМ¶ana noledaЙЎМ¶axi, odaa onanyoketi ditibigimedi.
\v 22 Odaa aЙЎМ¶ica ane dinaЙЎМ¶aditi ane daЙЎМ¶a yeloЙЎМ¶oteloco. Codaa inoatawece ane dinaЙЎМ¶aditedini, icota monadi niЙЎМ¶ina oko.
\v 23 NiЙЎМ¶ina oko anowajipatalo yotaЙЎМ¶a leeditibige mowatacotece.вҖқ
\p 
\v 24 Meetediogi Jesus, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ina baЙЎМ¶a owookoni niЙЎМ¶ina majipaatalo yotaЙЎМ¶a. Anemiita niЙЎМ¶ina eledi oko, odaa jiЙЎМ¶idaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a igotedaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, odaa eliodi niЙЎМ¶ica ane yajigote niЙЎМ¶ina oko anowatacotece latematiko.
\v 25 IgaataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji daЙЎМ¶axatace meliodi ane yajigote niЙЎМ¶ina oko anoyiwaЙЎМ¶adi. Pida niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane diЙЎМ¶ica eliwaЙЎМ¶atakaneЙЎМ¶egi, AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji noЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ijo onateciЙЎМ¶ini anida minitaЙЎМ¶a.вҖқ
\s1 Natematigigi icoa lolacidi
\p 
\v 26 Jesus mee, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ina AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me iiЙЎМ¶e laaleЙЎМ¶enali oko, liciagi niЙЎМ¶ina ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa aneyatedini nolacidi miditaЙЎМ¶a iiЙЎМ¶o ane ibinie.
\v 27 NiЙЎМ¶ina neЙЎМ¶enoale diote, odaa nicotini niЙЎМ¶ina naЙЎМ¶a noko, odaa niЙЎМ¶ijoa nolacidi ja nokoloЙЎМ¶o codaa me ili, pida ayowooЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ica anodaaЙЎМ¶ee me ili.
\v 28 IiЙЎМ¶o eo me ili nawodigijedi. Odoejegi nokoloЙЎМ¶o nawodigijegi, nigidiaaЙЎМ¶idi ja daxoditice ligecidi. Odaa nigidiaaЙЎМ¶idi jaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a nodi lolacidi.
\v 29 NiЙЎМ¶ina neЙЎМ¶ei niЙЎМ¶inoa ligecidi, odaa aЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a leegi niЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa ja nakagidi yatita nodaajo, leeЙЎМ¶odi jiЙЎМ¶icota noko me nopilaЙЎМ¶aditedio lawodigijedi.вҖқ
\s1 Natematigigi aca lolacawaana вҖңmostaadaвҖқ
\r (Mateus 13.31-32, 35; Lucas 13.18-19)
\p 
\v 30 EЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee Jesus me dotaЙЎМ¶a, mee, вҖңIgamigodaaЙЎМ¶ee nige iiЙЎМ¶e AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji laaleЙЎМ¶enali niЙЎМ¶ina oko? Amigida ica natematigo ane jiciaceeketege me jakadi me jatemati?
\v 31 NiЙЎМ¶ina AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji niЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶eyatedigi me iiЙЎМ¶e laaleЙЎМ¶enali niЙЎМ¶ina oko, liciagi naЙЎМ¶ana lolagi mostaada. NiЙЎМ¶ina moyateloco niЙЎМ¶ina iiЙЎМ¶o, naЙЎМ¶ani lolagi daЙЎМ¶axa me lionawaana liwigotigi niЙЎМ¶inoa eletidi lolacidi.
\v 32 Pida nigidiaaЙЎМ¶idi nigoyatini naЙЎМ¶ajo lolagi, odaa ili yayoketicoace niЙЎМ¶ijoa eletidi nawodigijedi. Codaa libiwedi daЙЎМ¶axa me nelecoli, odaa ilaaЙЎМ¶axodi owote libatoli odiwaletigi laamotiidi.вҖқ
\p 
\v 33 NiЙЎМ¶ijo Jesus me yatematitediogi niЙЎМ¶ijo oko nibodicetedi anele, ibake owidi natematiko anida ane iciaceeketetege liciagi niЙЎМ¶ijoa natematiko baanaЙЎМ¶a yatematitediogi. Inoka eetetece niЙЎМ¶ina anoyakadi moyowooЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ina oko.
\v 34 Codaa adatematikatediogi me daЙЎМ¶a ibaketeda natematigo anida ane iciaceeketege. Pida niЙЎМ¶ina noЙЎМ¶okiniwatece ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece, odaa Jesus ja yeloЙЎМ¶oditediogi niЙЎМ¶ica ane diitigi ijoatawece niЙЎМ¶ijoa ane diiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atetece.
\s1 Jesus yamaketedini niwocotaЙЎМ¶a
\r (Mateus 8.23-27; Lucas 8.22-25)
\p 
\v 35 NiЙЎМ¶ijo noko naЙЎМ¶a dawike, Jesus meetediogi niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece, вҖңIniЙЎМ¶a daato weiigi.вҖқ
\v 36 Odaa jiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶oyaladi niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi-nelegi, odaa joЙЎМ¶oyadeegi Jesus catinedi niwatece niЙЎМ¶ijo aneetedi naЙЎМ¶a ika me datematika, odaa jiЙЎМ¶igotibeci. Odaa ijoa eletidi niwateceli joЙЎМ¶odiotece.
\p 
\v 37 Pida codaaЙЎМ¶ida noЙЎМ¶onenagi ica niwocotaЙЎМ¶a. Odaa niЙЎМ¶icoa ebekadi nelecoli ja yalaketedibigeloco naЙЎМ¶ajo niwatece, odaa naЙЎМ¶ajo niwatece ja domaЙЎМ¶a nolee ninyoЙЎМ¶odi.
\v 38 Pida idiaa Jesus oneote lakaalaЙЎМ¶adi, odaa ja diote digoida lowiditice naЙЎМ¶ajo niwatece. Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece joЙЎМ¶oyojietelogo, odaa moditalo, вҖңЗӨoniiЙЎМ¶axinoЙЎМ¶odi, aЙЎМ¶ica mawiitioЙЎМ¶oji? NiЙЎМ¶ida moko ja jaaЙЎМ¶a!вҖқ
\p 
\v 39 Odaa Jesus jiЙЎМ¶itedibige, odaa ja yamaketedini niocodi, codaa meetediogi ebekadi, вҖңAnotokitiniwaci!вҖқ Odaa niocodi ja damatini, odaa ijoatawece damatiniwace.
\v 40 Odaa Jesus meetediogi, вҖңIgaamee ina madoiitiwaji? Igame leeЙЎМ¶odi me deЙЎМ¶ewi me iwaЙЎМ¶ati AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji?вҖқ
\p 
\v 41 Odaa eliodi modoitalo Jesus niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ijo loenatagi. Odaa dinigetiwage, modi, вҖңAmiidoa icoa ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa? IgaataЙЎМ¶a codaa me niocodi inaa ebekadi oyiwaЙЎМ¶adi!вҖқ
\c 5
\s1 Jesus icilatidi ica ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa ane dakatiogi niwigo abeyaceЙЎМ¶egi
\r (Mateus 8.28-34; Lucas 8.26-39)
\p 
\v 1 Jesus ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece naЙЎМ¶a diЙЎМ¶etita daato niweiigi GalilГ©ia, odaa joЙЎМ¶otota miditaЙЎМ¶a nipodigi ane liЙЎМ¶eladi noiigi geraseenotedi.
\v 2 NiЙЎМ¶ijo Jesus naЙЎМ¶a waxoditedice naЙЎМ¶ajo niwatece, aЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a leegi ja noditice ica ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa icoЙЎМ¶otiwece apiiЙЎМ¶o, odaa jiЙЎМ¶icotalo Jesus. NiЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa dakatiogi niwigo abeyaceЙЎМ¶egi.
\v 3 Ja liЙЎМ¶eladi minitaЙЎМ¶a apiiЙЎМ¶o midiwataЙЎМ¶a lawimaЙЎМ¶ajetedi-wetiadi anoyatedice niЙЎМ¶inoa Г©maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a. AonaЙЎМ¶aleeЙЎМ¶ica ane yakadi me niwilo niЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa, oteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina moibake galeena moigoetini.
\v 4 Onelioditibece niЙЎМ¶ina modibata, odaa joЙЎМ¶oigoe libaaЙЎМ¶atedi, codaa me loЙЎМ¶onaka oyatita galeena, pida idioka limedi me nakagidi niЙЎМ¶icoa galeenatedi, eote laЙЎМ¶aagetedawaanaЙЎМ¶a. Codaa aЙЎМ¶aleeЙЎМ¶ica ane yakadi me yajacaЙЎМ¶adi, leeЙЎМ¶odi ja daЙЎМ¶axa me yoniciwadi.
\v 5 Inoatawece nokododi codaa minoatawece enoaleli igoteloco apiiЙЎМ¶o codaa midiwa wetiadi, dapaawetibece, codaa dinanacilotidita wetiЙЎМ¶a.
\p 
\v 6 NiЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa naЙЎМ¶a naditege Jesus, walokoditege, odaa jeЙЎМ¶enitinigiiЙЎМ¶o lodoe Jesus.
\v 7 Odaa dapaawe, meetalo, вҖңAЙЎМ¶ica anejitaЙЎМ¶agi, Jesus. JaЙЎМ¶akamaЙЎМ¶akaami Lionigi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji aninoatawece notoetico. Jibake LiboonaЙЎМ¶adi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me jipokotaЙЎМ¶awa me daЙЎМ¶a adiloikatiti.вҖқ
\v 8 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo niwigo abeyaceЙЎМ¶egi eote niЙЎМ¶ijoa lotaЙЎМ¶a leeЙЎМ¶odi maleedaЙЎМ¶a dotaЙЎМ¶a, Jesus jaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a dotaЙЎМ¶a, meeteta, вҖңNiwigo abeyaceЙЎМ¶egi, anotitice niЙЎМ¶ini ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa!вҖқ
\v 9 Odaa Jesus ja ige niЙЎМ¶ijo niwigo abeyaceЙЎМ¶egi, meeteta, вҖңIgame ЙЎМ¶aboonaЙЎМ¶adi?вҖқ Odaa ja igidi, mee, вҖңIboonaЙЎМ¶adi вҖҳEliodi okoвҖҷ! LeeЙЎМ¶odi moko eliodi.вҖқ
\v 10 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo niwigo abeyaceЙЎМ¶egi eliodi me dipokotalo Jesus me daЙЎМ¶a iticoitedicoace me iiЙЎМ¶e moyaladi niЙЎМ¶idi nipodigi.
\p 
\v 11 Digoida maditaЙЎМ¶a naЙЎМ¶aca wetiЙЎМ¶a onini ica lapo nigidagiwadi, niodaЙЎМ¶a.
\v 12 Odaa ijoatawece niЙЎМ¶ijoa niwicidi abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a eliodi modipokotibigalo Jesus, moditalo, вҖңЗӨodikaneЙЎМ¶egi me iniЙЎМ¶a jakaЙЎМ¶atiogilo nigidagiwadi.вҖқ
\v 13 Odaa Jesus ja ikatedicoace me igotibeci, odaa niЙЎМ¶ijoa niwicidi abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a ja noditicoaci mijotaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa, odaa joЙЎМ¶odakatiogilo nigidagiwadi. Odaa ijotawece niЙЎМ¶ijo lapo nigidagiwadi walediticogi midataЙЎМ¶a wakagi iiЙЎМ¶o, odaa daxaboketiniwace, joЙЎМ¶oceЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a miditaЙЎМ¶a weiigi. Onijoa iniwata miili nigidagiwadi.
\p 
\v 14 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijoa ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi anoyowie nigidagiwadi ja ialeticoace. Odaa joЙЎМ¶oyatematitedibece manitaЙЎМ¶a nigotaЙЎМ¶a, codaa me niЙЎМ¶inoa nipodaЙЎМ¶a anototalo. Odaa eliodi oko igotibeci oiwi niЙЎМ¶ica niciagi.
\v 15 NiЙЎМ¶ijo noЙЎМ¶ototalo Jesus, odaa joЙЎМ¶onadi niЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa anodakatiogi niwicidi abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a. Odaa eliodi me doitibigiwaji niЙЎМ¶ijo noЙЎМ¶onadi niЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa me nicoti, codaa me dinixo, codaa aЙЎМ¶alee yetole.
\v 16 NiЙЎМ¶ijo anonadi niЙЎМ¶ijo niciagi oyatematitedibece anodaaЙЎМ¶eeteda niЙЎМ¶ijoa nigidagiwadi, codaa niЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa ane dakatiogi niwicidi abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a.
\v 17 Odaa joЙЎМ¶odipokotalo Jesus me noditedice niЙЎМ¶idi niiЙЎМ¶o.
\p 
\v 18 NiЙЎМ¶ijo Jesus naЙЎМ¶a waxoditedinigi naЙЎМ¶ajo niwatece mopi, niЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa anijo modakatiogi niwicidi abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a dipokotibigalo Jesus me domaЙЎМ¶a yemaa me lixigaЙЎМ¶awa.
\v 19 Pida Jesus ayemaa daЙЎМ¶a yadeegi, odaa meeteta, вҖңEmii, opilitacicogi ЙЎМ¶adiЙЎМ¶eladi, odaa atematiitiogi ЙЎМ¶adoiigiwepodi niЙЎМ¶ica ЗӨaniotagodi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji meote eliodi aneletaЙЎМ¶adomi, codaa eliodi me ЙЎМ¶adiwikodeni.вҖқ
\v 20 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa joЙЎМ¶opi, igo miditaЙЎМ¶a nipodigi ane liboonaЙЎМ¶adi вҖңDeez nigotadiвҖқ, odaa yatematitibece ijoatawece niЙЎМ¶icoa Jesus aneotetema. Odaa ijotawece niЙЎМ¶ijo oko eliodi moyopo.
\s1 Jairo dipokotalo Jesus me icilatidi liona
\r (Mateus 9.18-19; Lucas 8.40-42)
\p 
\v 21 Jesus naЙЎМ¶a diЙЎМ¶etacedita daato weiigi. Odaa ica noiigi-nelegi dinatecoЙЎМ¶oteetelogo liniogotibece weiigi.
\v 22 Onida ica ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa ane liboonaЙЎМ¶adi Jairo one eledi lacilo liiakanaЙЎМ¶axi judeutedi manitaЙЎМ¶a naЙЎМ¶ani nigotaЙЎМ¶a. Jairo lixigaЙЎМ¶awepodi niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi-nelegi. NiЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a nadi Jesus, odaa dakagitini lodoe.
\v 23 Odaa eliodi me dipokotalo Jesus, meetalo, вҖңJaЙЎМ¶adiaa ionawaana ja doletibige me yeleo. Anagi, ipekeniteloco ЙЎМ¶abaaЙЎМ¶atedi amaleeЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a icГӯ me deelotika, codaa amaleeЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a iwoko nГ©maЙЎМ¶a!вҖқ
\v 24 Odaa Jesus jiЙЎМ¶igo lixigaЙЎМ¶awa Jairo.
\s1 Jesus icilatidi aca iwaalo awodina
\r (Mateus 9.20-22; Lucas 8.43-48)
\p Eliodi oko lixigaЙЎМ¶awepodi Jesus codaa diniligice.
\v 25 Onajo liwigotigi niЙЎМ¶ijo oko aca iwaalo awodina. JoneЙЎМ¶eote dooze nicaaЙЎМ¶ape me leelotagi.
\v 26 Eliodi migotece dotowexedi, yaaЙЎМ¶adi icoatawece ninyeelo. Codaa eliodi me dawikode me diniwakateetibece, pida aЙЎМ¶ica ane dinilatece, pida jeЙЎМ¶epaanaЙЎМ¶a deelotika.
\v 27 NiЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a dibodice moyalaЙЎМ¶atalo Jesus, odaa dakatiogi liwigotigi niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi-nelegi, odaa nowidila Jesus, odaa dibatece nijayogo Jesus.
\v 28 LeeЙЎМ¶odi meetibige le, вҖңNige jakadi mokexaa jiba-aatece nijayogo, odaa ja idici.вҖқ
\p 
\v 29 Odaa ewi niЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a dibatece nijayogo Jesus, aЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a leegi niЙЎМ¶ijoa lawodi ja wakagitege, odaa ja deemitetece lolaadi naЙЎМ¶a icГӯ.
\v 30 NaЙЎМ¶ajo lakata Jesus yowooЙЎМ¶odi me noditice midoataЙЎМ¶a loniciwaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane icilatidi naЙЎМ¶ajo iwaalo, odaa naЙЎМ¶a nawiilitetetege niЙЎМ¶ijo lapo-nelegi, odaa ja digika, meetediogi, вҖңAmiijo ica ane dibatece inijayogo?вҖқ
\p 
\v 31 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece moditalo, вҖңIgame leeЙЎМ¶odi ina magikani mica ane dibataЙЎМ¶aloco, aЙЎМ¶anati minatawece niЙЎМ¶ina oko etiЙЎМ¶adiligiceni?вҖқ
\p 
\v 32 Pida Jesus niipete liwailidi me doletedibige me nadi niЙЎМ¶ica ane dibatece nijayogo.
\v 33 Odaa naЙЎМ¶ajo iwaalo jeЙЎМ¶enagi lodoe, odaa yamaЙЎМ¶atedini lokotidi, igaataЙЎМ¶a yowooЙЎМ¶odi mijo ane deemitetece lolaadi. Odaa dawigice, doi, odaa ja yatematitalo Jesus ijoatawece niЙЎМ¶ijoa baanaЙЎМ¶a ixomaЙЎМ¶ateetedice.
\v 34 Odaa Jesus meeteta, вҖңIona, ja ЙЎМ¶adicili leeЙЎМ¶odi manakatoni AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Emii, odaa jinaЙЎМ¶alee adinigecaЙЎМ¶aleЙЎМ¶eni. IgaataЙЎМ¶a ewi naЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶adicili.вҖқ
\s1 Jesus yewikatiditace Jairo liona
\r (Mateus 9.23-26; Lucas 8.49-56)
\p 
\v 35 Jesus eЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶eeteda me dotaЙЎМ¶a neЙЎМ¶enotibeci ica oko oicoЙЎМ¶oticogi liЙЎМ¶eladi Jairo, niЙЎМ¶ijo lacilo niiakanaЙЎМ¶axi. Odaa joЙЎМ¶owo leemidi Jairo, modita, вҖңЗӨadiona ja yeleo. AЙЎМ¶alee leeditibige daЙЎМ¶a anigiwocitedice niiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶a.вҖқ
\v 36 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo Jesus naЙЎМ¶a wajipate lotaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ijo oko, odaa meeteta Jairo, вҖңJinaЙЎМ¶adoii, pida anakatoni nimaweneЙЎМ¶egi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.вҖқ
\v 37 Odaa Jesus aЙЎМ¶ica ane ikatedio me lixigaЙЎМ¶awa, pida ijoka yadeegiteda Pedro, ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo itoataale dinioxomigipi Tiago ijaa JoГЈo me lixigaЙЎМ¶awepodi.
\v 38 NiЙЎМ¶ijo niЙЎМ¶icotiobeci Jairo liЙЎМ¶eladi, odaa Jesus ja nadi niЙЎМ¶ijo ninyaaЙЎМ¶a, igedi me nacaagaЙЎМ¶ateloco.
\v 39 NiЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a dakatediwece diimigi, odaa meetediogi, вҖңIgaameni macaagetibecetiwaji, codaa mawiite inoa ЙЎМ¶adayaageЙЎМ¶eco? NaЙЎМ¶adi nigaanawaana ayeleo, pida diote.вҖқ
\p 
\v 40 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi joЙЎМ¶oyame. Odaa Jesus ja iiЙЎМ¶e mijotawece noditicoaci. Odaa ja leyakawepodi eliododipi naЙЎМ¶adi nigaanawaana, ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo itoatadiЙЎМ¶ida anodiotibece, odaa dakatediwece catiwedi aneitice lolaadi naЙЎМ¶adi nigaanawaana, anidiwa dooze nicaaЙЎМ¶ape.
\v 41 Odaa Jesus naЙЎМ¶a dibatedigi libaaЙЎМ¶adi, meeteta, вҖңTalitГЎ cumi!вҖқ amina anejinaЙЎМ¶ata вҖңNigaanawaana, adabititini!вҖқ
\p 
\v 42 Odaa aЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a leegi naЙЎМ¶ajo nigaanawaana ja dabiditini, odaa jeЙЎМ¶ewaligi. Pida eliodi me nawelatibigiwaji, codaa moyopo niЙЎМ¶ijo anonadi.
\v 43 Odaa Jesus ja najoitacediniwace me doЙЎМ¶oyatemati niЙЎМ¶ida niciagi. Odaa ja diiЙЎМ¶enatakate mowo liweenigi naЙЎМ¶ajo nigaanawaana.
\c 6
\s1 NiЙЎМ¶eladimigipitigi nigotaЙЎМ¶a NazarГ© aЙЎМ¶onakato Jesus
\r (Mateus 13.53-58; Lucas 4.16-30)
\p 
\v 1 Jesus naЙЎМ¶a noditedice niЙЎМ¶ijo aneite, odaa joЙЎМ¶opitedicogi manitaЙЎМ¶a epaa nigotaЙЎМ¶a lixigaЙЎМ¶awepodi niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece.
\v 2 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ica naЙЎМ¶a saabado, jiЙЎМ¶igo mani liiakanaЙЎМ¶axi judeutedi, odaa ja dowicenaЙЎМ¶a me diiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶a. Odaa eliodi niЙЎМ¶ijo oko ane yatecoЙЎМ¶o oyopo niЙЎМ¶ijo noЙЎМ¶owajipatalo lotaЙЎМ¶a Jesus, odaa dinigetiwage, modi, вҖңIgamige niiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶adi me diniiЙЎМ¶axitetece niЙЎМ¶inoa liiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco? Amigijo ica ane yajigotalo lixakedi? IgamigodaaЙЎМ¶ee me yakadi meote niЙЎМ¶inoa ЙЎМ¶odoxiceЙЎМ¶etedi?
\v 3 NiЙЎМ¶idoa me jowooЙЎМ¶otaЙЎМ¶a geme gapinteelegi, codaa lionigi Maria, nioxoa Tiago, JosГ©, Judas ijaa SimГЈo. Idiaa niwaalepodi inaa liЙЎМ¶eladi digoina.вҖқ Odaa aЙЎМ¶ele modibatege Jesus.
\p 
\v 4 Pida Jesus meetediogi, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ina oko idioka limedi modeemitetibige niЙЎМ¶ina anoyeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece lowooko AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Pida inoka doЙЎМ¶odeemitetibige niЙЎМ¶ina niЙЎМ¶eladimigipitigi manitaЙЎМ¶a epaa nigotaЙЎМ¶a, idiaa litacepodi, codaa me loiigiwepodi.вҖқ
\p 
\v 5 Odaa Jesus ayakadi meote niЙЎМ¶inoa ЙЎМ¶odoxiceЙЎМ¶etedi nelecoli manitaЙЎМ¶a naЙЎМ¶ani epaa nigotaЙЎМ¶a. Idokida me ipeketedeloco libaaЙЎМ¶atedi onateciЙЎМ¶idiwa eelotaginadi me nicilatiditedini.
\v 6 Codaa Jesus eliodi me yopo leeЙЎМ¶odi me doЙЎМ¶onakatoteda.
\s1 Jesus iiЙЎМ¶e niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece moyatematitibece nibodicetedi anele
\r (Mateus 10.5-15; Lucas 9.1-6)
\p Odaa Jesus jiЙЎМ¶igotetece nigotadawaanaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶idi nipodigi, codaa niiЙЎМ¶axitediniwace oko.
\p 
\v 7 Odaa eniditediogi niЙЎМ¶ijo dooze anodiotibece, odaa ja iiЙЎМ¶e migotibeci itoataaletibece oyatematitedibece nibodicetedi anele. MaleediЙЎМ¶igotibeci, odaa ja yajigotediogi notoetiigi moyakadi moiticoitedice niwicidi abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a.
\v 8 Codaa meetediogi me diЙЎМ¶icata anonibatine me wiajeeЙЎМ¶a. Ijoka yajoitetece moyadeegi ligiilaЙЎМ¶adi. Pida aika doЙЎМ¶owo oyadeegi liawogo, oteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a nixacoola, oteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a dinyeelo catinedi ninyeelaЙЎМ¶axi anonigoetigi.
\v 9 Odaa iiЙЎМ¶etediogi modinixotinigi liwelatedi, codaa moyadeegi onadateci nitoonicogo.
\v 10 Odaa niЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi Jesus jeЙЎМ¶eetediogi, вҖңNigakaatiwecetiwaji anigini diimigi me idiaaЙЎМ¶onitice, odaa idiaaЙЎМ¶onitice minitaЙЎМ¶a nigepaa limedi manotitice naЙЎМ¶ani nigotaЙЎМ¶a.
\v 11 Nige deЙЎМ¶ele modibataЙЎМ¶agitiwaji anigidi niЙЎМ¶eladimigipi, codaa nige doЙЎМ¶oyemaa mowajipatalo ЙЎМ¶adatematiko, odaaЙЎМ¶opili. Niganotiticogitiwaji we, odaa iticiЙЎМ¶i amoЙЎМ¶o midoa ЙЎМ¶awelatedi me ikeenitiogi mepaa icoЙЎМ¶otiogi. EjitaЙЎМ¶awa niЙЎМ¶ica noko nigicota nige iloikatidi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji niЙЎМ¶ina oko leeЙЎМ¶odi libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco, iloikatidi niЙЎМ¶idi oko caticedi niЙЎМ¶ijo niЙЎМ¶eladimigipitigi nigotaЙЎМ¶a Sodoma ajaa Gomorra leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ijo oko daЙЎМ¶axa minoa libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco.вҖқ
\p 
\v 12 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece jiЙЎМ¶igotibeci, oyatematitiogi inatawece oko me leeditibige modinilaatece libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco.
\v 13 Codaa moiticoitedice owidi niwicidi abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a. Codaa moyatikoleteloco lajidi oliveira lacilo eliodi oko eelotaginadi, odaa joЙЎМ¶onicilatiditiniwace.
\s1 LemeЙЎМ¶egi JoГЈo Batista
\r (Mateus 14.1-12; Lucas 9.7-9)
\p 
\v 14 Herodes niЙЎМ¶ijo inionigi-eliodi dibodicetalo icoatawece niЙЎМ¶icoa Jesus loenataka, leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶eladimigipitigi owidi nigotadi oyalaЙЎМ¶atalo. Onica ica oko anodi, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶idoa JoГЈo Batista AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ja yewikatiditace. JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi mida notoetiigi meote niЙЎМ¶inoa ЙЎМ¶odoxiceЙЎМ¶etedi.вҖқ
\v 15 Pida ica eledi oko modi, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶idoa Elias.вҖқ Odaa ica eledi modi, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶idoa anigepidiЙЎМ¶ica niЙЎМ¶ijo anoyeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lowooko, niЙЎМ¶ijo baanaЙЎМ¶a nigo niЙЎМ¶ijo jotigide!вҖқ
\p 
\v 16 Pida niЙЎМ¶ijo Herodes naЙЎМ¶a wajipatibece moyalaЙЎМ¶atalo niЙЎМ¶ica oko, moditece Jesus, odaa mee, вҖңEe mejimewi niЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ida JoГЈo Batista, niЙЎМ¶ijo ane jiiЙЎМ¶enatakata moyakagiditice lotoinaЙЎМ¶adi. Ja yewiЙЎМ¶atace!вҖқ
\p 
\v 17 IgaataЙЎМ¶a Herodes jiЙЎМ¶ijaa diiЙЎМ¶enatakata moigoetini JoГЈo, odaa joЙЎМ¶oixotiwece niwiloЙЎМ¶onaЙЎМ¶axi. Eo niЙЎМ¶ida anigota JoГЈo leeЙЎМ¶ote Herodias, naЙЎМ¶ajo lodawa Filipe, niЙЎМ¶ijo nioxoa iniaaЙЎМ¶ini Herodes. Herodes dibanoonaЙЎМ¶atece Herodias.
\v 18 JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi JoГЈo midioka limedi meetibiga Herodes, вҖңLiiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji yolitaЙЎМ¶adomi me ЙЎМ¶adodawa ЙЎМ¶anioxoa lodawa.вҖқ
\p 
\v 19 Odaa Herodias eliodi me yelatema JoГЈo, domaЙЎМ¶a yemaa daЙЎМ¶a yeloadi. Pida aЙЎМ¶ica nimaweneЙЎМ¶egi.
\v 20 IgaataЙЎМ¶a Herodes doita JoГЈo, leeЙЎМ¶odi yowooЙЎМ¶odi JoГЈo me ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a ane dibatema iniokiniwateda AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Odaa Herodes aika diЙЎМ¶ica JoГЈo ninyaagi. Herodes lemaanigi me wajipata JoГЈo, pida niЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a wajipatalo lotaЙЎМ¶a, eliodi me doЙЎМ¶owikomata, aЙЎМ¶alee yowooЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ica anee.
\p 
\v 21 Pida jiЙЎМ¶icota ica noko Herodias me yakadi nimaweneЙЎМ¶egi meo ane beyagitema JoГЈo. NiЙЎМ¶ica noko me nakatio lanikegi Herodes. Odaa Herodes jeЙЎМ¶eo nalokegi, ja nodetiogi niЙЎМ¶ijo ane niiЙЎМ¶enatakanaЙЎМ¶a ijaaЙЎМ¶ijoa niЙЎМ¶ijoa lacilodi iodaЙЎМ¶awadi codaa me niЙЎМ¶eladimigipitigi ane ЙЎМ¶oneЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a nipodigi GalilГ©ia.
\v 22 Odaa aca liona Herodias ja dakatiwece aneiticoace me nalooЙЎМ¶o, odaa ja dinibaile. Herodes ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo lodenigipi eliodi moyemaa nibaileЙЎМ¶eco. Odaa inionigi-eliodi Herodes meeta naЙЎМ¶ajo awicije, вҖңAnipokitiwa niЙЎМ¶ica anemaani, odaa jajigotaЙЎМ¶awa.вҖқ
\v 23 Odaa jeЙЎМ¶eo ligegitege, meeta, вҖңOkanicodaaЙЎМ¶ica ananipokitiwa, jajigotaЙЎМ¶awa, codaa me liwai inatawece niЙЎМ¶ina ane jiiЙЎМ¶e.вҖқ
\p 
\v 24 Odaa naЙЎМ¶ajo awicije ja noditice, odaa jiЙЎМ¶igo ige naЙЎМ¶ajo eliodo, meeta, вҖңAmiini ica ane jipokotigi?вҖқ Odaa niniЙЎМ¶odi, meeta, вҖңIpokita lacilo JoГЈo Batista.вҖқ
\p 
\v 25 Odaa aЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a leegi naЙЎМ¶ajo awicije ja yediiЙЎМ¶a me dakatacio minitaЙЎМ¶a inionigi-eliodi, odaa meeta, вҖңJemaa lacilo JoГЈo Batista exakitinigi ЙЎМ¶inogo niЙЎМ¶ina natigide.вҖқ
\p 
\v 26 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo inionigi-eliodi eliodi magecaЙЎМ¶alo. Pida ayemaa me anojicetema naЙЎМ¶ajo awicije leeЙЎМ¶odi jeЙЎМ¶eo ligegitege, codaa leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ijo nodenigipi moiwita.
\v 27 Odaa aЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a leegi ja iiЙЎМ¶e onijoteci niЙЎМ¶ijoa iodaЙЎМ¶awadi migo manitaЙЎМ¶a niwiloЙЎМ¶onaЙЎМ¶axi me yakagiditice lotoinaЙЎМ¶adi JoГЈo. Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo iodaЙЎМ¶awa jiЙЎМ¶igo, odaa ja yakagiditice JoГЈo lotoinaЙЎМ¶adi manitaЙЎМ¶a niwiloЙЎМ¶onaЙЎМ¶axi.
\v 28 Odaa ja nadeegi JoГЈo lacilo yexaЙЎМ¶atinigi ЙЎМ¶inogo, odaa ja yajigota naЙЎМ¶ajo awicije. Odaa naЙЎМ¶ajo awicije jiЙЎМ¶igo yajigota naЙЎМ¶ajo eliodo.
\v 29 NiЙЎМ¶ijo noЙЎМ¶odibodiceta niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibeci JoГЈo niЙЎМ¶ida niciagi, jiЙЎМ¶igotibeci aneitice, odaa joЙЎМ¶oyadeegi lolaadi JoГЈo, monaligitini.
\s1 Jesus niodeЙЎМ¶etedini ica noiigi-nelegi
\r (Mateus 14.13-21; Lucas 9.10-17; JoГЈo 6.1-14)
\p 
\v 30 NiЙЎМ¶ijoa dooze ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi ane iiЙЎМ¶e Jesus moyatemati latematigo naЙЎМ¶a dopitibeci, odaa joЙЎМ¶oyatematitalo Jesus ijoatawece loenataka codaa ane odiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atece.
\v 31 Odaa Jesus meetediogi, вҖңAnagi! IniЙЎМ¶a mokomokoko miditaЙЎМ¶a nipodigi ane daxixe ane diЙЎМ¶ica niЙЎМ¶eladimigipi me inipenakawaanigi.вҖқ LeeЙЎМ¶odi eliodi oko igotibeci miditaЙЎМ¶a, inaaЙЎМ¶eledi baanaЙЎМ¶a dopitibeci, odaa Jesus ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece aЙЎМ¶aleeЙЎМ¶ica nimedi me niodaЙЎМ¶a.
\v 32 Odaa joЙЎМ¶owaxoditinigi aca niwatece, odaa ijokijo migotibeci miditaЙЎМ¶a nipodigi ane daxixe, ane diЙЎМ¶ica oko.
\p 
\v 33 Pida eliodi oko onadi niЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a noditicoaci, codaa oyowooЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo. Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo oko waleditece liniogotibece weiigi. NiЙЎМ¶ica oko oicoЙЎМ¶oticogi inoatawece ane nigotadawaanaЙЎМ¶a, odaa odoejedipi mototicogi ane diitedicogi Jesus ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece.
\v 34 NiЙЎМ¶ijo Jesus naЙЎМ¶a waxoditedice naЙЎМ¶ajo niwatece, odaa ja nadi niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi-nelegi. Odaa eliodi me iwikodetediogi, leeЙЎМ¶odi iciaceeketetege niЙЎМ¶inoa waxacocoli ane diЙЎМ¶ica nowienoЙЎМ¶odi. Odaa jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶eyatedigi me niiЙЎМ¶axitediniwace niЙЎМ¶ijo oko, codaa owidi niЙЎМ¶icoa ane iiЙЎМ¶axitetece.
\p 
\v 35 NiЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a doletibige me dawike, niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece Jesus jiЙЎМ¶igotibeci midoataЙЎМ¶a, odaa moditalo, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ina nipodigi anejonaЙЎМ¶a aЙЎМ¶ica niЙЎМ¶eladimigipi codaa ja ЙЎМ¶ocidi.
\v 36 IiЙЎМ¶eni niЙЎМ¶ina noiigi mopitibeci, amaleeЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a igotibeci niЙЎМ¶inoa bajeendatedi inaaЙЎМ¶inoa nigotadawaanaЙЎМ¶a modinoojetetibige liweenigi.вҖқ
\p 
\v 37 Pida Jesus ja igidi, meetediogi, вҖңAkamaЙЎМ¶akaamitiwaji ajicitiogi anoyeligo niЙЎМ¶ina noiigi!вҖқ Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece moditalo, вҖңOkomoЙЎМ¶oko jinoojeteeЙЎМ¶atibige paon anoyeligo? IgaataЙЎМ¶a loojedi dibata iniwata-taalia beexotedi, ane loojedi oito epenaitedi me jibaaЙЎМ¶a!вҖқ
\p 
\v 38 Odaa Jesus meetediogi, вҖңDigemii awini! Igame liwokodi ЙЎМ¶anipaontedi?вҖқ Odaa jiЙЎМ¶igotibeci oiwi, odaa moditalo, вҖңIdiwa onexaa ciinco paontedi idiaaЙЎМ¶idiwa itiodataale noЙЎМ¶ojedi.вҖқ
\p 
\v 39 Odaa Jesus ja iiЙЎМ¶e niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi-nelegi me dilapodetibece me nicotiniwace miditaЙЎМ¶a nadegocawaanigi.
\v 40 Odaa ja nicotiniwace ini lapo anidiwa onaniteci taalia oko, iniaaЙЎМ¶eledi lapo onidiwa meya-taalia oko.
\v 41 Odaa Jesus ja dibatetege niЙЎМ¶ijoa ciinco paontedi ijaaЙЎМ¶ijoa itiwataale noЙЎМ¶ojedi, naЙЎМ¶a iwitedibigimece ditibigimedi, odaa ja diniotagodeteta AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Odaa ja inoketedigi liwigotigi niЙЎМ¶ijoa paontedi, odaa yajigotediogi niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece monediatiniwace niЙЎМ¶idi noiigi-nelegi. Odaa jaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a ninoketedini niЙЎМ¶ijoa noЙЎМ¶ojedi, odaa joЙЎМ¶oyajigotiogi niЙЎМ¶idi oko.
\v 42 Odaa iditawece niЙЎМ¶idi oko niodaЙЎМ¶a, codaa nitiminaЙЎМ¶a.
\v 43 NiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece joЙЎМ¶onoleenaЙЎМ¶adi dooze etacani liwailidi niЙЎМ¶ijoa paontedi ijaaЙЎМ¶ijoa noЙЎМ¶ojedi ane iiЙЎМ¶otedice anoyapitelogo niЙЎМ¶ijo oko.
\v 44 Onicoa ciinco miili ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi ane niodaЙЎМ¶a, pida baadoЙЎМ¶onilaЙЎМ¶adi nigaanigipawaanigi idiaa iwaalepodi anaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a niodaЙЎМ¶a.
\s1 Jesus ewaligitedeloco ditibigimedi ninyoЙЎМ¶odi
\r (Mateus 14.22-33; JoГЈo 6.15-21)
\p 
\v 45 AЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a leegi Jesus iiЙЎМ¶e niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece mowaxoditinigi naЙЎМ¶ajo niwatece me dinewadetibigiwaji manitaЙЎМ¶a nigotakawaana ane liboonaЙЎМ¶adi Betsaida ane idei daato weiigi. IiЙЎМ¶e me igotibeci, niЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a ibodetediogi niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi-nelegi.
\v 46 NiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi naЙЎМ¶a ibodetediogi niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi-nelegi, Jesus jiЙЎМ¶igo manitaЙЎМ¶a aca wetiЙЎМ¶a me yotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶e AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.
\v 47 NiЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a doletibige me dalimeti aligeЙЎМ¶e, naЙЎМ¶ajo niwatece ideitice liwigotinigi niЙЎМ¶ijo weiigi, idaa Jesus neniЙЎМ¶idoatece digoida daato weiigi.
\v 48 Pida naditediogi niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece me dinoniciwaЙЎМ¶aditibigiwaji me nolaakanaЙЎМ¶a, leeЙЎМ¶odi odiitege niocodi. NiЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a ixomaЙЎМ¶atedice iniwatadaЙЎМ¶ani lakata me nigoitijo, maleedaЙЎМ¶a yeloЙЎМ¶otigi, Jesus jiЙЎМ¶igo miditaЙЎМ¶a. Ewaligitedeloco ninyoЙЎМ¶odi, odaa domaЙЎМ¶a yewegitedijo.
\v 49 NiЙЎМ¶ijo noЙЎМ¶onadi Jesus mewaligitedeloco ditibigimedi ninyoЙЎМ¶odi, odaa odiletibige daЙЎМ¶a niwigo, odaa napaawaЙЎМ¶ateloco.
\v 50 NacaagaЙЎМ¶ateloco leeЙЎМ¶odi iditawece onaditege, odaa eliodi me doitibigiwaji. Pida aЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a leegi Jesus meetediogi, вҖңEloodaЙЎМ¶ateeni ЙЎМ¶adaaleЙЎМ¶enalitiwaji! JeЙЎМ¶emeЙЎМ¶ee! JinaЙЎМ¶adoiitiwaji!вҖқ
\v 51 Odaa ja waxoditedinigi naЙЎМ¶ajo niwatece, odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo niocodi ja notokoti. Eliodi me nawelatibigiwaji, codaa aЙЎМ¶aleeЙЎМ¶oyowooЙЎМ¶odi anee.
\v 52 IgaataЙЎМ¶a aЙЎМ¶oyowooЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ica notoetiigi, idaaЙЎМ¶ee monadi niЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶odoxiceЙЎМ¶edi aneote naЙЎМ¶a yowidaЙЎМ¶atee niЙЎМ¶ijoa paontedi, leeЙЎМ¶odi me dakake laaleЙЎМ¶enali.
\s1 Jesus icilatidi eliodi oko eelotaginadi miditaЙЎМ¶a nipodigi GenesarГ©
\r (Mateus 14.34-36)
\p 
\v 53 NiЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a diЙЎМ¶etitacicoace daato weiigi, odaa joЙЎМ¶otota nipodigi GenesarГ©, odaa joЙЎМ¶oigoetini naЙЎМ¶ajo niwatece liniogotibece weiigi.
\v 54 NiЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a waxoditicoace naЙЎМ¶ajo niwatece, aЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a leegi, niЙЎМ¶ijo oko joЙЎМ¶oyowooЙЎМ¶oditege Jesus.
\v 55 Odaa joЙЎМ¶owalediteloco iditawece nipodigi, onadeegitalo niЙЎМ¶inoa eelotaginadi, niЙЎМ¶ina baanaЙЎМ¶a odiwoteloco nipe. Oyadeegiticogi niЙЎМ¶ijo anodi migotetece Jesus.
\v 56 Odaa Jesus igotetedeloco niЙЎМ¶icoa nigotadawaanaЙЎМ¶a, nigotadi codaa me nipodaЙЎМ¶a. Icoatawece niЙЎМ¶icoa ane licoli, odaa idiaaЙЎМ¶oyaticoace niЙЎМ¶ijoa eelotaginadi aneitice niЙЎМ¶ina oko me dakapetibigiwage, odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo oko odipokotalo Jesus me ika niЙЎМ¶ijoa eelotaginadi mokexaa odibateloco laxabi nijayogo. Odaa ijotawece niЙЎМ¶ijo eelotaginadi anodibateloco nijayogo ja nicilaЙЎМ¶a.
\c 7
\s1 LiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco laamipi judeutedi niЙЎМ¶ica jotigide
\r (Mateus 15.1-9)
\p 
\v 1 NiЙЎМ¶ijoa fariseutedi ijaaЙЎМ¶ijoa icoa niiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anadi anodiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atece lajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco MoisГ©s oicoЙЎМ¶oticogi nigotaЙЎМ¶a JerusalГ©m. Odaa oyatecoЙЎМ¶otelogo Jesus.
\v 2 Onadi anigepidiЙЎМ¶ica niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece Jesus moyeligo paon me doЙЎМ¶oiwilegiteda libaaЙЎМ¶atedi, odaa joЙЎМ¶odinapeteЙЎМ¶etege, leeЙЎМ¶odi baЙЎМ¶a lakatigi niЙЎМ¶ijoa fariseutedi mecoЙЎМ¶otace niwilecaЙЎМ¶a nigepaa nige niodaЙЎМ¶a.
\p 
\v 3 LeeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ijoa fariseutedi codaa miditawece noiigi judeutedi odioteci lakatigi niЙЎМ¶ica laamipi. AЙЎМ¶ica anoyeligo nige deЙЎМ¶ele moiwilegi libaaЙЎМ¶atedi.
\v 4 NiЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a dopiticoace moicoЙЎМ¶oticogi balaacogolawaanaЙЎМ¶a aneitedice niЙЎМ¶inoa enaanaЙЎМ¶a, odaa ja diniwilegitibigiwaji. Codaa odioteci niЙЎМ¶icoa eletidi nakataЙЎМ¶a, niЙЎМ¶ina moiwilegi goopatedi, bootitedi nelecoli, nooleli, codaa me nipeli.
\p 
\v 5 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijoa fariseutedi ijaaЙЎМ¶ijoa niЙЎМ¶ijoa niiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anadi anodiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atece najoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco oige Jesus, moditalo, вҖңIgame leeЙЎМ¶odi idiwa anodiotibigaЙЎМ¶adici me doЙЎМ¶odioteci lakataЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶odaamipi, niodaЙЎМ¶a me doЙЎМ¶oiwilegiteda libaaЙЎМ¶atedi?вҖқ
\p 
\v 6 Jesus niniЙЎМ¶odi, meetediogi, вҖңAkaamitiwaji niЙЎМ¶ina anokeo mele! IsaГӯas, niЙЎМ¶ijo ane yatematitedibece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lowooko niЙЎМ¶ijo jotigide, eetece niЙЎМ¶ina anewi, niЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a yalaЙЎМ¶ataЙЎМ¶awatiwaji. MaditaЙЎМ¶a lotaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji iwoteloco niЙЎМ¶ica IsaГӯas ane yalaЙЎМ¶ata, niЙЎМ¶ijo neЙЎМ¶ee niЙЎМ¶ica AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ligegi, anee,
\q1 вҖҳNiЙЎМ¶idi noiigi etidiweniЙЎМ¶ide niЙЎМ¶ina me notaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶a,
\q1 pida aЙЎМ¶etidemaa catiwedi laaleЙЎМ¶enali,
\q1 codaa leegitiwa metidetecetice.
\q1 
\v 7 AЙЎМ¶ica jaoЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina modoЙЎМ¶etetiwa,
\q1 igaataЙЎМ¶a odiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atece niЙЎМ¶inoa lowooko niЙЎМ¶ina oko micataЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶a yowooko.вҖҷ
\p 
\v 8 Odaa akaamitiwaji jiЙЎМ¶ikani niЙЎМ¶inoa liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, pida jiЙЎМ¶iwitecetiwaji lakataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶inoa ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi niЙЎМ¶ina moiwilegi bootitedi, goopatedi, codaa mawii niЙЎМ¶inoa eletidi anicinoa.вҖқ
\p 
\v 9 Odaa Jesus meetediogi, вҖңInoa owidi ЙЎМ¶animaweneЙЎМ¶ecotiwaji me daЙЎМ¶awii niЙЎМ¶ijo liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶egi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji awiitibige makati me iwitece niЙЎМ¶inoa akamaЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶adakataЙЎМ¶atiwaji.
\v 10 IgaataЙЎМ¶a MoisГ©s mee niЙЎМ¶ijo jotigide, вҖҳAweniЙЎМ¶ideni ЙЎМ¶adiodi aniaa ЙЎМ¶adiodo!вҖҷ Codaa eledi mee, вҖҳLeeditibige moyeloadi niЙЎМ¶ijo oko ane beyagi me dotaЙЎМ¶atibige eliodi codaa me eliodo.вҖҷ
\v 11 Pida menitibecetiwaji nigica oko anida nimaweneЙЎМ¶egi me yaxawa eliodi codaa me eliodo, pida nigeeta eliodi aniaa eliodo, вҖҳIda CorbanвҖҷ (ane diitigi вҖҳiboonigi ane jajigotalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶ojiвҖҷ). Odaa aЙЎМ¶alee leeditibige me yaxawa eliodi aniaa eliodo.
\v 12 NiЙЎМ¶ida aneni aЙЎМ¶aleeЙЎМ¶ikanitiwaji niЙЎМ¶ijo oko me yaxawa eliodi aniaa eliodo.
\v 13 JaЙЎМ¶awiitiwaji me diЙЎМ¶ica ane jaoЙЎМ¶a liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji leeЙЎМ¶odi me iwitecetiwaji lakataЙЎМ¶a anetiЙЎМ¶adiiЙЎМ¶axinitece ЙЎМ¶adaamipi. JiЙЎМ¶inoatiwaji owidi eletidi ЙЎМ¶abatico niЙЎМ¶ida ЙЎМ¶abatiigi anejita.вҖқ
\s1 Jesus yalaЙЎМ¶ate niЙЎМ¶ica aneo me napioi ЙЎМ¶odaaleЙЎМ¶ena
\r (Mateus 15.10-20)
\p 
\v 14 Jesus eniditacediogi niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi menagitacibeci midoataЙЎМ¶a, odaa meetediogi, вҖңAkaamitawecetiwaji, ajipaatalo niЙЎМ¶inoa yotaЙЎМ¶a, codaa jemaa mowooЙЎМ¶otitiwaji!
\v 15 Inoatawece ane jelicaЙЎМ¶a jakataЙЎМ¶ate we, odaa dakatiwece ЙЎМ¶onioladi. Odaa niЙЎМ¶ina ane icoЙЎМ¶oticogi we anapioyaЙЎМ¶adi ЙЎМ¶odaaleЙЎМ¶ena. Pida niЙЎМ¶inoa notaЙЎМ¶a ane noditedicogi ЙЎМ¶onioladi, inaaЙЎМ¶inoa ЙЎМ¶olidaЙЎМ¶ataka ane icoЙЎМ¶otiwece ЙЎМ¶odaaleЙЎМ¶ena, jiЙЎМ¶inaaЙЎМ¶owo me napioi ЙЎМ¶odaaleЙЎМ¶ena.
\v 16 NiЙЎМ¶ina oko anowajipatalo yotaЙЎМ¶a leeditibige mowatacotece.вҖқ
\p 
\v 17 NiЙЎМ¶ijo Jesus naЙЎМ¶a yetecetedicoace niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi-nelegi, ja dakatediwece diimigi, odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece joЙЎМ¶oige, moditalo, вҖңIgame diitigilo ijoa ЙЎМ¶adotaЙЎМ¶a.вҖқ
\v 18 Odaa meetediogi, вҖңLatopiwatigi me daЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶ica anaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a owooЙЎМ¶otitiwaji. ЗӨoweenigi ane dakatiwece ЙЎМ¶onioladi ayakadi me napioyaЙЎМ¶adi ЙЎМ¶odaaleЙЎМ¶ena.
\v 19 IgaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina niweenigi adakatiwece ЙЎМ¶odaaleЙЎМ¶ena, pida baЙЎМ¶a dakatinece ЙЎМ¶owokomaЙЎМ¶a, odaa niЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi ja noditice.вҖқ (JiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee Jesus me ikee me jakataЙЎМ¶a me jelicaЙЎМ¶a okanicodaaЙЎМ¶ica niweenigi.)
\p 
\v 20 Odaa Jesus eledi yalaЙЎМ¶ate, mee, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ica ane napioyaЙЎМ¶adi niЙЎМ¶ina oko laaleЙЎМ¶ena niЙЎМ¶ina ane noditice, ane icoЙЎМ¶otiwece laaleЙЎМ¶ena, codaa niЙЎМ¶inoa lotaЙЎМ¶a ane icoЙЎМ¶otiwece nioladi.
\v 21 IgaataЙЎМ¶a digawini niЙЎМ¶ina ane icoЙЎМ¶otiwece ЙЎМ¶odaaleЙЎМ¶ena; ЙЎМ¶odowooko ane beyagi, ina me jilidaЙЎМ¶ataЙЎМ¶a me ЙЎМ¶odoomatewa lodawa eledi oko, codaa me ewocomigipi, ina me jilidaЙЎМ¶ataЙЎМ¶a me jolicaЙЎМ¶a, codaa me jaijeeЙЎМ¶a.
\v 22 Odaa catiwedi ЙЎМ¶odaaleЙЎМ¶ena icoЙЎМ¶otiwece ЙЎМ¶olidekico, codaa me jilidaЙЎМ¶ataЙЎМ¶a me jaoЙЎМ¶a okanicodaaЙЎМ¶ica ane beyagi, codaa me jiwitakaЙЎМ¶a, codaa me jaoЙЎМ¶a okanicodaaЙЎМ¶ica niЙЎМ¶ina ЙЎМ¶odolaadi ane yemaa meo, ina me ЙЎМ¶odocetema eledi oko, codaa me beyagi me jotaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶atibige eledi oko, codaa meo moko anaЙЎМ¶axakeneЙЎМ¶egi, codaa niЙЎМ¶inoa ЙЎМ¶olidaЙЎМ¶ataka owo me beyagi me jowookonaЙЎМ¶a micataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina yetole.
\v 23 Inatawece niЙЎМ¶ina ane beyagi icoЙЎМ¶otiwece catiwedi ЙЎМ¶odaaleЙЎМ¶ena, odaa jeЙЎМ¶eo me napioi ЙЎМ¶odaaleЙЎМ¶ena.вҖқ
\s1 Ica eliwaЙЎМ¶atakaneЙЎМ¶egi aca iwaalo ane daЙЎМ¶a judeu
\r (Mateus 15.21-28)
\p 
\v 24 Jesus noditedice niЙЎМ¶ijo aneitedice, odaa jiЙЎМ¶igo nipodigi ane ipegitege niЙЎМ¶ijoa nigotadi Tiro aniaa Sidom. NiЙЎМ¶ijo niЙЎМ¶icotedio, odaa naЙЎМ¶a dakatediwece ica diimigi, adomaЙЎМ¶a yemaa diЙЎМ¶ica ane yowooЙЎМ¶odi miniwa catiwedi diimigi. Pida aЙЎМ¶ica nimaweneЙЎМ¶egi me dinaЙЎМ¶aditedini.
\v 25-26 Onaca aca iwaalo ane daЙЎМ¶a judeu, pida loiigi siro-fenГӯcia. Onani aca liona ane dakatiogi niwigo abeyaceЙЎМ¶egi. NiЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a dibodicetigi Jesus, odaa aЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a leegi, odaa jiЙЎМ¶igo midoataЙЎМ¶a, odaa ja yamaЙЎМ¶atedini lokotidi lodoe. Odaa eliodi me dipokotalo Jesus me iticoitedice niЙЎМ¶ijo niwigo abeyaceЙЎМ¶egi ane dakatiogi liona.
\v 27 Pida Jesus meeteta, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ina me niodaЙЎМ¶a, leeditibige modoejedipi nionigipi me niodaЙЎМ¶a. IgaataЙЎМ¶a aЙЎМ¶ele doЙЎМ¶onoЙЎМ¶a liweenigi nionigipi, oditaЙЎМ¶a oyajigotiogi necexodi.вҖқ
\v 28 Pida naЙЎМ¶ajo iwaalo ja igidi, meetalo, вҖңEwi, Iniwa-aagodi. Pida niЙЎМ¶inoda necexodawaanaЙЎМ¶a ane idi-iite catiwedi nameeja oyeligo niЙЎМ¶inoa latijedi niЙЎМ¶ina niga-aanigipawaanigi.вҖқ
\v 29 Odaa Jesus ja igidi, meeteta, вҖңLeeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶inoa ЙЎМ¶adotaЙЎМ¶a ane ikee manakatoni AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, opiliticogi ЙЎМ¶adiЙЎМ¶eladi, igaataЙЎМ¶a niwigo abeyaceЙЎМ¶egi ja noditice majotaЙЎМ¶a naЙЎМ¶ajo ЙЎМ¶adiona.вҖқ
\v 30 NaЙЎМ¶ajo iwaalo niЙЎМ¶icoticogi liЙЎМ¶eladi, odaa icoteloco naЙЎМ¶ajo liona me iwoteloco nipe, codaa niЙЎМ¶ijo niwigo abeyaceЙЎМ¶egi aЙЎМ¶aleeЙЎМ¶ica, ja noditice majotaЙЎМ¶a naЙЎМ¶ajo liona.
\s1 Jesus icilatidi ica ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa aticilonaЙЎМ¶a codaa me ewaloЙЎМ¶onaЙЎМ¶a
\p 
\v 31 NiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi Jesus ja noditedicogi niЙЎМ¶idi nipodigi ane ipegitege niЙЎМ¶ijoa nigotadi Tiro aniaa Sidom, odaa ja ixomaЙЎМ¶atedicogi nipodigi ane liboonaЙЎМ¶adi вҖңDeez nigotadiвҖқ, odaa jiЙЎМ¶icotedicogi miditaЙЎМ¶a niweiigi GalilГ©ia.
\v 32 Odaa joЙЎМ¶onadeegitalo Jesus ica ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa aticilonaЙЎМ¶a codaa me ewaloЙЎМ¶onaЙЎМ¶a, odaa joЙЎМ¶odipokotalo Jesus me ipeketedeloco libaaЙЎМ¶atedi niЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa me icilatidi.
\v 33 Jesus yadeegitedicogi niЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa wetice niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi-nelegi, odaa yojogotediwece napaaЙЎМ¶ate niЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa yatite nibedona. Codaa yawale nibedona, odaa ja dibatedeloco loceligi niЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa yocelate lawale.
\v 34 Odaa iwitedibigimece ditibigimedi, odaa nikatedice laadi. Odaa mee, вҖңEfatГЎ!вҖқ niЙЎМ¶ina anejinaЙЎМ¶ata, вҖңOmoke!вҖқ
\p 
\v 35 Odaa aЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a leegi niЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa ja wajipa, codaa jeЙЎМ¶ele loceligi, odaa ja yakadi me dotaЙЎМ¶a.
\v 36 Jesus iiЙЎМ¶e niЙЎМ¶ijo anonadi me doЙЎМ¶oyatemati niЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶odoxiceЙЎМ¶edi. Pida idaaЙЎМ¶ida me domaЙЎМ¶a iiЙЎМ¶etediogi me doЙЎМ¶oyatemati, pida joЙЎМ¶oyatemati oiЙЎМ¶axake niЙЎМ¶ijo anonadi.
\v 37 NiЙЎМ¶ijo oko eliodi moyopo, odaa modi, вҖңInoatawece aneote, ele meote. Codaa eote niЙЎМ¶inoa aticilonadi me najipaaЙЎМ¶a, codaa niЙЎМ¶inoa ewaloЙЎМ¶onadi me notaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶a!вҖқ
\c 8
\s1 Jesus niodeЙЎМ¶etedini ica cwaatolo miili oko
\r (Mateus 15.32-39)
\p 
\v 1 NiЙЎМ¶ijoa nokododi dinatecoЙЎМ¶oteetace niЙЎМ¶ica noiigi-nelegi, codaa aЙЎМ¶aleeЙЎМ¶ica gaantokaaЙЎМ¶ini anoyeligo. Odaa Jesus jeЙЎМ¶eniditediogi niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece migotibeci midoataЙЎМ¶a, odaa meetediogi,
\v 2 вҖңJa jiwikode niЙЎМ¶ina noiigi, igaataЙЎМ¶a jeЙЎМ¶eote itoatadiЙЎМ¶ida nokododi mina meetaЙЎМ¶a, odaa aЙЎМ¶aleeЙЎМ¶ica gaantokaaЙЎМ¶idi anoyeligo.
\v 3 DaЙЎМ¶a jiiЙЎМ¶eticogi liЙЎМ¶elatedi me diЙЎМ¶icata anoyeligo, odaa daЙЎМ¶a yemaa idi anenitiniwace naigitece leeЙЎМ¶odi nabocaЙЎМ¶a, igaataЙЎМ¶a idi ane icoЙЎМ¶oticogi ditigedi.вҖқ
\p 
\v 4 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece joЙЎМ¶oigidi, moditalo, вҖңIgamigetiЙЎМ¶ida ica ЙЎМ¶onimaweneЙЎМ¶egi me jakataЙЎМ¶a paontedi me jiniodeЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶atiniwace niЙЎМ¶idi noiigi-nelegi? IgaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina nipodigi aЙЎМ¶ica niЙЎМ¶eladimigipi.вҖқ
\v 5 Odaa Jesus ja nigetediniwace, meetediogi, вҖңIgame liwokodi ЙЎМ¶anipaontedi?вҖқ Odaa joЙЎМ¶oigidi, moditalo, вҖңIdiwa seete paontedi.вҖқ
\p 
\v 6 Odaa Jesus ja iiЙЎМ¶e niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi-nelegi monicotinigiiЙЎМ¶o. Odaa ja dibate niЙЎМ¶ijoa seete paontedi, odaa diniotagodete AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Odaa naЙЎМ¶a inoketedigi liwigotigi niЙЎМ¶ijoa paontedi, odaa ja yajigotediogi niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece monediatiniwace niЙЎМ¶idi noiigi-nelegi.
\v 7 Codaa aaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a idiwa onateciЙЎМ¶idiwa noЙЎМ¶ojedawaanaЙЎМ¶a. Odaa Jesus diniotagodete AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ijoa noЙЎМ¶ojedawaanaЙЎМ¶a, odaa jaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a iiЙЎМ¶e niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece moyajigotiogi niЙЎМ¶idi noiigi-nelegi.
\v 8 Odaa ijotawece niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi niodaЙЎМ¶a, codaa nitiminaЙЎМ¶a. NiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece Jesus joЙЎМ¶onioda niЙЎМ¶ijoa liwailidi ane iiЙЎМ¶otedice liwai paontedi ijaaЙЎМ¶ijoa noЙЎМ¶ojedawaanaЙЎМ¶a, odaa joЙЎМ¶onoleenaЙЎМ¶adi seete etacanitedi nelecoli.
\v 9 Ejime cwaatolo miili oko ane niodaЙЎМ¶a.
\p 
\v 10 NiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi Jesus ja iiЙЎМ¶e mopitibeci niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi-nelegi, odaa aЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a leegi ja waxoditedinigi naЙЎМ¶ajo niwatece ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece, odaa jiЙЎМ¶igotibeci nipodigi Dalmanuta.
\s1 Icoa fariseutedi odipokotalo Jesus meote ica ЙЎМ¶odoxiceЙЎМ¶edi
\r (Mateus 12.38-42; 16.1-4)
\p 
\v 11 Icoa fariseutedi igotibeci midoataЙЎМ¶a Jesus, odaa jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶oyatigi modinotigimadetege. Odineetalo Jesus, joaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi modipokotalo meote ЙЎМ¶odoxiceЙЎМ¶edi ane ikee mida nimaweneЙЎМ¶egi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji midoataЙЎМ¶a.
\v 12 Odaa Jesus nikatedice laadi leeЙЎМ¶odi yopo laaleЙЎМ¶enali me daЙЎМ¶axa me dakake, odaa meete, вҖңIgame leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane newiЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶inoa nokododi monipokotiwa me jao ЙЎМ¶odoxiceЙЎМ¶edi me jikee me idimonya AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji? EjitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji ajao ЙЎМ¶odoxiceЙЎМ¶edi lodoe niЙЎМ¶ina oko me jikee AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me idimonya.вҖқ
\p 
\v 13 Odaa Jesus ja yetecetedicoace niЙЎМ¶ijoa fariseutedi. Ja waxoditacedinigi naЙЎМ¶ajo niwatece, odaa jiЙЎМ¶igotace daato weiigi.
\s1 Jesus yalaЙЎМ¶ate lakatigi fariseutedi ijaa inionigi Herodes, iciaceeketetege labookojegi aneo me ili leyeema moyoe paon
\r (Mateus 16.5-12)
\p 
\v 14 NiЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece Jesus oyaagiditece doЙЎМ¶oyadeegi paon. Pida onidi oniditeci paon mijotaЙЎМ¶a catinedi naЙЎМ¶ajo niwatece.
\v 15 Odaa Jesus jeЙЎМ¶eote leemidi, meetediogi, вҖңDigawinitiwaji! Adinowetitege nabookojegi fariseutedi ijaa inionigi Herodes!вҖқ
\p 
\v 16 Odaa jiЙЎМ¶idaa diiticogi me dinotigimadetiwage, modi, вҖңEote niЙЎМ¶ida ligegitedoЙЎМ¶owa leeЙЎМ¶odi me daЙЎМ¶a inadeegaЙЎМ¶ateda paontedi.вҖқ
\v 17 Jesus yowooЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ijo anodinotigimadetigi, odaa meetediogi, вҖңIgame leeЙЎМ¶odi madinotigimadenitiwage me diЙЎМ¶icoa ЙЎМ¶anipaonteditiwaji manadeegi? IcaaЙЎМ¶ina daЙЎМ¶alee doЙЎМ¶owooЙЎМ¶otitiwaji niЙЎМ¶ijoa ananati. Codaa icaaЙЎМ¶ina daЙЎМ¶a akakaЙЎМ¶ati ЙЎМ¶adaaleЙЎМ¶enalitiwaji me daЙЎМ¶a adinakatoni.
\v 18 Idiwa ЙЎМ¶agecooЙЎМ¶eli, pida agodoЙЎМ¶owooЙЎМ¶otitiwaji niЙЎМ¶inoa ananati. Codaa idiwa ЙЎМ¶anapaaЙЎМ¶atedi, pida agodoЙЎМ¶owooЙЎМ¶otitiwaji niЙЎМ¶inoa anajipaatalo. AЙЎМ¶analakitibigetiwaji niЙЎМ¶ijoa yoenataka.
\v 19 NiЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a ininoketedini niЙЎМ¶ijoa ciinco paontedi, odaa ja jiniodeЙЎМ¶etedini niЙЎМ¶ijoa ciinco miili ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi, igame liwokodi etacanitedi nelecoli ane nolee liwailidi ane iiЙЎМ¶otedice ananiodaatiwaji?вҖқ Odaa joЙЎМ¶oigidi, moditalo, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ijo noko jenaЙЎМ¶atigilo dooze etacanitedi nelecoli.вҖқ
\p 
\v 20 Odaa Jesus ja nigetacediniwace, meetediogi, вҖңCodaa niЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a ininoketedini niЙЎМ¶ijoa seete paontedi me jajigotiogi niЙЎМ¶ijoa cwaatolo miili oko, igame liwokodi etacanitedi nelecoli ane nolee liwailidi ane iiЙЎМ¶otedice ane aniodaa?вҖқ Odaa joЙЎМ¶oniniЙЎМ¶odi, moditalo, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ijo noko baЙЎМ¶a jenaЙЎМ¶atigilo seete etacanitedi niЙЎМ¶inoa nelecoli.вҖқ
\v 21 Odaa Jesus meetediogi, вҖңPida ica ina daЙЎМ¶alee doЙЎМ¶owooЙЎМ¶otitedatiwaji niЙЎМ¶ijoa ananati.вҖқ
\s1 Jesus icilatidi ica etoinaЙЎМ¶a ane icoЙЎМ¶oticogi nigotakawaana Betsaida
\p 
\v 22 Jesus ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece joЙЎМ¶ototicogi manitaЙЎМ¶a nigotakawaana Betsaida. Ijo ica oko anonadeegitalo ica etoinaЙЎМ¶a, odaa joЙЎМ¶odipokotalo me dibatedeloco me icilatidi niЙЎМ¶ijo etoinaЙЎМ¶a.
\v 23 Odaa Jesus ja dibatedigi libaaЙЎМ¶adi niЙЎМ¶ijo etoinaЙЎМ¶a, odaa noЙЎМ¶atedicogi naЙЎМ¶ani nigotakawaana. Odaa Jesus yawaletediwece ligecooЙЎМ¶eli niЙЎМ¶ijo etoinaЙЎМ¶a, odaa ja dibatedeloco ligecooЙЎМ¶eli, odaa ja ige, meeteta, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ica ananati?вҖқ
\v 24 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa naЙЎМ¶a nawacetibige lacilo me dole, odaa mee, вҖңJinadi niЙЎМ¶ina oko midiaanaЙЎМ¶adi, pida liciagi niЙЎМ¶inoa nialeli.вҖқ
\v 25 Odaa Jesus ja dibatacetedeloco ligecooЙЎМ¶eli niЙЎМ¶ijo etoinaЙЎМ¶a, odaa iiЙЎМ¶etaceda me doletibece. Odaa aЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a leegi ligecooЙЎМ¶eli niЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa ja icГӯ, odaa yakadi mepaanaЙЎМ¶a doletibece.
\v 26 Odaa Jesus ja iiЙЎМ¶e mopiticogi liЙЎМ¶eladi, codaa meeteta, вҖңJinaЙЎМ¶akaatiwece naЙЎМ¶ani nigotakawaana, codaa jiniЙЎМ¶ica anatematiita manitaЙЎМ¶a naЙЎМ¶ani nigotakawaana niЙЎМ¶ida ane jaotaЙЎМ¶adomi.вҖқ
\s1 Pedro yeloЙЎМ¶odi anijoa Jesus
\r (Mateus 16.13-20; Lucas 9.18-21)
\p 
\v 27 Ica noko Jesus ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece jiЙЎМ¶igotibeci midiwataЙЎМ¶a nigotadawaanaЙЎМ¶a miditaЙЎМ¶a nipodigi ane liboonaЙЎМ¶adi вҖңCesarГ©ia Filipe ane dabiteЙЎМ¶etiniвҖқ. Odaa naigitece mewaligitibigiwaji, Jesus nigetediniwace, meetediogi, вҖңIna oko, amigida ica anodiletibige ane Ee?вҖқ
\p 
\v 28 Odaa joniЙЎМ¶ica anoigidi, moditalo, вҖңInatecibece oko modi makaami JoГЈo Batista, pida inatecibece eledi modi makaami Elias, codaa ina eledi boЙЎМ¶oditibige makaami anigepidiЙЎМ¶ica niЙЎМ¶ijo anoyeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lowooko niЙЎМ¶ijo jotigide.вҖқ
\p 
\v 29 Odaa jaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a nigetediniwace, meetediogi, вҖңPida baЙЎМ¶akaamitiwaji, amakati me Ee?вҖқ Odaa Pedro ja niniЙЎМ¶odi, meetalo, вҖңAkaami NiЙЎМ¶ijo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane niiЙЎМ¶e ЙЎМ¶odatamaЙЎМ¶ateeneЙЎМ¶egitege ЙЎМ¶odaxakawepodi.вҖқ
\v 30 Odaa Jesus ja najoitediniwace me doЙЎМ¶oyatematitibece anijoa.
\s1 Jesus yatemati micota me dawikode, codaa yalaЙЎМ¶ate me leeditibige me yeleo
\r (Mateus 16.21-28; Lucas 9.22-27)
\p 
\v 31 Odaa Jesus jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶eyatedigi me niiЙЎМ¶axitediniwace niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece me leeditibige meliodi me dawikode, mijoa me ЗӨoneleegiwa ane icoЙЎМ¶otedibigimece ditibigimedi. Codaa me leeditibige niЙЎМ¶ijo laxokodipi lacilodi niЙЎМ¶idi noiigi, ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo niЙЎМ¶ijo anoiiЙЎМ¶e sacerdotitedi, ijaaЙЎМ¶ijoa niiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anadi anodiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atece lajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco MoisГ©s, miditawece aЙЎМ¶odibatege Jesus. Codaa me leeditibige me yeleo, pida yewiЙЎМ¶atace nige ixomaЙЎМ¶atedijo itoatadiЙЎМ¶ida nokododi.
\v 32 Jesus iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶atece niЙЎМ¶ijoa lotaЙЎМ¶a. Odaa Pedro ja yadeegitedice me ideite liwigotigi niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece, odaa jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶eyatigi me yapeteЙЎМ¶e Jesus.
\v 33 Pida Jesus nilokotediogi, me niipetediogi niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece, odaa ja yapeteЙЎМ¶e Pedro, meeteta, вҖңOtonitice yodoe, SatanГЎs! NiЙЎМ¶ida makaami mowookoni ЙЎМ¶adiciagi niЙЎМ¶ina eledi oko me nowookonaЙЎМ¶a, pida aЙЎМ¶owookoni daЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶adiciagi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me dowooko.вҖқ
\p 
\v 34 NiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi Jesus eniditediogi niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi-nelegi ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece me enagitibeci midoataЙЎМ¶a. Odaa meetediogi, вҖңNigica oko ane yemaa me niotici, leeditibige me ika me dioteci niЙЎМ¶ica anepaa yemaa, codaa leeditibige me igotema me dawikode nigepaa yeleo inoatawece nokododi, codaa me igotema moyametibigo leeЙЎМ¶odi me niotici, odaa baЙЎМ¶a yakadi me niotici.
\v 35 IgaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina oko aninoka doletibige me dinowedi, niЙЎМ¶ini oko icota me yeleo nigepaa ganigicatibige. Pida niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane yeleo leeЙЎМ¶odi me niotici, codaa me leeЙЎМ¶odi me yatematitedibece nibodicetedi anele anoyalaЙЎМ¶atiwa, niЙЎМ¶ini oko baЙЎМ¶a yewiЙЎМ¶atace nigidiaaЙЎМ¶idi.
\v 36 Nigica oko ane yakadi inoatawece aninoa niЙЎМ¶ina iiЙЎМ¶o, pida nige yeleo, odaa aЙЎМ¶ica aneletema ijoatawece niЙЎМ¶ijo ane yakadi.
\v 37 NiЙЎМ¶ina oko aЙЎМ¶ica gaantokaaЙЎМ¶ini ane yakadi me yajigotalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me yakadi lewiЙЎМ¶a ane diЙЎМ¶ica liniogo.
\v 38 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane dinibolikatiditici, codaa me dinibolikatiditece niЙЎМ¶inoa yotaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina mini liwigotigi niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane diЙЎМ¶ika mowo doЙЎМ¶onakato AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji niЙЎМ¶inoa nokododi, codaa aneliodi me abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a, odaa aaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a idinibolikatiditece niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane dinibolikatiditici nige idopitacijo me ixigaЙЎМ¶awepodi niЙЎМ¶ijoa aanjotedi anodibatema iniokiniwateda AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Odaa Ee, ЗӨoneleegiwa ane jicoЙЎМ¶otibigimece ditibigimedi, jikee inaЙЎМ¶atetigi me iciagi Eiodi naЙЎМ¶atetigi.вҖқ
\c 9
\p 
\v 1 Odaa Jesus meetediogi niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi, вҖңEjitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji niЙЎМ¶ina anewi. Inatibece oko digoina anaЙЎМ¶a nigo nigonadi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji nigidaaЙЎМ¶eyatedigi me iiЙЎМ¶e laaleЙЎМ¶enali oko yatite nimaweneЙЎМ¶egi.вҖқ
\s1 Elias ijaa MoisГ©s oyotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶e Jesus
\r (Mateus 17.1-13; Lucas 9.28-36)
\p 
\v 2 NaЙЎМ¶a ixomaЙЎМ¶atedijo seis nokododi, odaa Jesus yadeegi Pedro, Tiago ijaa JoГЈo. Yadeegitedicogi maditaЙЎМ¶a aca wetiЙЎМ¶a ane leegitibigimece ane diЙЎМ¶ica oko anodipegitege. NoЙЎМ¶oiwitalo Jesus, odaa jeЙЎМ¶eledi latopagi.
\v 3 NiЙЎМ¶ijoa lowoodi Jesus ja datale, daЙЎМ¶axa me yapacaЙЎМ¶a, caticedi okanicodaaЙЎМ¶aca lapacoЙЎМ¶ogo ane yabake nabakenaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶alo.
\v 4 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo itoatadiЙЎМ¶ida anodiotibece joЙЎМ¶onadi Elias ijaa MoisГ©s anoicoЙЎМ¶otibigimece ditibigimedi moyotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶e Jesus.
\v 5 Odaa Pedro jeЙЎМ¶eetalo Jesus, вҖңЗӨoniiЙЎМ¶axinoЙЎМ¶odi, ejimele minaaЙЎМ¶ejonaЙЎМ¶atice digoina. JaoЙЎМ¶ate idabiteЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶atedi iniwatadiЙЎМ¶ini nopecetiidi, oniniteci ЙЎМ¶anebi, ini eledi MoisГ©s, iniaaЙЎМ¶eledi baЙЎМ¶a Elias nebi.вҖқ
\v 6 Pida ayowooЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ica lowoogo meo niЙЎМ¶ijo ligegi, leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ijo itoatadiЙЎМ¶ida anodiotibece eliodi me doitibigiwaji.
\p 
\v 7 Odaa ja dinikatini ica lolaadi ane yapoЙЎМ¶oditiniwace, odaa joЙЎМ¶owajipatalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me dotaЙЎМ¶a catiwedi niЙЎМ¶ijo lolaadi, mee, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶idoa jiЙЎМ¶idaa Ionigi yemaanigi. Ajipaatalo niЙЎМ¶inoa lotaЙЎМ¶a!вҖқ
\v 8 Codaa noЙЎМ¶onida niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece noЙЎМ¶oiwiteloco niЙЎМ¶inoa liwailidi, odaa joЙЎМ¶onadi idokaaniЙЎМ¶inoateda Jesus miditaЙЎМ¶a.
\p 
\v 9 MaleeЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee me dinikatiniwace naЙЎМ¶ajo wetiЙЎМ¶a, Jesus najoitediniwace, meetediogi, вҖңJinaЙЎМ¶a atematiitiwaji niЙЎМ¶ijo ananati nigepaaЙЎМ¶icota me idewiЙЎМ¶atace Ee, ЗӨoneleegiwa ane jicoЙЎМ¶otibigimece ditibigimedi.вҖқ
\p 
\v 10 Odaa oyiwaЙЎМ¶adi niЙЎМ¶ijo Jesus liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶egi, aЙЎМ¶ica anoyatematita. Idokida modinotigimadetigi niЙЎМ¶ica ane diitigi niЙЎМ¶ijoa lotaЙЎМ¶a Jesus me yalaЙЎМ¶ate me yewiЙЎМ¶atace.
\v 11 Odaa joЙЎМ¶oige Jesus, moditalo, вҖңIgame leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ijo niiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anadi anodiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atece lajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco MoisГ©s modi Elias modoejegi meno, odaa nigidiaaЙЎМ¶idi jaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶enagi NiЙЎМ¶ijoa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane niiЙЎМ¶e me ЙЎМ¶odatamaЙЎМ¶ateetege ЙЎМ¶odaxakawepodi?вҖқ
\p 
\v 12 Jesus ja igidi, meetediogi, вҖңEwi Elias noЙЎМ¶odoejegi meno me ilakidetema naigi NiЙЎМ¶ijo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane niiЙЎМ¶e. Pida igame leeЙЎМ¶odi naЙЎМ¶ajo lotaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me yalaЙЎМ¶ata niЙЎМ¶ijo ЗӨoneleegiwa ane icoЙЎМ¶otibigimece ditibigimedi meliodi me dawikode, codaa niЙЎМ¶ina oko mododigota micataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina naagogo?
\v 13 Pida ejitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji Elias jiЙЎМ¶ijo meno, odaa joЙЎМ¶owo ane beyagitema niЙЎМ¶ica anepaaЙЎМ¶oyemaa modigota, anodaaЙЎМ¶ee me yalaЙЎМ¶ata AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lotaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axi maleediЙЎМ¶icota niЙЎМ¶ida niciagi.вҖқ
\s1 Jesus icilatidi ica nigaanigi ane dakatiogi niwigo abeyaceЙЎМ¶egi
\r (Mateus 17.14-21; Lucas 9.37-43)
\p 
\v 14 NiЙЎМ¶ijo noЙЎМ¶odipegitiogi niЙЎМ¶ijo eledi anodiotibece, odaa joЙЎМ¶onadi niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi-nelegi monawiile. Codaa onidi niЙЎМ¶ijoa niiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anadi anodiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atece lajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco MoisГ©s modinotigimadetege.
\v 15 NiЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi noЙЎМ¶onaditege Jesus, odaa eliodi moyopo, odaa joЙЎМ¶owaleditege moyecoaditece.
\v 16 Odaa Jesus nigetediniwace niЙЎМ¶ijoa niiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anadi, meetediogi, вҖңAmiini ica ane adinotigimadenitigitiwaji?вҖқ
\p 
\v 17 Odaa ica ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa liwigotigi niЙЎМ¶idi noiigi ja igidi, meetalo, вҖңЗӨoniiЙЎМ¶axinoЙЎМ¶odi, inadeegitaЙЎМ¶awa ionigi ini niwigo abeyaceЙЎМ¶egi aneo me daЙЎМ¶a yakadi me dotaЙЎМ¶a.
\v 18 Codaa niЙЎМ¶ica niwigo idioka limedi me dibata, odaa yokoletinigiiЙЎМ¶o. Codaa natiatigi nioladi, yacigice lowe, codaa me dinawigice. Ja domaЙЎМ¶a jipokotiogi niЙЎМ¶idi anodiotibigaЙЎМ¶adici moiticoitice niЙЎМ¶ijo niwigo abeyaceЙЎМ¶egi, pida joЙЎМ¶oyapi.вҖқ
\p 
\v 19 Odaa Jesus ja igidi, meeteta, вҖңJaЙЎМ¶akamaЙЎМ¶akaamitiwaji niЙЎМ¶ica noiigi ane doЙЎМ¶oyiwaЙЎМ¶aditeda AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Igamige liwokodi nokododi ane leeditibige minaaЙЎМ¶ejotice makaamitaЙЎМ¶atiwaji? Igamige liwokodi nokododi jakadi me idinatitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji leeЙЎМ¶odi me daЙЎМ¶a adadiwaЙЎМ¶ati? Anadeegitiwa niЙЎМ¶ini nigaanigawaanigi!вҖқ
\v 20 Odaa joЙЎМ¶oyadeegitalo niЙЎМ¶ijo nigaanigawaanigi. NiЙЎМ¶ijo niwigo abeyaceЙЎМ¶egi naЙЎМ¶a nadi Jesus, odaa ja yaxilaketibece niЙЎМ¶ijo nigaanigawaanigi, odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo nigaanigawaanigi jeЙЎМ¶enitinigiiЙЎМ¶o, dinawililetibece, natiatigi nioladi.
\v 21 Odaa Jesus ja ige eliodi niЙЎМ¶ijo nigaanigi, meeteta, вҖңAkaaЙЎМ¶idokee?вҖқ Odaa ja igidi, meetalo, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ijo malee nigaanigawaanigi naЙЎМ¶a leelotagi.
\v 22 JeЙЎМ¶elioditibece niwigo abeyaceЙЎМ¶egi me doletibige me yeloadi, idatecibece eo me dinaxoЙЎМ¶otiogi noledi codaa me ninyoЙЎМ¶odi. Natigide nigakati mawii me icГӯ ionigi, ЙЎМ¶odiwikodeneЙЎМ¶egi, codaa ЙЎМ¶odaxawaneЙЎМ¶egi!вҖқ
\p 
\v 23 Odaa Jesus meeteta, вҖңAЙЎМ¶eliodi ЙЎМ¶atiwaЙЎМ¶atakaneЙЎМ¶egi alawini menitiwa, вҖҳNigakatiвҖҷ. AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji yakadi meote okanicodaaЙЎМ¶ica loenatagitetema niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane nakato.вҖқ
\v 24 Odaa aЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a leegi niЙЎМ¶ijo eliodi niЙЎМ¶ijo nigaanigawaanigi jaЙЎМ¶anoe, dapaawe, meetalo, вҖңIniotagodi, jinakato AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, codaa adaxawani mepaanaЙЎМ¶a jinakato!вҖқ
\p 
\v 25 NiЙЎМ¶ijo Jesus naЙЎМ¶a nadi eliodi oko ane odinatecoЙЎМ¶oteetelogo, odaa ja yapeteЙЎМ¶e niЙЎМ¶ijo niwigo abeyaceЙЎМ¶egi, meeteta, вҖңNiwigo abeyaceЙЎМ¶egi anawii niЙЎМ¶idi nigaanigi me daЙЎМ¶a yakadi me dotaЙЎМ¶a oteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a wajipa, ЙЎМ¶adiiЙЎМ¶eni manotiticogi niЙЎМ¶idi nigaanigi, codaa jinaЙЎМ¶aleeЙЎМ¶akaatiogi!вҖқ
\v 26 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo niwigo abeyaceЙЎМ¶egi ja dinigetaЙЎМ¶atee me dacaage, ecoЙЎМ¶otace eo me dinaxilaketibece niЙЎМ¶ijo nigaanigi, odaa ja noditice. NiЙЎМ¶idi nigaanigi ja liciagi niЙЎМ¶ina Г©meЙЎМ¶egi, odaa eliodi oko modi, вҖңJa yeleo!вҖқ
\v 27 Pida Jesus dibatedigi libaaЙЎМ¶adi niЙЎМ¶ijo nigaanigi, odaa ja yaxawa me dabiditini.
\p 
\v 28 NiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi Jesus ja dakatediwece ica diimigi, onijoateci ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece, odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece joЙЎМ¶oige, moditalo, вҖңIgamige leeЙЎМ¶odi me daЙЎМ¶a jakataЙЎМ¶a me jiticodaЙЎМ¶atice niЙЎМ¶ijo niwigo abeyaceЙЎМ¶egi?вҖқ
\v 29 Odaa Jesus ja igiditediogi, meetediogi, вҖңIdoka akati miticoitice liciagi niЙЎМ¶ijo niwigo abeyaceЙЎМ¶egi niЙЎМ¶ina mecoЙЎМ¶otace otaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶enitiwaji AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.вҖқ
\s1 Jesus yalaЙЎМ¶atace me yeleo, codaa me yewiЙЎМ¶atace
\r (Mateus 17.22-23; Lucas 9.43-45)
\p 
\v 30 Jesus ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece ja noditicogi niЙЎМ¶idi nipodigi, odaa ja ixomaЙЎМ¶aticogi miditaЙЎМ¶a nipodigi GalilГ©ia. Jesus adomaЙЎМ¶a yemaa diЙЎМ¶ica ane yowooЙЎМ¶odi ane diЙЎМ¶etedicogi, igaataЙЎМ¶a domaЙЎМ¶a yemaa me niiЙЎМ¶axitediniwace idiokidi niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece.
\v 31 NiЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a niiЙЎМ¶axitediniwace, meetediogi, вҖңIcota metidajigotiogi niЙЎМ¶inoa ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi ЙЎМ¶oneЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a, odaa niЙЎМ¶idiwa ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi etideloadi, Ee, ЗӨoneleegiwa ane jicoЙЎМ¶otibigimece ditibigimedi. Pida nige ixomaЙЎМ¶atedijo itoatadiЙЎМ¶ida nokododi me ideleo, odaa ja idewiЙЎМ¶atace.вҖқ
\v 32 Pida niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece aЙЎМ¶oyowooЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ica ane diitigilo niЙЎМ¶ijoa lotaЙЎМ¶a. Pida joЙЎМ¶odoitalo doЙЎМ¶oigetece Jesus ica ane diitigilo niЙЎМ¶ijoa lotaЙЎМ¶a.
\s1 Jesus diiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atetece anodaaЙЎМ¶ee niЙЎМ¶ica ane daЙЎМ¶axa me ЙЎМ¶oneЙЎМ¶egi
\r (Mateus 18.1-5; Lucas 9.46-48)
\p 
\v 33 Jesus ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece jiЙЎМ¶icotiobece nigotaЙЎМ¶a Cafarnaum. NiЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a idiaaЙЎМ¶itice liЙЎМ¶eladi, odaa Jesus ja nigetediniwace, meetediogi, вҖңAmiini ica ane adinotigimadenitigitiwaji naigitece?вҖқ
\p 
\v 34 Pida notokotiniwace, aЙЎМ¶ica gaantokaaЙЎМ¶ida ligegi niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece, igaataЙЎМ¶a naigitece odinotigimadetigi niЙЎМ¶ica ane daЙЎМ¶axa me ЙЎМ¶oneЙЎМ¶egi liwigotigi.
\v 35 Jesus nicotedini, odaa jeЙЎМ¶eniditediogi, meetediogi, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ina oko ЙЎМ¶adiwigotigitiwaji ane yemaa me idei odoejegi nimedi, niЙЎМ¶ini oko leeditibige mowidijegi, codaa me ЙЎМ¶aotagitiwaji.вҖқ
\v 36 Odaa ja dibate ica nigaanigawaanigi, odaa ideyatedice liwigotigi. Odaa ja ibedotetece niЙЎМ¶ijo nigaanigawaanigi, odaa meetediogi niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece,
\v 37 вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ina oko ane dibatege nigaanigawaanigi liciagi niЙЎМ¶ini nigaanigawaanigi me Ee leeЙЎМ¶odi, niЙЎМ¶ini oko dibatigi. Odaa niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane dibatigi, aЙЎМ¶emoka dibatigi, pida aaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a dibatege NiЙЎМ¶ijoa ane idimonya.вҖқ
\s1 Jesus diiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atetece niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane daЙЎМ¶a lakapetegiteda, odaa niЙЎМ¶ini oko anida aneetege
\r (Lucas 9.49-50)
\p 
\v 38 JoГЈo meetalo Jesus, вҖңЗӨoniiЙЎМ¶axinoЙЎМ¶odi, jinataЙЎМ¶a ijo ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa ibake ЗӨaboonaЙЎМ¶adi me iticoitedice niwicidi abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a, odaa ja joxokojoЙЎМ¶o me ibake ЗӨaboonaЙЎМ¶adi, leeЙЎМ¶odi adiotibigaЙЎМ¶adici daЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶odiciagi.вҖқ
\v 39 Odaa Jesus meeteta, вҖңJinoЙЎМ¶oxoki eledi oko me ibake IboonaЙЎМ¶adi, igaataЙЎМ¶a aЙЎМ¶ica ini ane yakadi me ibake IboonaЙЎМ¶adi meo ЙЎМ¶odoxiceЙЎМ¶edi, oditaЙЎМ¶a aleegi odaa ja beyagi me dotaЙЎМ¶atibigiji.
\v 40 IgaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane daЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶odakapetegi, niЙЎМ¶ini oko ida anejinaЙЎМ¶atege.
\v 41 IgaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane yajigotaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji goopa ninyoЙЎМ¶odi leeЙЎМ¶odi mida anenitigi, Ee ane idimonya AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me jewikatiditace niЙЎМ¶ina oko. EjitaЙЎМ¶awa niЙЎМ¶ina anewi, AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji yajigote noЙЎМ¶eedi anele niЙЎМ¶ini oko.вҖқ
\s1 Anodaa leeditibige miniЙЎМ¶ata ЙЎМ¶obeyaceЙЎМ¶egi
\r (Mateus 18.6-9; Lucas 17.1-2)
\p 
\v 42 Jesus eЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee me dotaЙЎМ¶a, odaa meetediogi, вҖңNigica aneo oniniteci niЙЎМ¶idi nigaanigipawaanigi meyamaЙЎМ¶atice eliwaЙЎМ¶atakaneЙЎМ¶egi, odaa ejimetaЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶axa mele doЙЎМ¶oigoetece lotoinaЙЎМ¶adi wetiЙЎМ¶a nelegi liciagi naЙЎМ¶ana wetiЙЎМ¶a anoibake monidi leyeema, oditaЙЎМ¶a oyokoletinigi akiidi-eliodi.
\v 43 ЗӨabaaЙЎМ¶adi nigeo mabataa, ejimetaЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶axa mele makagiti, oditaЙЎМ¶a onaniЙЎМ¶idatece ЙЎМ¶abaaЙЎМ¶adi, pida akaatiwece aneitedice AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji midioka limedi makaami miniwataЙЎМ¶a. Aliciagi daЙЎМ¶a idoatawece ЙЎМ¶abaaЙЎМ¶atedi, pida etiЙЎМ¶adokoleniticogi miditaЙЎМ¶a aneite nawikodico minitaЙЎМ¶a noledi ane daЙЎМ¶a ipe.
\v 44 Digoida idioka limedi midiwa nigojokodi anoyeligo lolaadi niЙЎМ¶ina Г©meЙЎМ¶egi, codaa noledi aЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a ipe.
\v 45 ЗӨadoЙЎМ¶onagi nigeo mabataa, ejimetaЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶axa mele makagiti, oditaЙЎМ¶a akaami alejaado, pida akaatiwece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji aneitedice midioka limedi makaami miniwataЙЎМ¶a. Aliciagi daЙЎМ¶a idoatawece ЙЎМ¶adoЙЎМ¶onaka, pida etiЙЎМ¶adokoleniticogi miditaЙЎМ¶a aneite nawikodico minitaЙЎМ¶a noledi ane daЙЎМ¶a ipe.
\v 46 Digoida idioka limedi midiwa nigojokodi anoyeligo lolaadi niЙЎМ¶inoa Г©maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a, codaa noledi ane daЙЎМ¶a ipe.
\v 47 ЗӨagecooЙЎМ¶e nigeo mabataa, ejimetaЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶axa mele manoЙЎМ¶aa onaniteci ЙЎМ¶agecooЙЎМ¶e, oditaЙЎМ¶a onaniteci ЙЎМ¶aneike, pida akaatiwece aneitedice AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji midioka limedi makaami miniwataЙЎМ¶a. Aliciagi daЙЎМ¶a idiwatawece ЙЎМ¶agecooЙЎМ¶eli, pida etiЙЎМ¶adokoleniticogi minitaЙЎМ¶a noledi ane daЙЎМ¶a ipe, aneite nawikodico.
\v 48 Digoida idioka limedi midiwa nigojokodi anoyeligo lolaadi niЙЎМ¶inoa Г©maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a, codaa noledi ane daЙЎМ¶a ipe.
\p 
\v 49 NiЙЎМ¶ina monigodi niЙЎМ¶inoa eijedi anoibootema AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, odaa onocie libole me doЙЎМ¶oika me beyagi maleedoЙЎМ¶oyalegi, jiЙЎМ¶idaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶aee niЙЎМ¶inoa ЙЎМ¶odawikodico, dapicoЙЎМ¶o liciagi niЙЎМ¶ina noledi, odaa eo ЙЎМ¶otiwaЙЎМ¶atakaneЙЎМ¶egi me daЙЎМ¶a beyagi, pida jeЙЎМ¶epaanaЙЎМ¶a datiteti.
\v 50 Ele me jibakenaЙЎМ¶a yoci, pida niЙЎМ¶ina yoci nige naЙЎМ¶aniaditema libayodaЙЎМ¶a, odaa aЙЎМ¶aleeЙЎМ¶ica ЙЎМ¶onimaweneЙЎМ¶egi daЙЎМ¶a jaoЙЎМ¶atace me bayodi. MicataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina yoci me daЙЎМ¶a ika libole me beyagi, idaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶aeni jiniЙЎМ¶ikani gaantokaaЙЎМ¶ini ane ibeyacaЙЎМ¶adi ЙЎМ¶ademaanaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶egi anida makaamitaЙЎМ¶atiwaji, jinaЙЎМ¶a adinotigimadeni, oteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a adinideleЙЎМ¶enitiwagetiwaji.вҖқ
\c 10
\s1 Jesus diiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶a yalaЙЎМ¶ate nalataЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶egi
\r (Mateus 19.1-12; Lucas 16.18)
\p 
\v 1 NiЙЎМ¶ijo Jesus naЙЎМ¶a noditedicogi nipodigi GalilГ©ia, odaa jiЙЎМ¶igo miditaЙЎМ¶a nipodigi JudГ©ia, daato akiidi JordГЈo. Ica noiigi-nelegi odinatecoЙЎМ¶oteetacelogo, codaa modipegitalo, odaa ja niiЙЎМ¶axitacediniwace, ane ligileЙЎМ¶egi.
\p 
\v 2 Icoa fariseutedi igotibeci midoataЙЎМ¶a, odaa joЙЎМ¶oige, moditalo, вҖңIca ЙЎМ¶onajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶egi domige ika ina ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa me yaladi lodawa?вҖқ DomoЙЎМ¶odoletibige me nilaagedi Jesus mowote niЙЎМ¶ijoa lotaЙЎМ¶a.
\v 3 NiЙЎМ¶ijo Jesus naЙЎМ¶a niniЙЎМ¶oditediogi, odaa ja nigetediniwace, meetediogi, вҖңAmiini ica MoisГ©s ane iiЙЎМ¶etaЙЎМ¶awa mawiitiwaji?вҖқ
\v 4 Odaa joЙЎМ¶oigidi, moditalo, вҖңMoisГ©s ika niЙЎМ¶ina ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa meo idГӯ notaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axi ane yalaЙЎМ¶ata me yaladi lodawa, odaa yakadi me iiЙЎМ¶e mopi.вҖқ
\p 
\v 5 Odaa Jesus ja igidi, meetediogi, вҖңMoisГ©s iditini niЙЎМ¶ida lajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶egi leeЙЎМ¶odi ЙЎМ¶adaaleЙЎМ¶enali me dakake.
\v 6 Pida niЙЎМ¶ijo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji neЙЎМ¶eote inoatawece aninoa, jiЙЎМ¶idaa ane yalaЙЎМ¶ata AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lotaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axi, mee, вҖҳAneotedoЙЎМ¶oji eote ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa aniaaЙЎМ¶iwaalo.
\v 7 JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa me ika eliodi, eliodo niЙЎМ¶ina naЙЎМ¶a lodawa naЙЎМ¶ana lodawa.
\v 8 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo itoataale ja micataЙЎМ¶a doЙЎМ¶okinitece oko.вҖҷ Odaa jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee aЙЎМ¶alee liciagi miniwataale oko, pida ja micataЙЎМ¶a doЙЎМ¶okinitece oko.
\v 9 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ina AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane yadoneЙЎМ¶etediwage, aЙЎМ¶ica oko ane yakadi me yawalacetiwage.вҖқ
\p 
\v 10 NiЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a idiaaЙЎМ¶itice minitaЙЎМ¶a ica diimigi ane lotokaЙЎМ¶adi, odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece Jesus joЙЎМ¶oigetece ane diitigilo niЙЎМ¶ijoa lotaЙЎМ¶a.
\v 11 Odaa Jesus meetediogi, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ina ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa ane yaladi lodawa, odaa nige lodawa eledi iwaalo, odaa ja iЙЎМ¶olaЙЎМ¶adi naЙЎМ¶ajo odoeje lodawa.
\v 12 Codaa naЙЎМ¶ana iwaalo ane yaladi lodawa, nige lodawa eledi ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa, odaa ja iЙЎМ¶olaЙЎМ¶adi niЙЎМ¶ijo odoejegi lodawa.вҖқ
\s1 Jesus ibinietediogi ica nigaanigipawaanigi
\r (Mateus 19.13-15; Lucas 18.15-17)
\p 
\v 13 Ica noiigi oyadeegitalo Jesus nigaanigipawaanigi me ipeketedeloco libaaЙЎМ¶atedi me ibinietediogi. Pida niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece joЙЎМ¶odowocetege niЙЎМ¶ijo oko anonadeegi lionigipi.
\v 14 Pida Jesus naЙЎМ¶a nadi niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece niЙЎМ¶ica anowote, odaa ja yelatetema, odaa meetediogi, вҖңIkanitiwaji niЙЎМ¶ina nigaanigipawaanigi menagitibeci meetaЙЎМ¶a, jinaЙЎМ¶a oliitege menagitibeci meetaЙЎМ¶a, igaataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji iiЙЎМ¶e laaleЙЎМ¶enali niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane liciagi niЙЎМ¶ina nigaanigipawaanigi.
\v 15 EjitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji niЙЎМ¶ina anewi. AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji aiiЙЎМ¶e laaleЙЎМ¶ena niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane daЙЎМ¶a dibatege anodaaЙЎМ¶ee niЙЎМ¶ina nigaanigawaanigi me dibatege.вҖқ
\v 16 Odaa Jesus nibedotedi niЙЎМ¶ijo nigaanigipawaanigi, odaa ja ipeketedeloco libaaЙЎМ¶atedi me ibinietediogi.
\s1 Ica ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa liico dakapetege Jesus
\r (Mateus 19.16-30; Lucas 18.18-30)
\p 
\v 17 NiЙЎМ¶ijo Jesus naЙЎМ¶a idaa diitacedicogi me diniwiaje, odaa ica ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa walokoditege, odaa ja yamaЙЎМ¶atedi lokotidi lodoe Jesus. Odaa ja ige, meetalo, вҖңIniiЙЎМ¶axinoЙЎМ¶odi anele, amiida ica ane leeditibige me jao midioka limedi me idewiЙЎМ¶a miniwataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji?вҖқ
\p 
\v 18 Odaa Jesus meeteta, вҖңIgame leeЙЎМ¶odi menitiwa me Ee ele? AЙЎМ¶ica anele, iniokiniwateda AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji mele.
\v 19 JoЙЎМ¶owooЙЎМ¶oti liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ЙЎМ¶odiiЙЎМ¶e, meete, вҖҳJinaЙЎМ¶a aijee, jinaЙЎМ¶a aЙЎМ¶olaЙЎМ¶atakani, jinaЙЎМ¶a olice, codaa jinaЙЎМ¶a ilikoni. AweniЙЎМ¶ideni ЙЎМ¶adiodi, codaa me ЙЎМ¶adiodo.вҖҷ Codaa jinaЙЎМ¶a inaaleni eledi oko manoЙЎМ¶aa ane nebi.вҖқ
\p 
\v 20 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa ja igidi, meetalo, вҖңIniiЙЎМ¶axinoЙЎМ¶odi, idioka limedi me jeemitetibige idiwatawece niЙЎМ¶idiwa niiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco niЙЎМ¶ijo maleeЙЎМ¶ee nigaanigi codaa niЙЎМ¶ina natigide.вҖқ
\p 
\v 21 Jesus naЙЎМ¶a iwiteta, odaa eliodi me yemaa, odaa meeteta, вҖңOnaniЙЎМ¶idatece ane leeditibige mawii. Aani niЙЎМ¶icoa ane ЙЎМ¶anepilidi, odaa edianitece ЙЎМ¶aninyeelo niЙЎМ¶ina madewetedipi. Odaa jiЙЎМ¶idaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji nige yajigotedaЙЎМ¶awa owidi ЙЎМ¶anepilidi digoida ditibigimedi. OdaaЙЎМ¶anagi, pida leeditibige me ЙЎМ¶adigomi mawikodee nigepaa ЙЎМ¶adelewi, odaa baЙЎМ¶akati maniwitici.вҖқ
\v 22 NiЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa naЙЎМ¶a wajipatalo niЙЎМ¶ijoa lotaЙЎМ¶a Jesus, odaa deemitetece catiwedi laaleЙЎМ¶ena dakake meo niЙЎМ¶ijo aneeteta Jesus. Odaa eliodi magecaЙЎМ¶alo, odaa joЙЎМ¶opi, leeЙЎМ¶odi owidi niЙЎМ¶icoa ane nepilidi.
\p 
\v 23 Odaa Jesus niipetediogi niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece monawiile, odaa meetediogi, вҖңIca me dakake AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me iiЙЎМ¶e laaleЙЎМ¶ena niЙЎМ¶ina liico!вҖқ
\p 
\v 24 NiЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece eliodi me nawelatibigiwaji niЙЎМ¶ijo noЙЎМ¶owajipatalo niЙЎМ¶ijoa lotaЙЎМ¶a. Pida Jesus eЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee me dotaЙЎМ¶a, meetediogi, вҖңIonigipi, dakake AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me iiЙЎМ¶e laaleЙЎМ¶ena niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane dinaЙЎМ¶akatiditalo niЙЎМ¶ina ane niliicaЙЎМ¶ajetecidi!
\v 25 EneЙЎМ¶egi dakake AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me iiЙЎМ¶e laaleЙЎМ¶ena niЙЎМ¶ina liico, aliciagi gameelo me dakatiwece etakado lawimaЙЎМ¶ajegi.вҖқ
\p 
\v 26 NiЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece noЙЎМ¶owajipatacalo niЙЎМ¶ijoa lotaЙЎМ¶a, odaa nawelatacibigiwaji. Odaa ja dinigetiwage, modi, вҖңEnice, amigijo ica ane yakadi midioka limedi me yewiЙЎМ¶a miniwataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji?вҖқ
\p 
\v 27 Odaa Jesus naЙЎМ¶a niipetacediogi, odaa meetediogi, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ina oko aЙЎМ¶ica nimaweneЙЎМ¶egi deЙЎМ¶epaaЙЎМ¶owo midioka limedi me newiЙЎМ¶a miniwataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, pida AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji biЙЎМ¶ida nimaweneЙЎМ¶egi. Codaa yakadi meote okanicodaaЙЎМ¶ica, aЙЎМ¶ica idi ane daЙЎМ¶a yakaditeda meote.вҖқ
\p 
\v 28 Odaa Pedro jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶eyatedigi me yotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶e Jesus, meetalo, вҖңDigawini! Ja jikanaЙЎМ¶atedice ijoatawece ane ЙЎМ¶onepilidi leeЙЎМ¶odi me jiwaЙЎМ¶atibigaЙЎМ¶adici.вҖқ
\v 29 Jesus ja igidi, meeteta, вҖңEjitaЙЎМ¶awa niЙЎМ¶ina anewi. Inatawece oko anoyaladi liЙЎМ¶eladi, nioxoadipi, codaa me niwaalepodi, eliodi, eliodo, lodawa, lionigipi, codaa me niЙЎМ¶inoa niiЙЎМ¶otedi Ee leeЙЎМ¶odi, codaa me leeЙЎМ¶odi me yatematitedibece nibodicetedi anele,
\v 30 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji yajigote niЙЎМ¶ini oko caticedi niЙЎМ¶icoa ane yaladi malee newiЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina iiЙЎМ¶o. AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji yajigote anige liwokodi taalia caticedi ane liwokodi niЙЎМ¶ica anoyaladi. Codaa niЙЎМ¶ini oko dinigaanyetece liЙЎМ¶elatedi, nioxoadipi, niwaalepodi, eliododipi, nigaanigipawaanigi, codaa me niiЙЎМ¶otedi. Codaa icota moiatetibeci, pida nigidiaaЙЎМ¶idi idioka limedi me yewiЙЎМ¶a miniwataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.
\v 31 Eliodi oko ane daЙЎМ¶axa me ЙЎМ¶oneЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶inoa nokododi digoina iiЙЎМ¶o, niЙЎМ¶idi oko icota me iwikodadipi. Odaa eliodi oko ane iwikodadipi niЙЎМ¶inoa nokododi, niЙЎМ¶idi oko icota me daЙЎМ¶axa me ЙЎМ¶oneЙЎМ¶egipi.вҖқ
\s1 Jesus yalaЙЎМ¶atace moyeloadi
\r (Mateus 20.17-19; Lucas 18.31-34)
\p 
\v 32 Jesus ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece eЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee mewaligitibigiwaji, odaa joЙЎМ¶odowicetibigimece manitaЙЎМ¶a nigotaЙЎМ¶a JerusalГ©m. Jesus igo lodoe niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece odaa one oyopo. NiЙЎМ¶ijo oko anodiotece doitibigiwaji. Odaa Jesus jeЙЎМ¶eniditediogi niЙЎМ¶ijo dooze anodiotibece, ixipetedicoace. Odaa yeloЙЎМ¶oditediogi ane ninyaagi.
\v 33 Meetediogi, вҖңDigawini! Ja jowicaЙЎМ¶ata nigotaЙЎМ¶a JerusalГ©m. Odaa Ee, ЗӨoneleegiwa ane jicoЙЎМ¶otibigimece ditibigimedi etidajigotiogi niЙЎМ¶ijo anoiiЙЎМ¶e sacerdotitedi, ijaaЙЎМ¶ijoa niЙЎМ¶ijoa niiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anadi anodiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atece lajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco MoisГ©s. Odaa modi me leeditibige metideloadi, codaa aaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a etidajigotiogi niЙЎМ¶ijo ane daЙЎМ¶a judeutedi.
\v 34 Odaa niЙЎМ¶idi ane daЙЎМ¶a judeutedi oyametibigiji, etidalaketibige, codaa metidawaletice, odaa jeЙЎМ¶etideloadi. Pida nigidiaaЙЎМ¶idi nige ixomaЙЎМ¶atedijo itoatadiЙЎМ¶ida nokododi, odaa ja idewiЙЎМ¶atace.вҖқ
\s1 Tiago ijaa JoГЈo ida nipoketegitalo Jesus
\r (Mateus 20.20-28)
\p 
\v 35 Tiago ijaa JoГЈo ane lionigipi Zebedeu, jiЙЎМ¶igotibeci odipegitalo Jesus, odaa moditalo, вҖңЗӨoniiЙЎМ¶axinoЙЎМ¶odi, jemaanaЙЎМ¶a mawiitoЙЎМ¶odomi ane jipokaЙЎМ¶ataЙЎМ¶awa.вҖқ
\v 36 Odaa Jesus nigetediniwace, meetediogi, вҖңAmiini ica anemaanitiwaji me jaotaЙЎМ¶adomi?вҖқ
\v 37 Odaa joЙЎМ¶oigidi, moditalo, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ina AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji nige ЙЎМ¶adinelecaЙЎМ¶ateeni, nigicota me iiЙЎМ¶eni inoatawece, ЙЎМ¶odikaneЙЎМ¶egi me ЙЎМ¶odicote ЙЎМ¶awai oniniteci diЙЎМ¶etege ЙЎМ¶abaaЙЎМ¶adi iniaaЙЎМ¶eledi diЙЎМ¶etege ЙЎМ¶animagijegi.вҖқ
\p 
\v 38 Pida Jesus meetediogi, вҖңAЙЎМ¶owooЙЎМ¶otitiwaji niЙЎМ¶ica anipokitibige. Domigakatitiwaji mawikodee anodaaЙЎМ¶eji me jawikode, codaa domige akatitiwaji mawikodee nigepaa ЙЎМ¶adelewi anodaaЙЎМ¶eji me ideleo?вҖқ
\v 39 Odaa joЙЎМ¶oigidi, moditalo, вҖңJakataЙЎМ¶a!вҖқ Odaa Jesus meetediogi, вҖңAwikodeetiwaji anodaaЙЎМ¶eji me jawikode, codaa me ЙЎМ¶adelewi, anodaaЙЎМ¶eji me ideleo.
\v 40 Pida aЙЎМ¶ica inaЙЎМ¶atetigi deЙЎМ¶ejitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji me akati manicootini ibaaЙЎМ¶adi, iniaaЙЎМ¶eledi inimagijegi. AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji yajigote niЙЎМ¶idiwa nimetiidi niЙЎМ¶ica oko anepaa iolatedice me nicoteloco.вҖқ
\p 
\v 41 NiЙЎМ¶ijo eledi deez anodiotibece Jesus owajipata niЙЎМ¶ijo Tiago ijaa JoГЈo anodipokotalo Jesus, odaa joЙЎМ¶oyelatema.
\v 42 Odaa Jesus jeЙЎМ¶eniditediogi modipegitalo, odaa meetediogi, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ijo anoditiogi me ЙЎМ¶odacilodi, owooЙЎМ¶otitiwaji me lemaanigi me iiЙЎМ¶e niЙЎМ¶ina oko, codaa niЙЎМ¶ina oko anodiletibige niЙЎМ¶ina eledi oko diЙЎМ¶ida naЙЎМ¶atetigi, niЙЎМ¶ijo oko lemaanigi me ibake epaanaЙЎМ¶a naЙЎМ¶atetigi.
\v 43 JiniЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶enitiwaji digo miditaЙЎМ¶a. Pida niЙЎМ¶ina ane yemaa mida naЙЎМ¶atetigi ЙЎМ¶adiwigotigitiwaji, niЙЎМ¶ini oko leeditibige makaamitawece dibataЙЎМ¶adomitiwaji.
\v 44 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane yemaa me dibata odoejegi nimedi ЙЎМ¶adiwigotigitiwaji, niЙЎМ¶ini leeditibige makaamitawecetiwaji aotageni.
\v 45 IgaataЙЎМ¶a codaa me Ee, ЗӨoneleegiwa ane jicoЙЎМ¶otibigimece ditibigimedi, ajanagi daЙЎМ¶a jiotage niЙЎМ¶ina oko, pida janagi me Ee niotagi, codaa me etidajigo me ideleo, odaa ja jao AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me yakadi me dibatetege eliodi oko.вҖқ
\s1 Jesus icilatidi ica ЙЎМ¶olaЙЎМ¶a ane liboonaЙЎМ¶adi Bartimeu
\r (Mateus 20.29-34; Lucas 18.35-43)
\p 
\v 46 Jesus ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece joЙЎМ¶oyakagiditeloco nigotaЙЎМ¶a JericГі. NiЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a doletibige me noditedice naЙЎМ¶ajo nigotaЙЎМ¶a, ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece icaaЙЎМ¶ica noiigi-nelegi, odaa jiЙЎМ¶icote ica ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa ЙЎМ¶olaЙЎМ¶a ane liboonaЙЎМ¶adi Bartimeu, lionigi Timeu. Bartimeu idiaa nicote liniogotibece naigi, dipokotibige dinyeelo.
\v 47 NiЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a wajipatibece modi Jesus anelatedigi nigotaЙЎМ¶a NazarГ© me inaaЙЎМ¶igotedinece aneitice, odaa jiЙЎМ¶idaa dinanatigi me dapaawe, mee, вҖңJesus, anida anenitege licoЙЎМ¶egi inionigi Davi, adiwikodenita!вҖқ
\p 
\v 48 Pida eliodi oko oyapeteЙЎМ¶e, codaa moiiЙЎМ¶e me notokotini. Pida jeЙЎМ¶epaanaЙЎМ¶a dapaawetibece, mee, вҖңAkaami, anida anenitege licoЙЎМ¶egi inionigi Davi, adiwikodeni!вҖқ
\p 
\v 49 Odaa Jesus ja dabiditedi, odaa ja diiЙЎМ¶enatakate monadeegitalo. Odaa joЙЎМ¶onidita niЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶olaЙЎМ¶a, modita, вҖңEloodaЙЎМ¶ateeni ЙЎМ¶adaaleЙЎМ¶ena! Adabititini! JeЙЎМ¶eniditedaЙЎМ¶awa.вҖқ
\v 50 Odaa Bartimeu ja yokoletice aca nicaapa, codaa yediiЙЎМ¶a me dabiditini, odaa jiЙЎМ¶igo midoataЙЎМ¶a Jesus.
\v 51 Odaa Jesus ja ige, meeteta, вҖңAmiini ica anemaani me jaotaЙЎМ¶adomi?вҖқ Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶olaЙЎМ¶a ja niniЙЎМ¶odi, meetalo, вҖңIniotagodi, jemaa me jatetacibece.вҖқ
\v 52 Odaa Jesus meeteta, вҖңEmii, ja ЙЎМ¶adicili leeЙЎМ¶odi manakatoni AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me yakadi me ЙЎМ¶adicilatiti.вҖқ AjaaЙЎМ¶ajo naЙЎМ¶aca lakata Bartimeu jona yatetacibece, odaa ja diotece Jesus mijotaЙЎМ¶a naigi.
\c 11
\s1 Jesus dakatediwece nigotaЙЎМ¶a JerusalГ©m me liciagi niЙЎМ¶ina inionigi-eliodi
\r (Mateus 21.1-11; Lucas 19.28-40; JoГЈo 12.12-19)
\p 
\v 1 Jesus ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece noЙЎМ¶odipegita nigotaЙЎМ¶a JerusalГ©m, odaa joЙЎМ¶ototicogi minitaЙЎМ¶a ica lojotaЙЎМ¶adi ane liboonaЙЎМ¶adi вҖңLojotaЙЎМ¶adi OliveiraвҖқ, anipegitege icoa nigotadawaanaЙЎМ¶a ane liboonaЙЎМ¶adi BetfagГ© aniaa BetГўnia. Odaa Jesus ja iiЙЎМ¶e itoa niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece, odaa meetediogi,
\v 2 вҖңEmiitiwaji manitaЙЎМ¶a nigotakawaana digoida ЙЎМ¶ododoe. Nige akaatiobecetiwaji, aЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a leegi icoota boliicawaanigi ane dinigoetini analeediЙЎМ¶ica mowaxoditeloco. Odaa owilecenitiwaji, anadeegitiwa.
\v 3 Pida nigica aneetaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji, вҖҳIgame leeЙЎМ¶odi mowilecenitiwaji ini boliicawaanigi?вҖҷ, odaa enita, вҖҳЗӨoniotagodi yopotedibige. NopilaЙЎМ¶adi natigidawaanigi.вҖҷвҖқ
\p 
\v 4 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo itoatataale anodiotibece jiЙЎМ¶igotibeci, odaa joЙЎМ¶otota niЙЎМ¶ijo boliicawaanigi naigitece, dinigoetini ipegitege lapoagi ica diimigi. Odaa joЙЎМ¶oyowilece niЙЎМ¶ijo boliicawaanigi.
\v 5 Odaa ica oko anidiaaЙЎМ¶itice ja nigikanaЙЎМ¶a, moditiogi, вҖңIgaamenitiwaji? Igame leeЙЎМ¶odi mowilecenitiwaji ini boliicawaanigi?вҖқ
\p 
\v 6 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo itoatataale anodiotibece Jesus joЙЎМ¶oigidi niЙЎМ¶ijo aneetediogi Jesus me ligegi. Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo oko joЙЎМ¶oikatece niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece Jesus moyadeegi boliicawaanigi.
\v 7 Odaa noЙЎМ¶oyadeegitalo Jesus niЙЎМ¶ijo boliicawaanigi, odaa joЙЎМ¶oyexaЙЎМ¶ateloco nicaapatedi niЙЎМ¶ijo boliicawaanigi, odaa Jesus ja waxoditedeloco.
\v 8 Eliodi oko oipecetedice nicaapatedi niЙЎМ¶ijo naigitece, odaa ica eledi onakagidi exate-lamodi oipecetinece naigi. (IdaЙЎМ¶aee leeЙЎМ¶odi moiweniЙЎМ¶ide Jesus.)
\v 9 Odaa ijo oko anigotibeci lodoe Jesus, codaa ica eledi boЙЎМ¶odiotece lowidi napaawaЙЎМ¶ateloco, modi,
\q1 вҖңJiweniЙЎМ¶idenaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji!
\q1 Codaa jemaanaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me ibinie NiЙЎМ¶inoa anenagi
\q1 ibake naЙЎМ¶atetigi LiboonaЙЎМ¶adi ЗӨoniotagodi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji!
\q1 
\v 10 JemaanaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me ibinie NiЙЎМ¶iniwa anida aneetetege licoЙЎМ¶egi inionigi-eliodi Davi,
\q1 ane niiЙЎМ¶etedoЙЎМ¶owa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me ЙЎМ¶oninionigi-eliodi,
\q1 liciagi Davi me ninionigi-eliodi niЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶odaamipi!вҖқ
\p 
\v 11 Jesus ja dakatediwece nigotaЙЎМ¶a JerusalГ©m, odaa jiЙЎМ¶igo minitaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liЙЎМ¶eladi. NaЙЎМ¶a dakatediwece, odaa iwitedigi initawece le. NiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi ja noditedice leeЙЎМ¶odi naЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶ocidi, odaa jiЙЎМ¶igo manitaЙЎМ¶a nigotakawaana BetГўnia lixigaЙЎМ¶awepodi niЙЎМ¶ijo dooze anodiotibece.
\s1 Jesus ixoo naЙЎМ¶ajo niale fiigoigo
\r (Mateus 21.18-19)
\p 
\v 12 NaЙЎМ¶a nigoi Jesus ja noditedicogi BetГўnia, odaa leecawaanigi ja deemitete me nigicile.
\v 13 Odaa ditigedi naЙЎМ¶a nadite aca niale fiigoigo ane daamotiide. Odaa jiЙЎМ¶igo iwi daЙЎМ¶aca ela. Pida niЙЎМ¶ijo niЙЎМ¶icote naЙЎМ¶ajo niale, aЙЎМ¶aca yakadi otaЙЎМ¶anitece ela, inokinoa laamotiidi, leeЙЎМ¶odi anaЙЎМ¶a limedi me etaye.
\v 14 Odaa Jesus jeЙЎМ¶eete naЙЎМ¶ajo niale, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ina natigide, aЙЎМ¶aleeЙЎМ¶ica ane yeligo ЙЎМ¶atГЎ.вҖқ Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece joЙЎМ¶owajipatalo niЙЎМ¶ijoa lotaЙЎМ¶a.
\s1 Jesus iticoitedicoace icoa anoojetekaЙЎМ¶a anidiaaЙЎМ¶i minitaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liЙЎМ¶eladi
\r (Mateus 21.12-17; Lucas 19.45-48; JoГЈo 2.13-22)
\p 
\v 15 Odaa Jesus ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece noЙЎМ¶otota nigotaЙЎМ¶a JerusalГ©m, odaa ja dakatediwece minitaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liЙЎМ¶eladi, odaa jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶eyatedigi me iticoitedicoace ijoatawece niЙЎМ¶ijoa anoojetekaЙЎМ¶a codaa me niЙЎМ¶ijo ane oojeteeЙЎМ¶a. Odaa yamaЙЎМ¶atedini nameejatedi niЙЎМ¶ijo ane libakedi moiikoaЙЎМ¶e dinyeelo codaa eledi yamaЙЎМ¶atedini nibaancotedi niЙЎМ¶ijo anoyaa yotipitedi.
\v 16 AЙЎМ¶ica ane ika me ixomaЙЎМ¶atice minitaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liЙЎМ¶eladi me yoyaЙЎМ¶adi elaanaЙЎМ¶a.
\v 17 Odaa niЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi jiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶itedice me niiЙЎМ¶axitediniwace ica oko, meetediogi, вҖңMaditaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lotaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axi diniditeloco niЙЎМ¶icoa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lotaЙЎМ¶a, niЙЎМ¶ijo neЙЎМ¶ee, вҖҳOyatigi iЙЎМ¶eladi me вҖңDiimigi aneitice inatawece noiigi moyakadi moyotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶e AneotedoЙЎМ¶ojiвҖқ.вҖҷ Pida jaЙЎМ¶awiitiwaji AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liЙЎМ¶eladi me liciagi niЙЎМ¶ina liЙЎМ¶eladi olicaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a.вҖқ \fig |src="CN01787B.TIF" size="col" copy="В© 1978 David C. Cook Publishing Co." ref="Marcos 11.15-17"\fig*
\p 
\v 18 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo anoiiЙЎМ¶e sacerdotitedi ijaaЙЎМ¶ijoa niЙЎМ¶ijoa niiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anadi anodiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atece lajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco MoisГ©s joЙЎМ¶odibodiceta niЙЎМ¶ijo Jesus aneote. Odaa joЙЎМ¶odoletibige niЙЎМ¶ica nimaweneЙЎМ¶egi moyeloadi, pida odoitalo leeЙЎМ¶odi inatawece oko oyopo niЙЎМ¶ijo ane diiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atetece.
\v 19 NaЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶ocidi Jesus ja noditacedice nigotaЙЎМ¶a JerusalГ©m.
\s1 Jesus diiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atetece me leeditibige me jinakatonaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji
\r (Mateus 21.20-22)
\p 
\v 20 NaЙЎМ¶a nigoi, Jesus ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece inaaЙЎМ¶igotacinece niЙЎМ¶ijo ligi, odaa joЙЎМ¶onadi naЙЎМ¶ajo libatadi fiigo. NaЙЎМ¶ajo niale adatawece yadilo, codaa me litodi yadilo.
\v 21 Odaa Pedro ja nalaЙЎМ¶atibige niЙЎМ¶ijoa Jesus lotaЙЎМ¶a, odaa meetalo, вҖңЗӨoniiЙЎМ¶axinoЙЎМ¶odi, digawini! NaЙЎМ¶ajo niale ane ixoomi ja yadilo.вҖқ
\p 
\v 22 Odaa Jesus ja igidi, meeteta, вҖңAnakatonitetiwaji AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji!
\v 23 NiЙЎМ¶ina nigewi me iwaЙЎМ¶atitiwaji, akati me enita naЙЎМ¶adi wetiЙЎМ¶a, вҖҳEmii, adinokolenitinigi akiidi-eliodi!вҖҷ Odaa nige daЙЎМ¶a awienatakanitiwaji, pida nige iwaЙЎМ¶atakani micota niЙЎМ¶ijo ane ЙЎМ¶agegita, odaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji eote micota.
\v 24 JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi mejitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji niЙЎМ¶ina motaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eni AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, mokanicodaaЙЎМ¶ica anipokitalo, iwaЙЎМ¶ati AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me yajigotedaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji, odaa yajigotedaЙЎМ¶awa niЙЎМ¶ica ane ipokitalo.
\v 25 Codaa niЙЎМ¶ina motaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eni AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, ixomaЙЎМ¶ateenitice okanicodaaЙЎМ¶ica ane beyagi aneotaЙЎМ¶adomi eledi oko, amaleeЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a ЗӨadiodi ane ideite ditibigimedi ixomaЙЎМ¶ateetedice ЙЎМ¶abeyaceЙЎМ¶ecotiwaji.
\v 26 Pida nige daЙЎМ¶a ixomaЙЎМ¶ateeniticetiwaji niЙЎМ¶ina ane beyagi anowotaЙЎМ¶adomi eledi oko, odaa ЗӨadiodi ane ideite ditibigimedi aixomaЙЎМ¶ateetedice ЙЎМ¶abeyaceЙЎМ¶ecotiwaji.вҖқ
\s1 Ica naЙЎМ¶atetigi Jesus
\r (Mateus 21.23-27; Lucas 20.1-8)
\p 
\v 27 NiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi Jesus ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece jiЙЎМ¶icotaciobece manitaЙЎМ¶a nigotaЙЎМ¶a JerusalГ©m. Jesus igotedigi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liЙЎМ¶eladi, odaa joЙЎМ¶ototalo niЙЎМ¶ijo anoiiЙЎМ¶e sacerdotitedi, ijaaЙЎМ¶ijoa niЙЎМ¶ijoa niiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anadi anodiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atece lajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco MoisГ©s, ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo laxokodi lacilodi niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi.
\v 28 Odaa moditalo Jesus, вҖңAmiida ica ЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶atetigi miticoiticoace niЙЎМ¶ijo oko minitaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liЙЎМ¶eladi? Codaa amiijo ane yajigotaЙЎМ¶awa ica ЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶atetigi?вҖқ
\p 
\v 29 Odaa Jesus meetediogi, вҖңJeloЙЎМ¶oditaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji ane najigotiwa inaЙЎМ¶atetigi niЙЎМ¶ina nige adigiti ane ЙЎМ¶adigeetece.
\v 30 Amiijo ica ane yajigota JoГЈo Batista naЙЎМ¶atetigi me nilegetiniwace oko? Domige AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, oЙЎМ¶oa domigoko? Jemaa madigititiwaji!вҖқ
\p 
\v 31 Odaa joЙЎМ¶odinotigimadetigi, modi, вҖңNigejinaЙЎМ¶a me AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane yajigote naЙЎМ¶atetigi JoГЈo, odaa jeЙЎМ¶eetedoЙЎМ¶owa, вҖҳEnice igame leeЙЎМ¶odi me daЙЎМ¶a iwaЙЎМ¶atitedatiwaji lotaЙЎМ¶a JoГЈo?вҖҷ
\v 32 Pida nigejinaЙЎМ¶a me niЙЎМ¶ina oko oiiЙЎМ¶e JoГЈo, odaa niЙЎМ¶ina oko joЙЎМ¶oyelatoЙЎМ¶odomi.вҖқ Odoitiogi niЙЎМ¶idi noiigi leeЙЎМ¶odi iditawece niЙЎМ¶idi oko oyiwaЙЎМ¶adi JoГЈo mewi me niЙЎМ¶inaaЙЎМ¶ina niЙЎМ¶ina ane yeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lowooko.
\v 33 Odaa joЙЎМ¶oigidi Jesus, moditalo, вҖңAjowooЙЎМ¶otaЙЎМ¶a ane niiЙЎМ¶e JoГЈo!вҖқ Odaa Jesus meetediogi, вҖңEnice amaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a jatematitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji ane najigotiwa inaЙЎМ¶atetigi me jaote niЙЎМ¶inoa yoenataka.вҖқ
\c 12
\s1 Ica natematigigi icoa nawodaЙЎМ¶anadi abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a
\r (Mateus 21.33-46; Lucas 20.9-19)
\p 
\v 1 Jesus jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶eyatedigi me yatematitediogi natematiko anida ane iciaceeketetege me diiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶a. Odaa meetediogi, вҖңIca ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa eyatedi uuva libatatiidi, odaa ja niotaa, codaa eo ligixitaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axi me niopaaЙЎМ¶aditedi uuva me yoe viinyo, codaa eo lipe lajo moibeo niЙЎМ¶ijoa lawodigijedi niЙЎМ¶inoa nowienoЙЎМ¶ododi. Odaa niЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi ja niwaiЙЎМ¶awepodi icoa nawodaЙЎМ¶anadi, odaa jiЙЎМ¶igo diniwiajeticogi ica eledi iiЙЎМ¶o. \fig |src="LB00104B.TIF" size="span" copy="Bass В©The British & Foreign Bible Society, 1994." ref="Marcos 12.1"\fig*
\v 2 NiЙЎМ¶ijo niЙЎМ¶icota limedi me nopilaЙЎМ¶aditedio elali, niЙЎМ¶ijo ane nebi niЙЎМ¶ijoa nawodigijedi nimonya ica liotagi me dienaЙЎМ¶atalo niЙЎМ¶ijoa elali ane nepilidi.
\v 3 Pida niЙЎМ¶ijoa nawodaЙЎМ¶anadi odibata niЙЎМ¶ijo nimeedi, odaa onalaketibige, codaa oiiЙЎМ¶e mopi me diЙЎМ¶icata ane yadeegi.
\v 4 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo ane nebi ja niiЙЎМ¶etace ica eledi liotagi, pida niЙЎМ¶ijoa nawodaЙЎМ¶anadi onigidatice, codaa oyacilotidi lacilo, codaa owo me niboliЙЎМ¶a.
\v 5 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo ane nebi niЙЎМ¶ijoa nawodigijedi ja niiЙЎМ¶etace ica eledi liotagi, pida niЙЎМ¶ijoa nawodaЙЎМ¶anadi baanoЙЎМ¶oyeloadi. Odaa onalee niiЙЎМ¶e icoa eletidi liimetedi, pida niЙЎМ¶ijoa nawodaЙЎМ¶anadi owo liciagi niЙЎМ¶ijoa eletidi liimetedi. Ica eledi dinalaketibigiwaji, icaaЙЎМ¶ica eledi boЙЎМ¶onigodi.
\v 6 NiЙЎМ¶ijo ane nebi niЙЎМ¶ijoa nawodigijedi ini ica lionigi aneliodi me yemaa. Odaa niЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi ja iiЙЎМ¶eticogi niЙЎМ¶ijo lionigi midiwataЙЎМ¶a lawodigijedi. Meetibige le, вҖҳOdeemitetibige leeЙЎМ¶odi me ionigi.вҖҷ
\v 7 Pida niЙЎМ¶ijoa nawodaЙЎМ¶anadi noЙЎМ¶onaditege niЙЎМ¶ijo lionigi, odaa dinotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶e, modi, вҖҳNiЙЎМ¶ina niЙЎМ¶ijo lionigi niЙЎМ¶ijo ane nepilidi niЙЎМ¶idiwa nawodigijedi, anicota me nepilidi niЙЎМ¶inoa lawodigijedi. JeloataЙЎМ¶a, odaa ja jakataЙЎМ¶a me ЙЎМ¶onepilidi niЙЎМ¶idiwa nawodigijedi!вҖҷ
\v 8 Odaa joЙЎМ¶odibata niЙЎМ¶ijo lionigi niЙЎМ¶ijo ane nebi nawodigijedi, odaa joЙЎМ¶oyeloadi, codaa oyaladiticogi lolaadi wetice niЙЎМ¶ijoa nawodigijedi.вҖқ
\p 
\v 9 Odaa Jesus jeЙЎМ¶eetediogi, вҖңAmiida ica anakatitiwaji meo niЙЎМ¶ijo ane nepilidi nawodigijedi? Enagi, odaa ja diiЙЎМ¶enatakatiogi monigodi niЙЎМ¶ijoa nawodaЙЎМ¶anadi, codaa yajigotiogi eletidi nawodaЙЎМ¶anadi niЙЎМ¶idiwa lawodigijedi.
\v 10 AjawienatakanaЙЎМ¶a me naЙЎМ¶a alomeЙЎМ¶enitelocotiwaji lotaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, niЙЎМ¶ijo mee,
\q1 вҖҳNaЙЎМ¶ajo wetiЙЎМ¶a anoyaladi niЙЎМ¶ijo anodabiteЙЎМ¶etini diimigi,
\q1 niЙЎМ¶ina natigide jaЙЎМ¶aniaaЙЎМ¶ani naЙЎМ¶aca wetiЙЎМ¶a ane daЙЎМ¶axa mida jaoЙЎМ¶a
\q1 caticedi niЙЎМ¶ijoa eletidi wetiadi anoibake modabiteЙЎМ¶etini diimigi.
\q1 
\v 11 JiЙЎМ¶ijaa ЗӨoniotagodi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji aneote naЙЎМ¶ajo wetiЙЎМ¶a me daЙЎМ¶axa mida ane jaoЙЎМ¶a.
\q1 Odaa jopooЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ida loenatagi.вҖҷвҖқ
\p 
\v 12 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijoa lacilodi judeutedi joЙЎМ¶oyowooЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ijo Jesus naЙЎМ¶a yatemati niЙЎМ¶ijo natematigo me lakapetedipi. Odaa joЙЎМ¶odoletibige moniwilo, pida odoitiogi niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi-nelegi. Odaa joЙЎМ¶oika Jesus, odaa joЙЎМ¶opitibeci.
\s1 NiЙЎМ¶ijoa fariseutedi oigetece Jesus migele moyediatece CГ©sar icoa dinyeelo
\r (Mateus 22.15-22; Lucas 20.20-26)
\p 
\v 13 NiЙЎМ¶ijoa lacilodi judeutedi oiiЙЎМ¶etalo Jesus icoa fariseutedi ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibeci inionigi-eliodi Herodes. OiiЙЎМ¶e migotibeci onake doЙЎМ¶owo Jesus meote okanicodaaЙЎМ¶ica ligegi ane beyagi domoЙЎМ¶owotibige me nilaagedi.
\v 14 Igotibeci midoataЙЎМ¶a Jesus, odaa moditalo, вҖңNiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶a, jowooЙЎМ¶otaЙЎМ¶a midioka limedi me enitece anewi, codaa aЙЎМ¶ica mawii niЙЎМ¶ina oko minoa anodiletibige daЙЎМ¶akaami. IgaataЙЎМ¶a aЙЎМ¶ica mawii naЙЎМ¶atetigi oko, pida ewi me iiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anitece naigi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Domige lakapetegi ЙЎМ¶onajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶egi me jedianaЙЎМ¶atece CГ©sar dinyeelo, ninionigi-eliodi romaanotedi ane ЙЎМ¶odiiЙЎМ¶e me jedianaЙЎМ¶a? Domigele me jedianaЙЎМ¶a, oЙЎМ¶oa aЙЎМ¶ele?вҖқ
\p 
\v 15 Pida Jesus yowooЙЎМ¶odi mokowo, odaa meetediogi, вҖңIgame leeЙЎМ¶odi madineenitiwatiwaji? Digawii anadeegitiwa beexo.вҖқ
\v 16 Odaa joЙЎМ¶oyadeegitalo aca beexo, naЙЎМ¶a nigetediniwace, meetediogi, вҖңAme latobi aniwoteloco ani beexo, codaa ame liboonaЙЎМ¶adi ane diniditeloco?вҖқ Odaa modi, вҖңCГ©sar.вҖқ
\v 17 Odaa Jesus meetediogi, вҖңEnice ajicitatiwaji CГ©sar ane nebi, codaa aaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a ajicitalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane nebi.вҖқ Odaa joЙЎМ¶oyopo niЙЎМ¶ijoa lotaЙЎМ¶a.
\s1 Icoa saduceutedi oigetece Jesus anodaaЙЎМ¶ee me newiЙЎМ¶atace niЙЎМ¶ina oko baanaЙЎМ¶a nigo
\r (Mateus 22.23-33; Lucas 20.27-40)
\p 
\v 18 NiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi jaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a onotalo Jesus icoa saduceutedi, niЙЎМ¶ijo anodi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me deЙЎМ¶eote me newiЙЎМ¶atace niЙЎМ¶ina oko baanaЙЎМ¶a nigo. Odaa joЙЎМ¶oige Jesus, moditalo,
\v 19 вҖңNiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶a, MoisГ©s didikotigi ЙЎМ¶odoiigi niЙЎМ¶ida najoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶egi, вҖҳNigica ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa wadonaЙЎМ¶a ane yeleo me diЙЎМ¶icata lionigipi, odaa nioxoa niЙЎМ¶ijo ane yeleo leeditibige me lodawa naЙЎМ¶ani wajekalo micoa lionaЙЎМ¶atege. Odaa niЙЎМ¶idi lionigipi micataЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶a lionigipi niЙЎМ¶ijo ane yeleo.вҖҷ
\v 20 Onica seete dinioxomigipi. NiЙЎМ¶ica liidaЙЎМ¶a naЙЎМ¶a wado, odaa ja yeleo me diЙЎМ¶ica lionigi.
\v 21 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo nioxoa liЙЎМ¶eejetewa ja lodawa naЙЎМ¶ajo wajekalo, pida niЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi jaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a yeleo me diЙЎМ¶icata lionigi. Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo eledi nioxoa jaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶eo liciagi.
\v 22 Odaa ijotawece niЙЎМ¶ijo seete dinioxomigipi nodawa ajokajo iwaalo, pida aЙЎМ¶ica anini lionigitege. NaЙЎМ¶a nigo ijotawece, odaa niЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi jaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a yeleo naЙЎМ¶ajo wajekalo.
\v 23 Ina nigeote AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji niЙЎМ¶inoa Г©maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a me newiЙЎМ¶atace, amigepidiЙЎМ¶ica niЙЎМ¶ijo seete dinioxomigi anepaЙЎМ¶a lodawa naЙЎМ¶ajo iwaalo, igaataЙЎМ¶a ijotawece nodawa naЙЎМ¶ajo iwaalo?вҖқ
\p 
\v 24 Jesus meetediogi, вҖңEliodi mabataatiwaji leeЙЎМ¶odi aЙЎМ¶owooЙЎМ¶oti aneetece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lotaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axi, oteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a owooЙЎМ¶oti AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji nimaweneЙЎМ¶egi.
\v 25 IgaataЙЎМ¶a nigicota AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji meote me newiЙЎМ¶atace niЙЎМ¶inoa Г©maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a, niЙЎМ¶ina oko aЙЎМ¶alee nadonaЙЎМ¶ateloco, pida ja liciaco aanjotedi me daЙЎМ¶a nadonaЙЎМ¶a, oteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a nigajeeЙЎМ¶a.
\v 26 EjiniЙЎМ¶ica malomeЙЎМ¶enitelocotiwaji aneetece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lotaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axi niЙЎМ¶ijo neЙЎМ¶eetece anodaaЙЎМ¶ee AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji micota meote niЙЎМ¶inoa Г©maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a me newiЙЎМ¶atace. NiЙЎМ¶ijo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me ideitedice catiwedi naЙЎМ¶ajo nialawaana ane Гӯdi, odaa meeteta MoisГ©s, вҖҳIdioka limedi me Ee NoenoЙЎМ¶odi AbraГЈo, NoenoЙЎМ¶odi Isaque, codaa me NoenoЙЎМ¶odi JacГі.вҖҷ
\v 27 Odaa niЙЎМ¶idiwa ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi dice newiЙЎМ¶a, igaataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji NoenoЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane newiЙЎМ¶a, idiЙЎМ¶ida aNoenoЙЎМ¶odi Г©maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a. Odaa eliodi makamaЙЎМ¶a adininaalenitiwaji.вҖқ
\s1 Jesus yalaЙЎМ¶ate niЙЎМ¶ica niiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶egi ane daЙЎМ¶axa mida ane jaoЙЎМ¶a
\r (Mateus 22.34-40; Lucas 10.25-28)
\p 
\v 28 Onica anigepidiЙЎМ¶ica niЙЎМ¶ijoa niiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anadi anodiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atece lajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco MoisГ©s wajipatiogi niЙЎМ¶ijoa saduceutedi modinotigimadetigi niЙЎМ¶ijoa lotaЙЎМ¶a Jesus. Codaa yowooЙЎМ¶odi Jesus mele me igiditediogi. Odaa jiЙЎМ¶igo midoataЙЎМ¶a Jesus me ige, meetalo, вҖңAmiida ica AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶egi ane daЙЎМ¶axa mida ane jaoЙЎМ¶a?вҖқ
\p 
\v 29 Odaa Jesus ja igidi, meeteta, вҖңAneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco ane daЙЎМ¶axa mida ane jaoЙЎМ¶ate, niЙЎМ¶ijo niiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶egi anee, вҖҳAjipaatatiwaji, akaami anakaami loiigi Israel! Oniniwatece ЗӨoniotagodi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, codaa Iniokiniwateda me Niotagodi inoatawece aninoa.
\v 30 Lajo memaani ЗӨaniotagodi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji manitawece ЙЎМ¶adaaleЙЎМ¶ena, codaa minitawece ЙЎМ¶adiwigo, codaa minitawece ЙЎМ¶adowoogo, codaa minitawece ЙЎМ¶adoniciwaЙЎМ¶a!вҖҷ
\v 31 Codaa ida eledi niiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶egi ane daЙЎМ¶axa mida ane jaoЙЎМ¶a, niЙЎМ¶ijo anee, вҖҳLajo memaani eledi oko digo aneni makamaЙЎМ¶a adinemaani!вҖҷ NiЙЎМ¶idoa itoataale niiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco daЙЎМ¶axa mida ane jaoЙЎМ¶ate caticedi ijoatawece niЙЎМ¶ijoa eletidi niiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco.вҖқ
\p 
\v 32 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo niiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶a meetalo Jesus, вҖңNiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶a, ele motaЙЎМ¶ani! Me enitece anewi niЙЎМ¶ijo neЙЎМ¶eni me oniniwatece ЗӨoniotagodi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, odaa aЙЎМ¶icoa eledi aneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.
\v 33 Codaa daЙЎМ¶axa mele me jemaanaЙЎМ¶a manitawece ЙЎМ¶odaaleЙЎМ¶ena, minitawece ica ЙЎМ¶odowoogo, codaa minitawece ЙЎМ¶odiwigo, codaa minitawece ЙЎМ¶odoniciwaЙЎМ¶a. Odaa daЙЎМ¶axa mele me jemaanaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina eledi oko anodaaЙЎМ¶ejinaЙЎМ¶a me idinemaanaЙЎМ¶a, aliciagi niЙЎМ¶ina me jalecaЙЎМ¶a eijedi maditaЙЎМ¶a nameeja AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me idinilakidenaЙЎМ¶atege leeЙЎМ¶odi ЙЎМ¶obeyaceЙЎМ¶eco, codaa niЙЎМ¶ina me jiboonaЙЎМ¶atalo eletidi ЙЎМ¶oboonaЙЎМ¶a.вҖқ
\p 
\v 34 Jesus nadi niЙЎМ¶ijo niiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶a ane diiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atece lajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco MoisГ©s mida lixakedi niЙЎМ¶ijo me igidi. Odaa Jesus meeteta, вҖңJa domaЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶adigomi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me iiЙЎМ¶e ЙЎМ¶adaaleЙЎМ¶ena.вҖқ NiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi naЙЎМ¶a nigotedini Jesus me dotaЙЎМ¶a, odaa aЙЎМ¶aleeЙЎМ¶ica anabo laaleЙЎМ¶ena me ige me dineetalo.
\s1 Jesus digikatetece NiЙЎМ¶icoa ane nimonyatedoЙЎМ¶owa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji
\r (Mateus 22.41-46; Lucas 20.41-44)
\p 
\v 35 NiЙЎМ¶ijo Jesus me diiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶a minitaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liЙЎМ¶eladi, odaa ja nigetediniwace niЙЎМ¶ijo oko, meetediogi, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ijoa niiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anadi anodiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atece lajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco MoisГ©s, igame leeЙЎМ¶odi moyakadi modi NiЙЎМ¶icoa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane niiЙЎМ¶e mokexaa ida aneetege licoЙЎМ¶egi Davi?
\v 36 IgaataЙЎМ¶a Liwigo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji eo Davi me dotaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ijo neЙЎМ¶ee,
\q1 вҖҳInoenoЙЎМ¶odi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji meeteta Iniotagodi,
\q1 вҖңAnicootini iwai ibaaЙЎМ¶adi nigepaa iЙЎМ¶eke inatawece ЙЎМ¶aneloЙЎМ¶ododipiвҖқ.вҖҷ
\p 
\v 37 IjaaЙЎМ¶ijo Davi meetalo, вҖҳIniotagodiвҖҷ. Enige igamigodaaЙЎМ¶ee NiЙЎМ¶icoa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane nimonya me yakadi mokexaa ida aneetege licoЙЎМ¶egi Davi?вҖқ NiЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi-nelegi eliodi moyemaa niЙЎМ¶ijoa lotaЙЎМ¶a Jesus.
\s1 Jesus yalaЙЎМ¶ate niЙЎМ¶ijoa niiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anadi anodiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atece lajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco MoisГ©s
\r (Mateus 23.1-36; Lucas 11.45-53; 20.45-47)
\p 
\v 38 Jesus niiЙЎМ¶axitediniwace oko, odaa meetediogi, вҖңAnidakitiogi niЙЎМ¶ijoa niiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anadi anodiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atece lajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco MoisГ©s! IgaataЙЎМ¶a lemaanigi me ewaligitibigiwaji modinixotinigi toonicogo ocaЙЎМ¶ataЙЎМ¶a ane lowoodaЙЎМ¶agi niЙЎМ¶ina oko ЙЎМ¶oneЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a owotibige monicetibigiwaji codaa modeemitetibige miditaЙЎМ¶a licooЙЎМ¶adi oko.
\v 39 Lemaanigi monicotelogo nibaancotedi niЙЎМ¶ina oko ЙЎМ¶oneЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a midiwataЙЎМ¶a niiakanaЙЎМ¶axiidi, codaa midiwataЙЎМ¶a nibaancotedi niЙЎМ¶ina oko anoiweniЙЎМ¶ide miditaЙЎМ¶a nalooЙЎМ¶o.
\v 40 Codaa oibanootece liЙЎМ¶elatedi codaa ane nepilidi niЙЎМ¶inoda wajekalodipi, codaa onowo niЙЎМ¶ina mocaЙЎМ¶ataЙЎМ¶a moyotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶e AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji micota meliodi me iloikatiditedibigiwaji.вҖқ
\s1 Aca wajekalo yajigotalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji icoatawece niЙЎМ¶icoa ninyeelo ane yopotibige
\r (Lucas 21.1-4)
\p 
\v 41 Jesus nicotedi minitaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liЙЎМ¶eladi ipegitetege naЙЎМ¶ajo iwokodaЙЎМ¶axi nelegi aneitice niЙЎМ¶ina oko moyokoletinigi ninyeelo anoibootalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Iwi anodaaЙЎМ¶ee niЙЎМ¶ijo oko moyajigo ninyeelo. Eliodi oko ane liicotedi oyajigo owidi dinyeelo.
\v 42 Odaa niЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi jaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶icotio aca wajekalo madewete, odaa ja yokoletinigi naЙЎМ¶ajo iwokodaЙЎМ¶axi iniodataale beexotedi.
\v 43 Odaa Jesus jeЙЎМ¶eniditediogi niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece, odaa meetediogi, вҖңEjitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji naЙЎМ¶ada wajekalo madewete yajigo caticedi niЙЎМ¶ina eledi oko anoyajigo.
\v 44 LeeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ina eledi oko oyajigo ninyeelo ane doЙЎМ¶oyopotibige, pida naЙЎМ¶ajo wajekalo baЙЎМ¶a yajigo ijoatawece ninyeelo, ane domaЙЎМ¶a yopotibige me dinoojetetibige ane yeligo.вҖқ
\c 13
\s1 Jesus yalaЙЎМ¶ate moyojiketini AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liЙЎМ¶eladi
\r (Mateus 24.1-2; Lucas 21.5-6)
\p 
\v 1 NiЙЎМ¶ijo Jesus naЙЎМ¶a doletedibige me noditedice AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liЙЎМ¶eladi, anigepidiЙЎМ¶ica niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece meetalo, вҖңЗӨoniiЙЎМ¶axinoЙЎМ¶odi, digawini niЙЎМ¶inoa wetiadi nelecoli minitaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ini diimigi! Codaa digawini niЙЎМ¶ica me libinienigi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liЙЎМ¶eladi!вҖқ
\p 
\v 2 Odaa Jesus ja igidi, meeteta, вҖңNaЙЎМ¶anati niЙЎМ¶ini diimigi-nelegi? Anigida noko otaЙЎМ¶anitece wetiЙЎМ¶a dipeteloco eledi minitaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ini diimigi, onanikatedini idiwatawece.вҖқ
\s1 Jesus yalaЙЎМ¶ate micota minoa ane dakaketoЙЎМ¶odomi
\r (Mateus 24.3-14; Lucas 21.8-19)
\p 
\v 3 Jesus idiaaЙЎМ¶itedice minitaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ijo lojotaЙЎМ¶adi ane liboonaЙЎМ¶adi вҖңLojotaЙЎМ¶adi OliveiraвҖқ nicotedi, dilokotetege AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liЙЎМ¶eladi. IdiaaЙЎМ¶itedice oniniwatece, odaa joЙЎМ¶ototalo Pedro, Tiago, JoГЈo ijaa AndrГ©. Odaa joЙЎМ¶oige, moditalo,
\v 4 вҖңAnatematiitoЙЎМ¶owa niЙЎМ¶ica noko nigoyojiketini AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liЙЎМ¶eladi. Codaa igamigodaaЙЎМ¶ee AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me ikee nige nipegi moyanikatini?вҖқ
\p 
\v 5 Jesus jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶eyatedigi me yeloЙЎМ¶oditediogi, odaa meetediogi, вҖңAdinowetitiwaji adiЙЎМ¶ica ane ЙЎМ¶adinaaleni!
\v 6 Eliodi oko ane dinikeetibigiwaji, oibake IboonaЙЎМ¶adi, odaa modi, вҖҳEe NiЙЎМ¶ijo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane nimonya.вҖҷ Odaa eliodi oko anoninaaletiniwace.
\v 7 Pida jinaЙЎМ¶adoiitiwaji nigajipaata layaco witidi, codaa nigabodicetigi witidi, igaataЙЎМ¶a leeditibige mina ane diniwitideЙЎМ¶etiwage. Pida aniЙЎМ¶icota niЙЎМ¶ica noko AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me yaaЙЎМ¶adi niЙЎМ¶ina iiЙЎМ¶o.
\v 8 IgaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina noiigi dinideleЙЎМ¶etiwage, codaa niЙЎМ¶inoa inionaЙЎМ¶a oiiЙЎМ¶e loiigi me witidi. Codaa icota me datalale iiЙЎМ¶o owidi nipodaЙЎМ¶a, codaa eliodi noiigi nigodi nigigi, codaa mowidi ЙЎМ¶oninyaco ane doide. Pida niЙЎМ¶inoa nawikodico jiЙЎМ¶inaaЙЎМ¶odoejedi me nawikodico liciagi niЙЎМ¶ina odoejegi lileenaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶egi naЙЎМ¶ana iwaalo ipileЙЎМ¶e.
\p 
\v 9 Pida adinowetitiwaji, igaataЙЎМ¶a etiЙЎМ¶adadeegiticogi lodoe niЙЎМ¶ijoa lacilodi, codaa etiЙЎМ¶adalakenitibigetiwaji midiwataЙЎМ¶a niiakanaЙЎМ¶axiidi. Codaa leeЙЎМ¶odi maniwitici, odaa etiЙЎМ¶adadeegiticogi lodoe niЙЎМ¶ina aninoa naЙЎМ¶atetico codaa midiwataЙЎМ¶a inionaЙЎМ¶a-eloodoli moiwi anodigotaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji. Odaa jiЙЎМ¶idaa nigakatitiwaji madatematiitiogi niЙЎМ¶idiwa lacilodi.
\v 10 Pida maleedaЙЎМ¶a yaaЙЎМ¶aditeda AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji niЙЎМ¶ina iiЙЎМ¶o, leeditibigetiwaji matematiitiogi inatawece niЙЎМ¶ina noiigi nibodicetedi anele anoyalaЙЎМ¶atiwa.
\v 11 Nige etiЙЎМ¶adiwilotiwaji, odaa jeЙЎМ¶etiЙЎМ¶adadeegiticogi lodoe niЙЎМ¶inoa lacilodi moiwi anodigotaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji, jinaЙЎМ¶a aЙЎМ¶owikomataatiwaji ane alitigi ЙЎМ¶agegi maleedaЙЎМ¶a etiЙЎМ¶adadeegitiwaji. IgaataЙЎМ¶a enitece niЙЎМ¶ica AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane ikeetedaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji me alitigi ЙЎМ¶agegi. IgaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶inoa ЙЎМ¶adotaЙЎМ¶a aicoЙЎМ¶oticogi makaamitaЙЎМ¶atiwaji, pida icoЙЎМ¶oticogi minitaЙЎМ¶a Liwigo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.
\v 12 Icota dinioxomigipi moyajigo epaa nioxoadipi monigodi, codaa niЙЎМ¶ina eniododipi oyajigo lionaЙЎМ¶a, codaa nionigipi dakapetege eliododipi, odaa oibootiobece monigodi.
\v 13 Eliodi oko oyelataЙЎМ¶adomitiwaji leeЙЎМ¶odi maniwitici. Pida AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji eote midioka limedi me yewiЙЎМ¶a miniwataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane ixomaЙЎМ¶ateetedice lawikodico, codaa me deЙЎМ¶eyamaЙЎМ¶atice eliwaЙЎМ¶atakaneЙЎМ¶egi.
\s1 Ica nawikodigi nelegi
\r (Mateus 24.15-28; Lucas 21.20-24)
\p 
\v 14 Icota manati niЙЎМ¶ica aneetece Daniel, niЙЎМ¶ijo ane yeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lowooko niЙЎМ¶ijo jotigide, me yalaЙЎМ¶ata niЙЎМ¶ica niwigo noenatagi aneo niЙЎМ¶ina oko ligecaЙЎМ¶aloЙЎМ¶o, libikotanaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶adi ane nigodi oko. Icota moidoyatice niЙЎМ¶ica niwigo digoida ane deЙЎМ¶ele me itice. NiЙЎМ¶ina ane yalomeЙЎМ¶eteloco niЙЎМ¶idiwa notaЙЎМ¶a ele me dinoniciwaЙЎМ¶adi me yowooЙЎМ¶odi ane diitigilo. Nigonadi niЙЎМ¶ica niwigo, niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane ideitice nipodigi JudГ©ia leeditibige me daleditibigimoace odeletibigimece wetiadi nelecoli.
\v 15 Nigica oko ane idei ditibigimedi liЙЎМ¶eladi lelГЎЙЎМ¶a, ele me daЙЎМ¶adakatio me dibatalo ane nepilidi.
\v 16 Codaa nigica anidiaaЙЎМ¶itice nixoЙЎМ¶otagi ele me doЙЎМ¶opitacio minitaЙЎМ¶a liЙЎМ¶eladi me igota nicaapa.
\v 17 Pida iwikodadipi iwaalepodi ipilaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a codaa eniododipi analee oilipeЙЎМ¶e lionaЙЎМ¶a!
\v 18 Ele mipokitalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me daЙЎМ¶a ikateda meyoketege niwetaЙЎМ¶a nige limedi me ialeticoace.
\v 19 IgaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶icoa nokododi owidi nawikodico. NiЙЎМ¶ijo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me iliidaЙЎМ¶adi niЙЎМ¶ina iiЙЎМ¶o codaa niЙЎМ¶ina natigide aЙЎМ¶ica nawikodigi liciagi niЙЎМ¶icoa nawikodico anenagi. Codaa aЙЎМ¶aleeЙЎМ¶icota eledi nawikodigi liciagi niЙЎМ¶inoa nawikodico anenagi.
\v 20 ЗӨoniotagodi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji noxopanatidi niЙЎМ¶icoa nokododi minoa nawikodico. DaaditaЙЎМ¶a noxopanatiditeda niЙЎМ¶icoa nokododi, agotiЙЎМ¶ica ane yakadi me yewiЙЎМ¶a. Pida noxopanatidi niЙЎМ¶icoa nokododi leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane iolatedice idioka limedi me newiЙЎМ¶a miniwataЙЎМ¶a.
\p 
\v 21 Nigica aneetaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji, вҖҳDigawini! NiЙЎМ¶ijoa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane nimonya etidoa digoina!вҖҷ oЙЎМ¶oa migetoЙЎМ¶odi, вҖҳDigawini! Etidoa digoida!вҖҷ JinaЙЎМ¶a iwaЙЎМ¶atitiwaji.
\v 22 IgaataЙЎМ¶a eliodi oko awitakaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a icota modi me niЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶idoa NiЙЎМ¶ijoa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane nimonya, oЙЎМ¶oa domigodi me niЙЎМ¶ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo niЙЎМ¶ijo anoyeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lowooko. Odaa owote ЙЎМ¶odoxiceЙЎМ¶etedi, codaa niЙЎМ¶inoa anetiЙЎМ¶odawelaЙЎМ¶adi moninaaletiniwace oko. Codaa domaЙЎМ¶a oninaaletiniwace niЙЎМ¶ina oko AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane iolatedicoace me nepilidi.
\v 23 Pida adinowetitiwaji! Ja jao ЙЎМ¶adeemidi maleedaЙЎМ¶a icotalo niЙЎМ¶inoa nawikodico anejitalo.
\s1 Lanokegi ЗӨoneleegiwa ane icoЙЎМ¶otibigimece ditibigimedi
\r (Mateus 24.29-35; Lucas 21.25-33)
\p 
\v 24 NigidiaaЙЎМ¶idi, nige ixomaЙЎМ¶atedijo niЙЎМ¶icoa nokododi menagi niЙЎМ¶icoa nawikodico, odaa aligeЙЎМ¶e ipe, codaa me epenai aЙЎМ¶alee datale.
\v 25 NiЙЎМ¶inoa yotetitedi niwadetedi. Odaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji itineЙЎМ¶e niwicidi anida nimaweneЙЎМ¶egi digoida ditibigimedi.
\v 26 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ina oko etidadi Ee, ЗӨoneleegiwa ane jicoЙЎМ¶otibigimece ditibigimedi. Idinikatini jiniotinece lolaadi, odaa janagi meliodi inimaweneЙЎМ¶egi, codaa jikee mida inaЙЎМ¶atetigi liciagi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji naЙЎМ¶atetigi.
\v 27 JiiЙЎМ¶e iniaanjotedi migoteloco inatawece niЙЎМ¶ina iiЙЎМ¶o moniodatece niЙЎМ¶ina oko AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane iolatedicoace me nepilidi.
\p 
\v 28 Digowoo naЙЎМ¶ana niale fiigoigo, odaa akati mowooЙЎМ¶oti. Nige dione libiwedi, codaa laamotiidi naЙЎМ¶a nokoloЙЎМ¶o, odaa joЙЎМ¶owooЙЎМ¶otitiwaji naЙЎМ¶a nipegi limedi ebicitedi.
\v 29 Odaa jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee nigeno niЙЎМ¶icoa nawikodico, odaa jaЙЎМ¶akati mowooЙЎМ¶otitiwaji naЙЎМ¶a nipegi niЙЎМ¶ica noko moyaaЙЎМ¶adi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liЙЎМ¶eladi.
\v 30 EjitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji niЙЎМ¶ina anewi. Icotece inoatawece niЙЎМ¶inoa anejitedaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji maleedaЙЎМ¶a nigo eliodi oko ane newiЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina noko.
\v 31 Ditibigimedi inaa iiЙЎМ¶o icota me ma, pida yotaЙЎМ¶a baadaЙЎМ¶a ixomaЙЎМ¶atedice.
\s1 AЙЎМ¶ica ane yowooЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ica noko Jesus nige dopitedijo
\r (Mateus 24.36-44)
\p 
\v 32 Odaa aЙЎМ¶ica ane yowooЙЎМ¶odi naЙЎМ¶aca lakata oteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ica noko nige idopitijo. OteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶idiwa aanjotedi digoida ditibigimedi aЙЎМ¶oyowooЙЎМ¶odi, oteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a Ee, Lionigi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ajowooЙЎМ¶odi. Pida iniokiniwateda AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane Eiodi, baЙЎМ¶a yowooЙЎМ¶odi.
\v 33 Adinowetitiwaji, codaa midioka limedi me ЙЎМ¶adigomi codaa otaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eni AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji igaataЙЎМ¶a aЙЎМ¶owooЙЎМ¶otitiwaji nigeno niЙЎМ¶ica noko.
\v 34 NiЙЎМ¶ida me Ee iciagi niЙЎМ¶ina ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa anigo diniwiajeticogi eledi iiЙЎМ¶o. Odaa yajigota naЙЎМ¶atetigi niЙЎМ¶idiwa liimetedi, codaa yajigota oninitecibeci epaa libakedi. Odaa ja iiЙЎМ¶e niЙЎМ¶ini nowienoЙЎМ¶odi diimigi midiaanaЙЎМ¶a iЙЎМ¶oadita me dinowedi.
\v 35 Enice, adinowetitiwaji, igaataЙЎМ¶a aЙЎМ¶owooЙЎМ¶oti niЙЎМ¶ica noko nige idopitijo, Ee, ane iciagi niЙЎМ¶ijo ane nebi diimigi. Yakadi me ЙЎМ¶ocidi, domige liwigo-enoale, domige niЙЎМ¶idatege nigoi, oЙЎМ¶oa domige naЙЎМ¶a yeloЙЎМ¶otibige, nige idopitijo.
\v 36 Enice adinowetitiwaji amaleeЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a nige aweleЙЎМ¶egi me idopitijo, odaa aЙЎМ¶adakatitiwaji me iote, oteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a me daЙЎМ¶awii niЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶abakedi ane joyataЙЎМ¶adomitiwaji mawii.
\v 37 NiЙЎМ¶ida anejitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji, ejitiogi iditawece iotagipi, maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a dinoweditibigiwaji!вҖқ
\c 14
\s1 NiЙЎМ¶ijoa lacilodi judeutedi odoletibige nimaweneЙЎМ¶egi moyeloadi Jesus
\r (Mateus 26.1-5; Lucas 22.1-2; JoГЈo 11.45-53)
\p 
\v 1 Aniaditibige itoataale nokododi daЙЎМ¶a nakatio nalokegi anodita me PГЎscoa, codaa niЙЎМ¶ijo eledi nalokegi anodita вҖңLalokegi paon ane diЙЎМ¶ica labookojegiвҖқ. NiЙЎМ¶ijo anoiiЙЎМ¶e sacerdotitedi ijaaЙЎМ¶ijoa niЙЎМ¶ijoa niiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anadi anodiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atece lajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco MoisГ©s odoletibige niЙЎМ¶ica nimaweneЙЎМ¶egi modolicetalo Jesus moyeloadi.
\v 2 Pida modi, вҖңAЙЎМ¶ele me jibaЙЎМ¶atalo midi nalooЙЎМ¶o ade jaoЙЎМ¶atibige niЙЎМ¶idi noiigi metiЙЎМ¶odideleЙЎМ¶e.вҖқ
\s1 Aca iwaalo yadotigi Jesus lacilo nadokojegi
\r (Mateus 26.6-13; JoГЈo 12.1-8)
\p 
\v 3 NiЙЎМ¶ijo Jesus midiaaЙЎМ¶itedice manitaЙЎМ¶a nigotakawaana BetГўnia, minitaЙЎМ¶a liЙЎМ¶eladi SimГЈo niЙЎМ¶ijo anijo me dawace-lolaadi. NaЙЎМ¶aniodi, jiЙЎМ¶igo aca iwaalo miniwataЙЎМ¶a yadeegi aca bootawaana wetiЙЎМ¶a ane liboonaЙЎМ¶adi вҖңalabastroвҖқ. NaЙЎМ¶ajo bootawaana nolee nadokojegi ane liboonaЙЎМ¶adi вҖңnardoвҖқ. NiЙЎМ¶ijo nadokojegi aЙЎМ¶ica gaantiЙЎМ¶ini lalegedi, codaa dakake loojedi. NaЙЎМ¶ajo iwaalo noyaaЙЎМ¶adi naЙЎМ¶ajo bootawaana, odaa ja yadoteloco Jesus lacilo niЙЎМ¶ijo nadokojegi.
\v 4 Ica oko anidiaaЙЎМ¶itice anonadi oyelatema, odaa dinotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶e, modi, вҖңIgame leeЙЎМ¶odi me yame ida nadokojegi?
\v 5 AЙЎМ¶oniaaЙЎМ¶eyaa niЙЎМ¶ida nadokojegi loojedi caticedi miniwatadaЙЎМ¶ani taalia beexotedi (abotege loojedi onidateci nicaaЙЎМ¶abi me jibaaЙЎМ¶a), oditaЙЎМ¶a yajigotiogi niЙЎМ¶inoa madewetedi niЙЎМ¶idiwa dinyeelo owidi.вҖқ Odaa joЙЎМ¶oyapeteЙЎМ¶e naЙЎМ¶ajo iwaalo.
\p 
\v 6 Pida Jesus meetediogi, вҖңIkanitiwaji naЙЎМ¶ani iwaalo! Igame leeЙЎМ¶odi manapeteЙЎМ¶enitice? Eotomi niЙЎМ¶ica nibakedi libinienigi.
\v 7 IgaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶inoa madewetedi idioka limedi mina makaamitaЙЎМ¶atiwaji, odaa akati me axawanitiogi nigemaani. Pida Ee baadiЙЎМ¶idioka limedi minaaЙЎМ¶ejotice makaamitaЙЎМ¶atiwaji.
\v 8 NaЙЎМ¶ani iwaalo eo niЙЎМ¶ica ane yakadi meo. Enagi maleedaЙЎМ¶a ideleo nenyaЙЎМ¶adi yolaadi monaligitini.
\v 9 EjitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji niЙЎМ¶ina anewi. NiЙЎМ¶ina moyatematitedibece niЙЎМ¶inoa nibodicetedi anele aneetici inatawece iiЙЎМ¶o, oyatematitibece niЙЎМ¶ida aneotomi moyalaЙЎМ¶atibige naЙЎМ¶ani iwaalo.вҖқ
\s1 Judas dinilakidetege niЙЎМ¶ijoa lacilodi judeutedi me yajigo Jesus
\r (Mateus 26.14-16; Lucas 22.3-6)
\p 
\v 10 Judas Iscariotes niЙЎМ¶ijo anida aneetege niЙЎМ¶ijo dooze anodiotibece Jesus igo yotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶e niЙЎМ¶ijo anoiiЙЎМ¶e sacerdotitedi me dinilakidetege me yajigo Jesus.
\v 11 Odaa eliodi me ninitibigiwaji noЙЎМ¶owajipa ane ligegi, odaa joЙЎМ¶odinilakidetege moyedia. Odaa Judas jiЙЎМ¶idaa dinanatigi me doletibige niЙЎМ¶ica nimaweneЙЎМ¶egi me yajigo Jesus.
\s1 Jesus ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece oyeligo liweenigi nalokegi PГЎscoa
\r (Mateus 26.17-25; Lucas 22.7-14, 21-23; JoГЈo 13.21-30)
\p 
\v 12 NiЙЎМ¶ijo odoejegi noko nalokegi ane liboonaЙЎМ¶adi вҖңPaon ane diЙЎМ¶ica labookojegiвҖқ, niЙЎМ¶ijoa judeutedi onigodi waxacocoli me odinenyaЙЎМ¶aditege moyoe liweenigi nige nakatio nalokegi PГЎscoa. NiЙЎМ¶ijo noko niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece oige Jesus, moditalo, вҖңIgamemaani meitice me joenaЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶oweenigi lajo PГЎscoa?вҖқ
\p 
\v 13 Odaa Jesus ja iiЙЎМ¶e itoataale niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece, meetediogi, вҖңEmiitiwaji nigotaЙЎМ¶a, odaa akapetege ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa ane yoyaЙЎМ¶adi leo ane nolee ninyoЙЎМ¶odi. Odaa iwitecetiwaji lowidi niЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa.
\v 14 Nige dakatiwece diimigi, enitatiwaji niЙЎМ¶ini ane nebi diimigi, вҖҳЗӨoniiЙЎМ¶axinoЙЎМ¶odi ЙЎМ¶odiiЙЎМ¶e me jigikanaЙЎМ¶atigi ane diЙЎМ¶etigi ica ЙЎМ¶odicooЙЎМ¶adi aneitice me jelicaЙЎМ¶a liweenigi nalokegi PГЎscoa me ligiiwepodi anodiotibece.вҖҷ
\v 15 Odaa ikeetaЙЎМ¶awa ЙЎМ¶odicooЙЎМ¶adi nelegi ditibigimedi dalaЙЎМ¶ate diimigi. NiЙЎМ¶ini ЙЎМ¶odicooЙЎМ¶adi jaigo, codaa idiwa inoatawece ane jopooЙЎМ¶atibige. Odaa oenitiwaji ЙЎМ¶oweenigi lajo nalokegi PГЎscoa.вҖқ
\p 
\v 16 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo itoataale anodiotibece jiЙЎМ¶igotibeci, odaa joЙЎМ¶oyakadi ijoatawece niЙЎМ¶ijoa aneetediogi Jesus. Odaa joЙЎМ¶oyoe ica liweenigi PГЎscoa.
\p 
\v 17 NiЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a dawike, Jesus jiЙЎМ¶icotedio minitaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ijo diimigi lixigaЙЎМ¶awepodi niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece.
\v 18 Odaa eЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee me niodaЙЎМ¶a maditaЙЎМ¶a nameeja, Jesus meetediogi, вҖңEjitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji niЙЎМ¶ina anewi, ini niЙЎМ¶ina akaamitiwaji anadigiwani, idajigotiogi ineloЙЎМ¶ododipi.вҖқ
\v 19 Odaa jiЙЎМ¶idaa diiticogi magecaЙЎМ¶alodipi, codaa oninitecibeci ige Jesus, meetalo, вҖңDomige ee ЙЎМ¶adajici? EjidaЙЎМ¶a jakadi daЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶adajici!вҖқ
\v 20 Odaa Jesus meetediogi, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ini ane ititinigi nipaon liwagedi midataЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶odokoladi niЙЎМ¶ina akaamitiwaji anakaami igiiwepodi, jiЙЎМ¶iniaa idajigo.
\v 21 LotaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji yalaЙЎМ¶atiwa, Ee, ЗӨoneleegiwa ane jicoЙЎМ¶otibigimece ditibigimedi, me leeditibige me ideleo. Pida nagoodi niЙЎМ¶ini ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa ane idajigotiogi ineloЙЎМ¶ododipi, Ee, ЗӨoneleegiwa ane jicoЙЎМ¶otibigimece ditibigimedi. EjimetaЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶axa meletema niЙЎМ¶ini ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa daaditiЙЎМ¶icata menitini! (IgaataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji eliodi me iloikatidi niЙЎМ¶ini ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa.)вҖқ
\s1 Ica owidijegi liweenigi ЗӨoniotagodi
\r (Mateus 26.26-30; Lucas 22.15-20; 1 CorГӯntios 11.23-25)
\p 
\v 22 NiЙЎМ¶ijo maleeЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee me niodaЙЎМ¶a, Jesus dibate ijo paon, odaa diniotagodete AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ijo paon. NaЙЎМ¶a ninoketedini niЙЎМ¶ijo paon, odaa ja yajigotediogi niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece. Odaa meetediogi, вҖңNee, abaategetiwaji! NiЙЎМ¶idi paon jiciaceeketege yolaadi.вҖқ
\v 23 NiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi odaa jaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a dibate aca goopa ane nolee viinyo. NaЙЎМ¶a diniotagodete AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, odaa ja yajigotediogi naЙЎМ¶ajo goopa ane nolee viinyo, odaa ijotawece owacipeta niЙЎМ¶ijo viinyo.
\v 24 Odaa Jesus meetediogi, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ida viinyo jiciaceeketege yawodi ane inadooЙЎМ¶odi leeЙЎМ¶odi eliodi oko. Odaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji jiЙЎМ¶ida gela nimaweneЙЎМ¶egi me dinilakidetetege niЙЎМ¶ina oko leeЙЎМ¶odi me inadooЙЎМ¶odi yawodi.
\v 25 EjitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji niЙЎМ¶ina anewi. AЙЎМ¶alee jacipe niЙЎМ¶ida viinyo nigepaaЙЎМ¶icota me iiЙЎМ¶e AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji laaleЙЎМ¶enali niЙЎМ¶ina oko, odaa micataЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶a jacipeta gela latopagi viinyo.вҖқ
\v 26 NaЙЎМ¶a nigotiniwace me nigaanaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶a, moigaa onateciЙЎМ¶ijoa Elaco Davi, odaa ja noditicoaci, jiЙЎМ¶igotibeci minitaЙЎМ¶a lojotaЙЎМ¶adi ane liboonaЙЎМ¶adi вҖңLojotaЙЎМ¶adi OliveiraвҖқ.
\s1 Jesus eote leemidi Pedro iditawece niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece icota me ilaagitibece
\r (Mateus 26.31-35; Lucas 22.31-34; JoГЈo 13.36-38)
\p 
\v 27 Jesus meetediogi niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece, вҖңInaaЙЎМ¶ina niЙЎМ¶ina enoale, akaamitawecetiwaji adikani, igaataЙЎМ¶a diniditeloco maditaЙЎМ¶a lotaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane yalaЙЎМ¶ate AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, niЙЎМ¶ijo mee,
\q1 вҖҳJeloadi niЙЎМ¶ini nowienoЙЎМ¶odi waxacocoli,
\q1 odaa niЙЎМ¶idiwa waxacocoli ilaagitiwaji.вҖҷ
\m 
\v 28 Pida nigidiaaЙЎМ¶idi nige idewiЙЎМ¶atace, ejigo ЙЎМ¶adodoetiwaji miditaЙЎМ¶a nipodigi GalilГ©ia.вҖқ
\p 
\v 29 Pida Pedro meetalo, вҖңIcaaЙЎМ¶ica nige inatawece etiЙЎМ¶adikani, pida ee baadaЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶adikani!вҖқ
\p 
\v 30 Odaa Jesus meeteta, вҖңEjitaЙЎМ¶awa niЙЎМ¶ina anewi. InaaЙЎМ¶ina niЙЎМ¶ina enoale, aniЙЎМ¶icatibige daЙЎМ¶a itoataale manoe okoЙЎМ¶okoodi, odaa itoatadiЙЎМ¶ida meni me daЙЎМ¶adowooЙЎМ¶oti.вҖқ
\p 
\v 31 Pida Pedro dinoniciwaЙЎМ¶aditibece me igidi, mee, вҖңIca deЙЎМ¶eji me daЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶adowooЙЎМ¶oti, icaaЙЎМ¶ica nige leeditibige makaami yemaЙЎМ¶awa, ja idigo makaami yemaЙЎМ¶awa!вҖқ Odaa ijotawece niЙЎМ¶ijo eledi anodiotibece idaaЙЎМ¶oyatigi ligegi.
\s1 Jesus yotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶e AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji midiwataЙЎМ¶a nawodigijedi nialeli вҖңoliveiraвҖқ ane liboonaЙЎМ¶adi GetsГӘmani
\r (Mateus 26.36-46; Lucas 22.39-46)
\p 
\v 32 Jesus ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece igotibeci midiwataЙЎМ¶a nawodigijedi nialeli вҖңoliveiraвҖқ ane liboonaЙЎМ¶adi GetsГӘmani. NiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi meetediogi, вҖңInaaЙЎМ¶oni anicootiniwacetiwaji, ejigo jotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶e AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.вҖқ
\v 33 BaЙЎМ¶a yadeegi lixigaЙЎМ¶awepodi Pedro, Tiago ijaa JoГЈo. Odaa jiЙЎМ¶idaa diiticogi meliodi magecaЙЎМ¶alo, doitedibece, codaa me doЙЎМ¶owikomata.
\v 34 Odaa meetediogi, вҖңCatiwedi yaaleЙЎМ¶ena eliodi me Ee agecaЙЎМ¶alo, ane jeemitetece liciagi niЙЎМ¶ina daantaЙЎМ¶a doletibige me ideleo. InaaЙЎМ¶onitetiwaji, codaa adinoweti.вҖқ
\p 
\v 35 Odaa jiЙЎМ¶igoawaanigi odoe, odaa ja yamaЙЎМ¶atedinigiiЙЎМ¶o lokotidi, odaa dipokote AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji dokaaЙЎМ¶a yakadi me yatamaЙЎМ¶ateetetege naЙЎМ¶aca lakata niЙЎМ¶icoa lawikodico.
\v 36 Odaa Jesus mee, вҖңEiodi yemaanigi, akati mawii okanicodaaЙЎМ¶ica. Nigemaani adatamaЙЎМ¶ateenitege niЙЎМ¶icoa yawikodico ane leeditibige me jixomaЙЎМ¶ateetedice! Pida jemaa me jao niЙЎМ¶ica anemaani, idiЙЎМ¶ida aЙЎМ¶inokinoa niЙЎМ¶inoa ane emaЙЎМ¶a jemaa me jaote.вҖқ
\p 
\v 37 NiЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a dopitetege niЙЎМ¶ijo itoatadiЙЎМ¶ida anodiotibece, odaa enotediogi me niotaЙЎМ¶ateloco, odaa meeteta SimГЈo Pedro, вҖңSimГЈo, iote? AЙЎМ¶akati madinoweti oteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a onaniteci lakata?
\v 38 Adinowetitiwaji, codaa otaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eni AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me daЙЎМ¶a abataa nige dineetaЙЎМ¶awa SatanГЎs. IgaataЙЎМ¶a beЙЎМ¶emaani mawiitiwaji niЙЎМ¶ina AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane yemaa, pida aЙЎМ¶ica ЙЎМ¶adoniciwaЙЎМ¶atiwaji.вҖқ
\p 
\v 39 Jesus ja yetecetacedicoace niЙЎМ¶ijo itoatadiЙЎМ¶ida anodiotibece, odaa jiЙЎМ¶igotace yotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶e AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji yopilaЙЎМ¶ateetedeloco ijaaЙЎМ¶ijoatace niЙЎМ¶ijoa ane lotaЙЎМ¶ate.
\v 40 NaЙЎМ¶a dopitacedijo miditaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece, odaa jeЙЎМ¶enotacediogi me niotaЙЎМ¶a. LeeЙЎМ¶odi eliodi me liotaЙЎМ¶a, codaa aЙЎМ¶oyakadi me noleticoace. Odaa aЙЎМ¶oyowooЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ica anoyatigi ligegi moyotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶e Jesus.
\p 
\v 41 NiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi Jesus jiЙЎМ¶igotace yotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶e AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. NiЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a itoatadiЙЎМ¶ida me dopitacediogi niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece, odaa meetediogi, вҖңEЙЎМ¶iotetiwaji, eЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee manipenitiniwace? JaЙЎМ¶abotiwaji! NaЙЎМ¶aca inilakata me jawikode ja nipegi micoteloco. JeЙЎМ¶etidajigotiogi libaaЙЎМ¶adi niЙЎМ¶ijoa ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a, Ee, ЗӨoneleegiwa ane jicoЙЎМ¶otibigimece ditibigimedi.
\v 42 Adabititiniwacetiwaji, jopilaЙЎМ¶a! Digawini! Etina jeЙЎМ¶enagi niЙЎМ¶ijo ane idajigotiogi ineloЙЎМ¶ododipi.вҖқ
\s1 Jesus diniwilo
\r (Mateus 26.47-56; Lucas 22.47-53; JoГЈo 18.3-11)
\p 
\v 43 EЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶eeteda me dotaЙЎМ¶a Jesus, odaa jiЙЎМ¶icotalo Judas niЙЎМ¶ijo anida aneetege niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece Jesus. LixigaЙЎМ¶awepodi eliodi oko liiЙЎМ¶exedi niЙЎМ¶ijo anoiiЙЎМ¶e sacerdotitedi ijaaЙЎМ¶ijoa niЙЎМ¶ijoa niiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anadi anodiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atece lajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco MoisГ©s, ijaa niЙЎМ¶ijo laxokodi lacilodi niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi. NiЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi-nelegi onigoetigilo nodaajoli-ocaЙЎМ¶atedi inaa neboli.
\v 44 NiЙЎМ¶ijo Judas ane yajigo Jesus maleediЙЎМ¶icotalo, ja yeloЙЎМ¶odi ica anodaaЙЎМ¶igotalo me ikee Jesus. Odaa meetiogi, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ica ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa ane inapicoЙЎМ¶o jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶idoa niЙЎМ¶ijoa anoleetibigetiwaji. Odaa abaatalo, adeegitetiwaji maniwilo.вҖқ
\p 
\v 45 Odaa Judas jiЙЎМ¶igo dowicetelogo Jesus, odaa meetalo, вҖңIniiЙЎМ¶axinoЙЎМ¶odi, iniiЙЎМ¶axinoЙЎМ¶odi!вҖқ, odaa ja napicoЙЎМ¶o Jesus.
\v 46 Odaa joЙЎМ¶odibatalo Jesus, joЙЎМ¶oniwilo.
\v 47 Pida ganigepidiЙЎМ¶ica niЙЎМ¶ijo anidiaaЙЎМ¶i midoataЙЎМ¶a nixigitice lodaajo-ocaЙЎМ¶ataЙЎМ¶a, odaa ja yakagiditice napaaЙЎМ¶ate niЙЎМ¶ijo liotagi niЙЎМ¶ijo lacilo-sacerdotitedi.
\v 48 Odaa Jesus meetediogi niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi anodibatalo, вҖңManagitiwaji adiwilo anadeegi ЙЎМ¶adodaajoli, ЙЎМ¶aneboli micataЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶a Ee ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa agopeloagi.
\v 49 Owidi nokododi idiaaЙЎМ¶ejotice minitaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liЙЎМ¶eladi, jiniiЙЎМ¶axitiniwace noiigi, pida aЙЎМ¶adiwilotiwaji. Pida natigide jiЙЎМ¶icota aneeta lotaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.вҖқ
\p 
\v 50 Odaa ijotawece niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece joЙЎМ¶oika aЙЎМ¶aleeЙЎМ¶ica mowote, ja daleditibige.
\p 
\v 51 Onini ica lioneeЙЎМ¶a ane diotibece Jesus. Onadi me dinilipaditigi niЙЎМ¶elate me yapoЙЎМ¶oditini lolaadi. Odaa joЙЎМ¶odoletibige modibata domoЙЎМ¶oniwilo.
\v 52 Pida yaladi naЙЎМ¶ajo niЙЎМ¶elate, odaa jeЙЎМ¶elodi mokijotani.
\s1 Oyadeegi Jesus lodoe niЙЎМ¶ijoa seteenta lacilodi niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi
\r (Mateus 26.57-68; Lucas 22.54-55, 63-71; JoГЈo 18.13-14, 19-24)
\p 
\v 53 Odaa joЙЎМ¶oyadeegitedicogi Jesus minitaЙЎМ¶a diimigi-nelegi liЙЎМ¶eladi niЙЎМ¶ijo lacilo-sacerdotitedi. Ja dinatecoЙЎМ¶otee niЙЎМ¶ijo anoiiЙЎМ¶e sacerdotitedi, codaa me niЙЎМ¶ijoa lacilodi noiigi judeu ijaaЙЎМ¶ijoa niЙЎМ¶ijoa niiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anadi anodiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atece lajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco MoisГ©s.
\v 54 Pedro diotece Jesus pida leegitalo me yetecetedice, odaa ja dakatiwece miditaЙЎМ¶a niogГі niЙЎМ¶ijo diimigi-nelegi ane liЙЎМ¶eladi niЙЎМ¶ijo lacilo-sacerdotitedi. Odaa ja nicotini liwigotigi niЙЎМ¶ijoa niotaka liniogotibece noledi maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a dinito.
\v 55 NiЙЎМ¶ijo anoiiЙЎМ¶e sacerdotitedi codaa mijotawece niЙЎМ¶ijoa seteenta lacilodi judeutedi odoletibige gaantiЙЎМ¶ijo ane yakadi anigetiЙЎМ¶ida ane leeЙЎМ¶odi modinanimaЙЎМ¶atalo Jesus domoЙЎМ¶owotibige doЙЎМ¶odiiЙЎМ¶enatakatalo moyeloadi. Pida aЙЎМ¶ica anoyakadi.
\v 56 Eliodi oko owote liwitakeco moyalaЙЎМ¶atalo Jesus, pida niЙЎМ¶icoa lotaЙЎМ¶a aЙЎМ¶ica ane niwoditema.
\p 
\v 57 Odaa onijo ica oko ane dabiditiniwace, odaa ja niwitakaЙЎМ¶a, modi,
\v 58 вҖңJajipaaЙЎМ¶atalo me yalaЙЎМ¶ate me yaaЙЎМ¶adi niЙЎМ¶ini AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liЙЎМ¶eladi ane loenatagi ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi, odaa nige itoatadiЙЎМ¶ida nokododi, odaa jeЙЎМ¶eotace eledi diimigi ane daЙЎМ¶a loenatagi ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi.вҖқ
\v 59 Pida oteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ijoa notaЙЎМ¶a ane domoЙЎМ¶owote modakapetege Jesus aЙЎМ¶oniwoditema.
\p 
\v 60 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo lacilo-sacerdotitedi ja dabiditi liwigotigi niЙЎМ¶ijo oko, odaa ja ige Jesus, meetalo, вҖңAЙЎМ¶ica ЙЎМ¶agegi? Amiinoa icoa lotaЙЎМ¶a idiwa ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi modakapetaЙЎМ¶agi?вҖқ
\p 
\v 61 Pida Jesus aЙЎМ¶ica gaantiЙЎМ¶ini ligegi. Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo lacilo-sacerdotitedi ja igetace Jesus, meetalo, вҖңDomige naЙЎМ¶akamaЙЎМ¶akaami NiЙЎМ¶icoa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane niiЙЎМ¶e me ЙЎМ¶odatamaЙЎМ¶ateetege ЙЎМ¶odaxakawadi, Lionigi NiЙЎМ¶ijoa ane joЙЎМ¶eeЙЎМ¶atalo?вҖқ
\v 62 Odaa Jesus ja igidi, meeteta, вҖңJeЙЎМ¶emeЙЎМ¶ee. Codaa akaamitawecetiwaji icota madati me idicotini liwai libaaЙЎМ¶adi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji anida eliodi nimaweneЙЎМ¶egi. Codaa icota madatitiwaji, Ee, ЗӨoneleegiwa ane jicoЙЎМ¶otibigimece ditibigimedi, nige jiniotinece lolaadi jicoЙЎМ¶otibigimece ditibigimedi.вҖқ \fig |src="cn01815B.tif" size="span" copy="В© 1978 David C. Cook Publishing Co." ref="Marcos 14.60-62"\fig*
\p 
\v 63 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo lacilo-sacerdotitedi ja yaaЙЎМ¶adi niЙЎМ¶ijoa lowoodi diletibige Jesus daЙЎМ¶a dotaЙЎМ¶atibige AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, mee, вҖңAЙЎМ¶alee jopooЙЎМ¶atibige eledi oko ane neloЙЎМ¶oditoЙЎМ¶owa ane libatiigi.
\v 64 JaЙЎМ¶ajipaatalotiwaji niЙЎМ¶ijoa lotaЙЎМ¶a me dotaЙЎМ¶atibige AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Amiida ica anakatitecetiwaji?вҖқ Odaa ijotawece ja nilaagedi Jesus codaa modi me leeditibige moyeloadi.
\v 65 Odaa joniЙЎМ¶ica niЙЎМ¶ijo oko jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶oyatedigi Jesus monawaletedice. Codaa onibatoo latobi Jesus monalaketedibige, odaa moditalo, вҖңIwela! Amiijo ica ane ЙЎМ¶adalakeni?вҖқ Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijoa nowienoЙЎМ¶ododi eledi onalaketedibige maleedoЙЎМ¶oyadeegiteda.
\s1 Pedro mee me diЙЎМ¶icoateda me yowooЙЎМ¶odi Jesus
\r (Mateus 26.69-75; Lucas 22.54-62; JoГЈo 18.15-18, 25-27)
\p 
\v 66 NiЙЎМ¶ijo Pedro maleeЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶itice miditaЙЎМ¶a niogГі niЙЎМ¶ijo liЙЎМ¶eladi niЙЎМ¶ijo lacilo-sacerdotitedi, odaa jiЙЎМ¶icota aca awicije liota niЙЎМ¶ijo lacilo-sacerdotitedi.
\v 67 Pedro idiaaЙЎМ¶itice liniogotibece noledi dinito. NaЙЎМ¶ajo awicije naЙЎМ¶a nadi Pedro, iwita, odaa mee, вҖңA-aami eledi idiaaЙЎМ¶o-oonitice mijoataЙЎМ¶a Jesus, niЙЎМ¶ijoa Nazareeno.вҖқ
\p 
\v 68 Pida Pedro me dotaЙЎМ¶a mee me diЙЎМ¶ica me dinadeegitibigege Jesus, odaa mee, вҖңOteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a jowooЙЎМ¶otawaanigiteda niЙЎМ¶icoa ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa anenitalo.вҖқ Odaa jiЙЎМ¶igo midataЙЎМ¶a lapoagi niogГі niЙЎМ¶ijo diimigi. Odaa jaЙЎМ¶anoe okoЙЎМ¶okoodi.
\v 69 Odaa aca eledi niota naЙЎМ¶a nadi Pedro niЙЎМ¶ijo aneitice. Odaa naЙЎМ¶ajo niota meetiogi niЙЎМ¶ica oko anodipegitege, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ida aaginaЙЎМ¶a eledi do-ootibece Jesus.вҖқ
\v 70 Odaa Pedro meetace me daЙЎМ¶a diotibece Jesus.
\p NaЙЎМ¶a leecawaanigi, niЙЎМ¶ijo oko anodipegitege moditaca Pedro, вҖңEjimewi makaami niЙЎМ¶ijo ane-diotibece, igaataЙЎМ¶a yeloЙЎМ¶o micoЙЎМ¶iticogi nipodigi GalilГ©ia, leeЙЎМ¶odi ЙЎМ¶adotaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶awa niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane icoЙЎМ¶oticogi digoida GalilГ©ia.вҖқ
\v 71 Pida Pedro jiЙЎМ¶idaa dinanatacigi me dotaЙЎМ¶a, mee, вҖңJemaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me idiloikatidi nige deЙЎМ¶ejitece anewi! IgaataЙЎМ¶a ewi meji me daЙЎМ¶a jowooЙЎМ¶oditeda niЙЎМ¶icoa ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa ane ЙЎМ¶adalakitalotiwaji.вҖқ
\p 
\v 72 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo okoЙЎМ¶okoodi jaЙЎМ¶anoetace. Odaa Pedro ja nalaЙЎМ¶atibige niЙЎМ¶ijoa ane lotaЙЎМ¶ate Jesus, niЙЎМ¶ijo meeteta, вҖңMaleedaЙЎМ¶a itoataale manoe okoЙЎМ¶okoodi, odaa itoatadiЙЎМ¶ida meni me daЙЎМ¶adowooЙЎМ¶oti.вҖқ NiЙЎМ¶ijo Pedro naЙЎМ¶a yowo niЙЎМ¶ijoa Jesus lotaЙЎМ¶ate, odaa eliodi magecaЙЎМ¶alo, codaa anoe.
\c 15
\s1 Jesus oyadeegite lodoe Pilatos, ninionigi-eliodi romaanotedi ane iiЙЎМ¶e iditawece nipodigi JudГ©ia
\r (Mateus 27.1-2, 11-14; Lucas 23.1-5; JoГЈo 18.28-38)
\p 
\v 1 NiЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a yeloЙЎМ¶otibige, odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo anoiiЙЎМ¶e sacerdotitedi odinatecoЙЎМ¶oteetege niЙЎМ¶ijoa laxokodi lacilodi judeutedi ijaaЙЎМ¶ijoa niЙЎМ¶ijoa niiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anadi anodiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atece lajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco MoisГ©s. Odinilakidetege niЙЎМ¶ijoa eletidi seteenta lacilodi noiigi judeu. Odaa joЙЎМ¶oigoetedi Jesus, joЙЎМ¶oyadeegi igotibeci moyajigotalo Pilatos, niЙЎМ¶ijo ninionigi-eliodi romaanotedi ane iiЙЎМ¶e niЙЎМ¶idi nipodigi JudГ©ia.
\v 2 Odaa Pilatos ja ige Jesus, meetalo, вҖңNaЙЎМ¶akamaЙЎМ¶akaami ninionigi-eliodi judeutedi?вҖқ Odaa Jesus naЙЎМ¶a igidi, meeteta, вҖңAnaliiki niЙЎМ¶ida ane alitigi ЙЎМ¶agegi.вҖқ
\v 3 NiЙЎМ¶ijo anoiiЙЎМ¶e sacerdotitedi eliodi modotaЙЎМ¶atibige Jesus me domoЙЎМ¶owotibige me odinanimaЙЎМ¶atalo lodoe Pilatos.
\v 4 Odaa Pilatos ja igetace Jesus, meetalo, вҖңAЙЎМ¶ica anigetiЙЎМ¶ida ЙЎМ¶adopilaЙЎМ¶atagitiogi? Digawini, eliodi modotaЙЎМ¶atibigaЙЎМ¶aji, odinanimaЙЎМ¶ataЙЎМ¶awa.вҖқ
\v 5 Pida Jesus aЙЎМ¶ica gaantokaaЙЎМ¶ida ligegi, odaa Pilatos eliodi me yopo.
\s1 OdiiЙЎМ¶enatakatalo moyeloadi Jesus
\r (Mateus 27.15-26; Lucas 23.13-25; JoГЈo 18.39вҖ“19.16)
\p 
\v 6 NiЙЎМ¶ina me nakatio lalokegi PГЎscoa, Pilatos ligileЙЎМ¶egi me ikatema niЙЎМ¶idi noiigi judeu onidateci niwilogojegi, niЙЎМ¶ica anepaaЙЎМ¶odipokotibige niЙЎМ¶idi noiigi.
\v 7 Odaa onini ica niwilogojegi ane liboonaЙЎМ¶adi BarrabГЎs. BarrabГЎs icaaЙЎМ¶icoa lokaaЙЎМ¶etedi diniwilotibigiwaji leeЙЎМ¶odi me nideleЙЎМ¶etiniwace romaanotedi ane niiЙЎМ¶enatakanaЙЎМ¶a, codaa daije.
\v 8 NiЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi-nelegi dinatecoЙЎМ¶otee, odaa jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶oyatigi modipokota Pilatos niЙЎМ¶ica ane ligileЙЎМ¶egitibece meo.
\v 9 Odaa Pilatos igidi, meetiogi, вҖңEmaanitiwaji me jikatedaЙЎМ¶adomitiwaji ninionigi-eliodi ЙЎМ¶adoiigi judeutedi?вҖқ
\v 10 Pilatos eote niЙЎМ¶ijoa lotaЙЎМ¶a leeЙЎМ¶odi yowooЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ijo anoiiЙЎМ¶e sacerdotitedi moyajigo Jesus leeЙЎМ¶odi monocetema.
\p 
\v 11 Pida niЙЎМ¶ijo anoiiЙЎМ¶e sacerdotitedi idioka limedi moyoniciwaЙЎМ¶adi niЙЎМ¶ica noiigi modipokota Pilatos me daЙЎМ¶a ikatedice Jesus, pida odipokota mijapaЙЎМ¶a ikatice BarrabГЎs.
\v 12 Pilatos ja nigetaciniwace, meetiogi, вҖңEnice, amiida anemaani mejigotalo niЙЎМ¶idoa ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa ane alitedigitiwaji me вҖҳNinionigi-eliodi judeutediвҖҷ?вҖқ
\p 
\v 13 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi napaawaЙЎМ¶ateloco, modi, вҖңOtonitedeloco nicenaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶ate meloati!вҖқ
\v 14 Odaa Pilatos ja nigetaciniwace, meetiogi, вҖңPida amiida ica loenatagi ane beyagi?вҖқ Odaa jeЙЎМ¶epaanaЙЎМ¶a napaawaЙЎМ¶ateloco, modi, вҖңOtonitedeloco nicenaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶ate meloati!вҖқ
\p 
\v 15 Pilatos yemaa me yocaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶e niЙЎМ¶idi noiigi. Odaa joaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi me ikatema BarrabГЎs, odaa ja diiЙЎМ¶enatakatalo monalaketedibige Jesus, yajigo midiwataЙЎМ¶a iodaЙЎМ¶awadi moyototedeloco nicenaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶ate moyeloadi.
\s1 NiЙЎМ¶ijoa iodaЙЎМ¶awadi oyametibigo Jesus
\r (Mateus 27.27-31; JoГЈo 19.2-3)
\p 
\v 16 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijoa iodaЙЎМ¶awadi joЙЎМ¶oyadeegi Jesus catiwedi niЙЎМ¶ijo diimigi-nelegi, liЙЎМ¶eladi niЙЎМ¶ijo lacilo romaanotedi, odaa ijoatawece niЙЎМ¶ijoa iodaЙЎМ¶awadi dinatecoЙЎМ¶otee.
\v 17 Odaa joЙЎМ¶onixomeЙЎМ¶etedinigi Jesus aca caapa lixagotoЙЎМ¶ogo, liciagi nicaapa niЙЎМ¶inoa inionaЙЎМ¶a-eloodoli. Odaa joЙЎМ¶owo lale odatika lalepiЙЎМ¶igo moyoe, odaa joЙЎМ¶onixotinece Jesus lacilo.
\v 18 Odaa jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶oyatedigi moyame, modi, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶idoa ninionigi-eliodi judeutedi!вҖқ
\v 19 Odaa onaxacoЙЎМ¶otice lacilo, oyatitalo laxacoЙЎМ¶onaЙЎМ¶adi, onawaletedice, codaa moyamaЙЎМ¶atedini lokotidi lodoe, onowo moiweniЙЎМ¶ide.
\v 20 NiЙЎМ¶ijo noЙЎМ¶oika moyametibigo, odaa joЙЎМ¶onoЙЎМ¶a naЙЎМ¶ajo nicaapa lixagotoЙЎМ¶ogo, odaa joЙЎМ¶onixomeЙЎМ¶etacedinigi niЙЎМ¶ijoa epaa lowoodi. Odaa joЙЎМ¶oyadeegi moyototedeloco nicenaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶ate moyeloadi.
\s1 Oyototedeloco Jesus nicenaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶ate moyeloadi
\r (Mateus 27.32-44; Lucas 23.26-43; JoГЈo 19.17-27)
\p 
\v 21 NiЙЎМ¶ijo maleeЙЎМ¶idaa diiticogi migotibeci minitaЙЎМ¶a lojotaЙЎМ¶adi, odaa joЙЎМ¶odakapetege ica ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa ane liboonaЙЎМ¶adi SimГЈo anelatibige nigotaЙЎМ¶a Cirene. SimГЈo eliodi Alexandre ijaa Rufo, icoЙЎМ¶oticogi nipodigi, igotibeci nigotaЙЎМ¶a JerusalГ©m. Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijoa iodaЙЎМ¶awadi joЙЎМ¶oiedeЙЎМ¶etege SimГЈo me yoyaЙЎМ¶adi naЙЎМ¶ajo licenaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶ate Jesus.
\v 22 Odaa joЙЎМ¶oyadeegitedicogi Jesus minitaЙЎМ¶a lojotaЙЎМ¶adi ane liboonaЙЎМ¶adi GГіlgota (ane diitigi вҖңAneitice ЙЎМ¶odacilo libitakaвҖқ.)
\v 23 Odaa niЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi domoЙЎМ¶oyajigotalo Jesus me wacipete viinyo awatege ica mirra ane yaaЙЎМ¶aditice niЙЎМ¶ina ane jileenaЙЎМ¶a, pida awacipete.
\v 24 Odaa niЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi joЙЎМ¶oyototedi Jesus maditaЙЎМ¶a naЙЎМ¶ajo nicenaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶ate. Odaa noЙЎМ¶odinawalacetigi niЙЎМ¶ijoa Jesus lowoodi, oiwi niЙЎМ¶ica anepaЙЎМ¶a dinetetece me yakadi oniditecibeci lowoodaЙЎМ¶agi.
\v 25 Onaca noove lakata me nigoitijo niЙЎМ¶ijo noЙЎМ¶oyototedi Jesus madataЙЎМ¶a nicenaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶ate.
\v 26 Diniditeloco niЙЎМ¶ica ane leeЙЎМ¶odi moyeloadi Jesus, oiditeloco taaboa ditibigimedawaanigi lacilo, iwoteloco,
\qc \sc вҖңNINIONIGI-ELIODI JUDEUTEDI.вҖқ\sc*
\p 
\v 27 Codaa niЙЎМ¶ijoa iodaЙЎМ¶awadi aaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a oyototedi itoata agopeloaЙЎМ¶a midoataЙЎМ¶a eletidi nicenaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶atedi. Onijoteci oidoyatice liwai libaaЙЎМ¶adi Jesus, odaa ica eledi agopeloagi oidoyatice eledi liwai diЙЎМ¶etege nimagijegi.
\v 28 Odaa jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee micotece niЙЎМ¶ijo aneetece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lotaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axi, niЙЎМ¶ijo neЙЎМ¶ee, вҖңAnodigotaЙЎМ¶awa owo liciagi niЙЎМ¶ijoa agopeloaЙЎМ¶a.вҖқ
\p 
\v 29 NiЙЎМ¶ijo oko anidiaaЙЎМ¶igotinece midoataЙЎМ¶a onalomeЙЎМ¶etedice. Codaa oyabale inoa lacilodi, modi, вҖңAidiiЙЎМ¶a! Geemeni me domaЙЎМ¶a ojikeni liЙЎМ¶eladi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, odaa domaЙЎМ¶a adabiteЙЎМ¶enitacini catiwedi itoatadiЙЎМ¶ida nokododi.
\v 30 JaЙЎМ¶abo mawikodee, axotitice naЙЎМ¶ada ЙЎМ¶adicenaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶ate!вҖқ
\p 
\v 31 IdaaЙЎМ¶ee maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a oyalomeЙЎМ¶e niЙЎМ¶ijo anoiiЙЎМ¶e sacerdotitedi, ijaaЙЎМ¶ijoa niЙЎМ¶ijoa niiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anadi anodiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atece lajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco MoisГ©s. Odaa dinotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶etiwage, modi, вҖңEote niЙЎМ¶ijo eledi oko me newiЙЎМ¶atace, pida ayakadi mepaa dinewikatidi.вҖқ
\v 32 Odaa moditalo Jesus, вҖңAkaami ane eni AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me ЙЎМ¶adimonyaa me ЙЎМ¶odatamaЙЎМ¶ateenitege ЙЎМ¶odaxakawadi, akaami ane eni makaami ninionigi-eliodi ЙЎМ¶odoiigi Israel, adaxotiti niЙЎМ¶ina natigide naЙЎМ¶ada ЙЎМ¶adicenaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶ate bidige jakataЙЎМ¶a me jinataЙЎМ¶a, codaa me ЙЎМ¶adadiwaЙЎМ¶ateЙЎМ¶egi!вҖқ Codaa me niЙЎМ¶ijoa itoataale agopeloaЙЎМ¶a anaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶oyototiniwace midoataЙЎМ¶a nicenaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶atedi aaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a oyalomeЙЎМ¶e Jesus.
\s1 LemeЙЎМ¶egi Jesus
\r (Mateus 27.45-56; Lucas 23.44-49; JoГЈo 19.28-30)
\p 
\v 33 NiЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a yaxoЙЎМ¶o-noko, ja nexocaЙЎМ¶a inatawece iiЙЎМ¶o, odaa nexocaЙЎМ¶a neЙЎМ¶epaa iniwatadaЙЎМ¶ani lakata me ЙЎМ¶ocidi.
\v 34 NiЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a iniwatadaЙЎМ¶ani lakata me ЙЎМ¶ocidi, odaa Jesus igedi me dapaawe, mee, вҖңEloГӯ, EloГӯ, lemГЎ sabactani?вҖқ (NiЙЎМ¶idiwa lotaЙЎМ¶a amina anejinaЙЎМ¶a вҖңInoenoЙЎМ¶odi, InoenoЙЎМ¶odi, igaamee me daЙЎМ¶adiaaЙЎМ¶ica mawiitigiji?вҖқ)
\p 
\v 35 AnigepidiЙЎМ¶ica niЙЎМ¶ijo oko anidiaaЙЎМ¶itice owajipatalo niЙЎМ¶ijoa lotaЙЎМ¶a Jesus, odaa modi, вҖңDigajipaatalo! Dapaawetedigi Elias!вҖқ
\v 36 Odaa onijoteci niЙЎМ¶ijo anidiaaЙЎМ¶itice midoataЙЎМ¶a walokodi, odaa itiminatidi niЙЎМ¶ijo litikonaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶adi midataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ijo viinyo ane daЙЎМ¶a dakake loojedi. Odaa ja dabiteЙЎМ¶etibigimece Jesus me domeЙЎМ¶eo me ilibitetece. Odaa mee, вҖңAlotacaliita! Jemaa me jiwinaЙЎМ¶a Elias nigenagi noЙЎМ¶atedice madataЙЎМ¶a naЙЎМ¶ada nicenaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶ate.вҖқ
\p 
\v 37 Odaa Jesus dinigetaЙЎМ¶ateetace me dapaawe, odaa ja yeleo.
\v 38 Onada minitaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liЙЎМ¶eladi aca lipegeteЙЎМ¶e ane noxoco niЙЎМ¶ijo diimigi-le ane ijokijoateda AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji mida aneetetege. NaЙЎМ¶ajo lipegeteЙЎМ¶e daawidigidicetigi liwigotigi ditibigimedi neЙЎМ¶epaa natinedi. \fig |src="CN01843B.TIF" size="span" copy="В© 1978 David C. Cook Publishing Co." ref="Marcos 15.38"\fig*
\v 39 IdiaaЙЎМ¶itice lodoe licenaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶ate Jesus ica jajeentegi. NiЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a nadi anodaaЙЎМ¶eeteda Jesus me dapaawe codaa anodaaЙЎМ¶eeteda me yeleo, odaa mee, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶idoa ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa dicewi me Lionigi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.вҖқ
\p 
\v 40 OnaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a idiaaЙЎМ¶iticoaci ica iwaalepodi pida leegitiogi moiЙЎМ¶oaditalo. Liwigotigi niЙЎМ¶ijo iwaalepodi ani naЙЎМ¶ajo anodita Maria Madalena, SalomГ©, ajaa Maria ane eliodo JosГ©, ijaa Tiago ane niloxooxegi.
\v 41 NiЙЎМ¶ijo Jesus maleeЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶itedice nipodigi GalilГ©ia, niЙЎМ¶idi iwaalepodi odiotibece oyaxawa. OnidiaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a itice ica eliodi eledi iwaalepodi ane lixigaЙЎМ¶awepodi maleekokigoteda Jesus manitaЙЎМ¶a nigotaЙЎМ¶a JerusalГ©m.
\s1 NoЙЎМ¶onaligitini lolaadi Jesus
\r (Mateus 27.57-61; Lucas 23.50-56; JoГЈo 19.38-42)
\p 
\v 42-43 NiЙЎМ¶ijo noko maleedaЙЎМ¶a nakatio saabado, noko noЙЎМ¶odinoweditege ica lalokegi PГЎscoa. NaЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶ocidi, jiЙЎМ¶icotio JosГ© anelatibige nigotaЙЎМ¶a ArimatГ©ia minitaЙЎМ¶a Pilatos. JosГ© ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa anele, lokaaЙЎМ¶etedipi me nibaaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ijoa seteenta lacilodi judeutedi. Ja walitege niЙЎМ¶ica noko AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji nige iiЙЎМ¶e laaleЙЎМ¶enali niЙЎМ¶ina oko. JosГ© abo laaleЙЎМ¶ena migo dipokota Pilatos Jesus lolaadi.
\v 44 Pilatos yopo niЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a dibodicetibige Jesus naЙЎМ¶a yeleo. Odaa jeЙЎМ¶enidita niЙЎМ¶ijo jajeentegi me ige domigewi naЙЎМ¶a leecawaanigi me yeleo Jesus.
\v 45 NiЙЎМ¶ijo jajeentegi naЙЎМ¶a yeloЙЎМ¶odita mewi, odaa Pilatos ja ika JosГ© me yadeegi Jesus lolaadi.
\v 46 JosГ© dinoojeteta aca lipegeteЙЎМ¶e lapacoЙЎМ¶ogo, odaa ja noЙЎМ¶a Jesus lolaadi madataЙЎМ¶a nicenaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶ate, odaa ja ilipaditigi Jesus lolaadi naЙЎМ¶ajo lipegeteЙЎМ¶e. NiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi ja yadeegiticogi Jesus lolaadi midataЙЎМ¶a ica ane gela moigodi lawimaЙЎМ¶ajegi-wetiЙЎМ¶a. Odaa JosГ© ja noxoco yatita aca wetiЙЎМ¶a nelegi me noxoco.
\v 47 IdiaaЙЎМ¶iticoaci moiwi Maria Madalena ajaa Maria ane eliodo eledi JosГ©. Odaa onadi niЙЎМ¶ijo anoyatice lolaadi Jesus.
\c 16
\s1 Jesus naЙЎМ¶a yewiЙЎМ¶atace
\r (Mateus 28.1-8; Lucas 24.1-12; JoГЈo 20.1-10)
\p 
\v 1 NiЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a ixomaЙЎМ¶atijo saabado, odaa Maria Madalena, SalomГ© ajaa Maria ane eliodo Tiago joЙЎМ¶odinoojetetalo nadokojetedi me domoЙЎМ¶oyatita Jesus lolaadi.
\v 2 One nigoitijo niЙЎМ¶ijo odoejegi noko semaana, aligeЙЎМ¶e ja doletibige me nodi, odaa jiЙЎМ¶igotibeci midataЙЎМ¶a lawimaЙЎМ¶ajegi-wetiЙЎМ¶a anoyatice Jesus lolaadi.
\v 3 Naigitece ja dinotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶etiwage, modi, вҖңAmigetiЙЎМ¶ijo ane noЙЎМ¶owatoЙЎМ¶odomi naЙЎМ¶ajo wetiЙЎМ¶a nelegi ane noxoco niЙЎМ¶ijo wetiЙЎМ¶a-lawimaЙЎМ¶ajegi?вҖқ
\v 4 Odaa jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee me dinotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶e igaataЙЎМ¶a naЙЎМ¶ajo wetiЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶axa me nelegi. Pida niЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a icotiobece, noЙЎМ¶oiwita, odaa joЙЎМ¶onadi naЙЎМ¶ajo wetiЙЎМ¶a nelegi joЙЎМ¶onoЙЎМ¶aticogi midataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ijo lawimaЙЎМ¶ajegi-wetiЙЎМ¶a.
\v 5 NiЙЎМ¶ijo noЙЎМ¶odakatiwece niЙЎМ¶ijo lawimaЙЎМ¶ajegi-wetiЙЎМ¶a, odaa joЙЎМ¶onadi ica lioneeЙЎМ¶a ane dinixotinigilo nowoodi ane yapacaЙЎМ¶a. Nicoti diЙЎМ¶eticogi liwai libaaЙЎМ¶adi niЙЎМ¶ijo anoyatice lolaadi Jesus. NiЙЎМ¶ijo noЙЎМ¶onadi, odaa eliodi me nawelatibigiwaji.
\p 
\v 6 Pida niЙЎМ¶ijo lioneeЙЎМ¶a meetiogi, вҖңJinaЙЎМ¶a anawelatiwaji! JowooЙЎМ¶odi me domoЙЎМ¶oleetibige Jesus anelatibige nigotaЙЎМ¶a NazarГ©. OwooЙЎМ¶oti moyototedeloco nicenaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶ate, odaa ja yeleo. Pida aЙЎМ¶aleeЙЎМ¶icoa digoina, ja yewiЙЎМ¶atace. Digawini anoyatice lolaadi.
\v 7 Pida niЙЎМ¶ina natigide emiitiwaji, eloЙЎМ¶otitiogi niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece codaa me Pedro. Enitiogi migo Jesus dinewadetedicogi digoida nipodigi GalilГ©ia. Odaa jiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶itice manatitetiwaji, niЙЎМ¶ijo ane ligegitedaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji.вҖқ
\p 
\v 8 Odaa ja yediiЙЎМ¶a me noditicoaci midataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ijo lawimaЙЎМ¶ajegi-wetiЙЎМ¶a, odaa ja daleditibige, nawigicaЙЎМ¶ateloco, leeЙЎМ¶odi meliodi me doitibigiwaji. Odaa aЙЎМ¶ica gaantiЙЎМ¶ijo anoyatematita.
\s1 Jesus dinikeeteta Maria Madalena
\r (Mateus 28.9-10; JoГЈo 20.11-18)
\p 
\v 9 Jesus yewiЙЎМ¶atace niЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a domiingo me nigoitijo. Odoeje me dinikeeteta Maria Madalena, naЙЎМ¶ajo anijo mijoa seete niwicidi abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a ane iticoitedice Jesus.
\v 10 Odaa Maria Madalena jiЙЎМ¶igo, yatematitiogi niЙЎМ¶ijo lokaaЙЎМ¶etedi Jesus aneliodi magecaЙЎМ¶alodipi codaa noenaЙЎМ¶ateloco.
\v 11 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a nibodicaЙЎМ¶a Jesus naЙЎМ¶a yewiЙЎМ¶atace, codaa Maria mee me nadi, aЙЎМ¶oyiwaЙЎМ¶adi.
\s1 Jesus jaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a dinikeetediogi icoa itoataale anodiotibece
\r (Lucas 24.13-35)
\p 
\v 12 NiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi Jesus dinikeetediogi niЙЎМ¶ijo itoataale anodiotibece maleeЙЎМ¶idaa diiticogi mewaligitibigiwaji miditaЙЎМ¶a ica nipodigi wetice nigotaЙЎМ¶a. Ica ane latopagi diniigi niЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a dinikeetediogi.
\v 13 NiЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a dopitiobece, odaa joЙЎМ¶oyatematitiogi niЙЎМ¶ijo eledi anodiotibece modakapetege Jesus. Pida niЙЎМ¶ijo eledi aЙЎМ¶oyiwaЙЎМ¶adi niЙЎМ¶ijo latematigo.
\s1 Jesus dinikeetediogi niЙЎМ¶ijo oonze anodiotibece
\r (Mateus 28.16-20; Lucas 24.36-49; JoГЈo 20.19-23; Atos 1.6-8)
\p 
\v 14 NiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi Jesus ja dinikeetediogi niЙЎМ¶ijo oonze anodiotibece niЙЎМ¶ijo me niodaЙЎМ¶a. Odaa ja napeteЙЎМ¶etediniwace leeЙЎМ¶odi laaleЙЎМ¶enali daЙЎМ¶axa me dakake, codaa leeЙЎМ¶odi me doЙЎМ¶oyiwaЙЎМ¶adi naЙЎМ¶a yewiЙЎМ¶atace noЙЎМ¶oyatemati niЙЎМ¶ijo anonadi naЙЎМ¶a yewiЙЎМ¶atace.
\v 15 Odaa Jesus meetediogi, вҖңEmiitecetiwaji inatawece ane noiigi niЙЎМ¶ina iiЙЎМ¶o, atematiitedibecetiwaji nibodicetedi anele aneetici.
\v 16 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji eote gela lewiЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina oko aneyiwaЙЎМ¶adi nibodicetedi anele, codaa leeditibige me dinilege. Pida niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane deЙЎМ¶eyiwaЙЎМ¶adi, AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji baЙЎМ¶a laagedi codaa me iloikatidi.
\v 17 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ikee niЙЎМ¶ica nimaweneЙЎМ¶egi, codaa eotetema loxiceЙЎМ¶edi niЙЎМ¶ina oko anoyiwaЙЎМ¶adi. Codaa oibake IboonaЙЎМ¶adi niЙЎМ¶ina moiticoitedice niwicidi abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a, codaa odotaЙЎМ¶atigilo eletidi iolatedi ane diЙЎМ¶ica modotaЙЎМ¶atigi niЙЎМ¶ica jotigide.
\v 18 Nigodibatalo laketedi ane diniweneene, oЙЎМ¶oa domige owacipeta weneeno me doЙЎМ¶oyowooЙЎМ¶odi, aЙЎМ¶ica ninyaagi. Nigoipeketelogo libaaЙЎМ¶atedi niЙЎМ¶inoa eelotaginadi, odaa ja nicilaЙЎМ¶a.вҖқ
\s1 Jesus noЙЎМ¶opitedibigimece ditibigimedi
\r (Lucas 24.50-53; Atos 1.9-11)
\p 
\v 19 NiЙЎМ¶ijo ЗӨoniotagodi Jesus naЙЎМ¶a ika me notaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶etediniwace, odaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ja yadeegitedibigimece ditibigimedi, odaa ja nicotedi liwai libaaЙЎМ¶adi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ikee mida naЙЎМ¶atetigi.
\v 20 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece jiЙЎМ¶igotibeci oyatematitedibece nibodicetedi inoatawece ane nipodaЙЎМ¶a. Odaa ЗӨoniotagodi yaxawatediogi, codaa meote ЙЎМ¶odoxiceЙЎМ¶etedi me ikee niЙЎМ¶inoa latematiko anoyatematitibece mewi. Odaa jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee. (AmГ©m.)
